(65, 7, 1, 1, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung UA49K5300 49 LED TV, Full HD, Digital - Smart', '<div class="sub-header" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Product Information</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 438.75px;">\r\n<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="background-color:transparent; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:408px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Product code</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">UA49K5300</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Screen Size (inches)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">49</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Resolution</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">Full HD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Features</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">USB, HDMI, Digital tuner, Smart TV</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Display Type</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">LED</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">SKU</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">15102077</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><span style="color:rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family:arial,sans-serif">Samsung</span><span style="color:rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family:arial,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family:arial,sans-serif">UA49K5300</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>49&quot; Smart Digital Tv</li>\r\n	<li>Full Hd Ready</li>\r\n	<li>Dvb-T2 Digital Tuner Ready</li>\r\n	<li>Wifi Direct</li>\r\n	<li>Hyper Real Picture Engine</li>\r\n	<li>Quad Core Processor</li>\r\n	<li>Wide Color Enhancer Plus</li>\r\n	<li>Smart View</li>\r\n	<li>Sports Mode/Film Mode/ Game Mode</li>\r\n	<li>Eco Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>2 Hdmi Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>2 Usb Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>1 Av Shared Input\r\n	<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n	<h2><strong>Your space. Your unique lifestyle. Joiiii</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>TVs always get the final say where the couch goes. We want to shake things up, and give you the freedom to decorate the way you want to, not the way you have to. So we bring you Joiiii. It&rsquo;s fun, playful and unique, and it goes anywhere. Best of all? It fits your lifestyle, not the other way around.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><img alt="Your space. Your unique lifestyle. Joiiii" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/levant-feature-full-hd-k5300-ua49k5300arsmz-60107736?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n	<h2><strong>Tailored design. Simply iconic.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>Joiiii breaks boundaries. Its smooth, clean design blends in anywhere, yet the playful colour doesn&rsquo;t get buried. Now, you have the freedom to tailor your TV to your own lifestyle. Finally, a TV that fits you.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><img alt="Tailored design. Simply iconic." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/levant-feature-full-hd-k5300-ua49k5300arsmz-60107740?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n	<h2><strong>A perfect fit. All 360 degrees.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>No messy wires. No unsightly air vents. Just one cord for a smooth back that looks great anywhere. So put Joiiii by the wall, in the middle of the room, or on a stand by the bed. It&rsquo;s unique, but blends in beautifully.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><img alt="A perfect fit. All 360 degrees." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/levant-feature-full-hd-k5300-60903755?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n	<h2><strong>4 legs. 2 different looks.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>We couldn&rsquo;t give Joiiii a set of wings, so we opted for unique metallic legs that fit into the built-in holes in seconds. The front ones are longer and can be reversed in seconds for a downward tilt (32&rdquo; only). Perfect for bedtime TV.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><img alt="4 legs. 2 different looks." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/levant-feature-full-hd-k5300-ua49k5300arsmz-60107748?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n	<h2><strong>One place for all your content</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n	<p>Accessing content should be quick and easy. Now, whatever you connect to your TV&mdash;apps, games, online videos, and streaming services&mdash;you can find it on one screen. Check the previews or dive right in.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><img alt="One place for all your content" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/levant-feature-full-hd-k5300-ua49k5300arsmz-60107750?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n	<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n	<h3><strong>Joiiii, a modern day jukebox</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n	<p>Haven&rsquo;t you ever wanted your own personal jukebox? Well now you can. Joiiii pumps out some awesome sound, and all you have to do is connect your phone with Bluetooth and press play on your favourite playlist.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><img alt="Joiiii, a modern day jukebox" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/levant-feature-full-hd-k5300-ua49k5300arsmz-60107739?$FB_TYPE_C_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n	<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n	<h3><strong>Joiiii for the whole family</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n	<p>Joiiii adapts to fit your needs, and it&rsquo;s perfect for every member of the family, especially seniors. With a quick switch, it gives your grandparents clearer images and crisp, more audible sound. Now everyone can see and hear equally well.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><img alt="Joiiii for the whole family" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/levant-feature-full-hd-k5300-ua49k5300arsmz-60107743?$FB_TYPE_B_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n	<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n	<h3><strong>Every pixel. Clear as crystal.</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n	<p>Vivid details. Bright colours. Dynamic visuals. Joiiii&rsquo;s noise reducing and colour-and-contrast enhancing technology refine every picture, so you aren&rsquo;t just watching a movie, you&rsquo;ll be part of it.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><img alt="Every pixel. Clear as crystal." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/levant-feature-full-hd-k5300-60903732?$FB_TYPE_C_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, '', '', 'JCG1015', NULL, '15102077', NULL, 'visible', 87145, 82995, 1, 'samsung-ua49k5300-49-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart.jpg', 'samsung-ua49k5300-49-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart-2.jpg', 'samsung-ua49k5300-49-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart-3.jpg', 'samsung-ua49k5300-49-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-ua49k5300-49-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart', '2017-09-12 20:57:17', '2017-09-12 20:57:17');
