(79, 7, 1, 1, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung UA55K5300 55 LED TV, Full HD, Digital - Smart', '<div class="sub-header" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Product Information</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 438.75px;">\r\n<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="background-color:transparent; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:408px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Product code</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">UA55K5300</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Features</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">USB, HDMI, Digital tuner, Smart TV</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Screen Size (inches)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">55</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Resolution</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">Full HD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Display Type</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">LED</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">SKU</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">15102078</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>55&quot; Smart Digital Tv</li>\r\n	<li>Full Hd Ready</li>\r\n	<li>Dvb-T2 Digital Tuner Ready</li>\r\n	<li>Wifi Direct</li>\r\n	<li>Hyper Real Picture Engine</li>\r\n	<li>Quad Core Processor</li>\r\n	<li>Wide Color Enhancer Plus</li>\r\n	<li>Smart View</li>\r\n	<li>Sports Mode/Film Mode/ Game Mode</li>\r\n	<li>Eco Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>2 Hdmi Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>2 Usb Inputs</li>\r\n	<li>1 Av Shared Input</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Your space. Your unique lifestyle. Joiiii</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>TVs always get the final say where the couch goes. We want to shake things up, and give you the freedom to decorate the way you want to, not the way you have to. So we bring you Joiiii. It&rsquo;s fun, playful and unique, and it goes anywhere. Best of all? It fits your lifestyle, not the other way around.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Tailored design. Simply iconic.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Joiiii breaks boundaries. Its smooth, clean design blends in anywhere, yet the playful colour doesn&rsquo;t get buried. Now, you have the freedom to tailor your TV to your own lifestyle. Finally, a TV that fits you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>A perfect fit. All 360 degrees.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>No messy wires. No unsightly air vents. Just one cord for a smooth back that looks great anywhere. So put Joiiii by the wall, in the middle of the room, or on a stand by the bed. It&rsquo;s unique, but blends in beautifully.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>4 legs. 2 different looks.</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We couldn&rsquo;t give Joiiii a set of wings, so we opted for unique metallic legs that fit into the built-in holes in seconds. The front ones are longer and can be reversed in seconds for a downward tilt (32&rdquo; only). Perfect for bedtime TV.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>One place for all your content</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Accessing content should be quick and easy. Now, whatever you connect to your TV&mdash;apps, games, online videos, and streaming services&mdash;you can find it on one screen. Check the previews or dive right in.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Joiiii, a modern day jukebox</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Haven&rsquo;t you ever wanted your own personal jukebox? Well now you can. Joiiii pumps out some awesome sound, and all you have to do is connect your phone with Bluetooth and press play on your favourite playlist.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Joiiii for the whole family</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Joiiii adapts to fit your needs, and it&rsquo;s perfect for every member of the family, especially seniors. With a quick switch, it gives your grandparents clearer images and crisp, more audible sound. Now everyone can see and hear equally well.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Every pixel. Clear as crystal.</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vivid details. Bright colours. Dynamic visuals. Joiiii&rsquo;s noise reducing and colour-and-contrast enhancing technology refine every picture, so you aren&rsquo;t just watching a movie, you&rsquo;ll be part of it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '', '', 'JCG1026', NULL, '15102078', NULL, 'visible', 104995, 99995, 1, 'samsung-ua55k5300-55-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart.jpg', 'samsung-ua55k5300-55-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart-2.jpg', 'samsung-ua55k5300-55-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-ua55k5300-55-led-tv-full-hd-digital-smart', '2017-09-13 19:44:45', '2017-09-13 19:44:45'),
(80, 7, 1, 1, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung 48" LED TV UA48J5200AK - SMART', '<div class="sub-header" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Product Information</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 438.75px;">\r\n<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="background-color:transparent; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:408px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Product code</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">UA48J5200AK</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Screen Size (inches)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">48</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Resolution</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">Full HD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Features</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">USB, HDMI, Digital tuner, Smart TV</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Display Type</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">LED</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">SKU</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">15102039</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>PRODUCT HIGHLIGHTS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Full HD 1080p&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Wide Color Enhancer&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Smart TV</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Picture Quality</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Full HD 1080p&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Wide Color Enhancer&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; CMR 100</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Smart&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Smart TV&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Apps&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Web Browser</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features &amp; Connectivity&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Dolby&reg; MS10&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; DTS Premium Sound&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; DTS Studio Sound&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 20W (2Ch)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 3 HDMI&reg; Connections&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 1 USB Connection&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Wi-Fi Built in&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 1 Component In&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 1 Composite In (AV)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Included in Box</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Standard Remote Control</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>FEATURES</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Discover a new reality in Full HD</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy a greater level of home entertainment realism than ever before. Thanks to a resolution twice as high as standard HD TVs, your Samsung FHD TV delivers a breathtaking viewing experience that takes you beyond the screen into a world of total immersion. When you&rsquo;ve seen the rich and vivid texture of Full HD images, your favourite TV programs and movies will never be the same again. Discover reality with a full high definition experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Content that suits your lifestyle</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Smart TVs are designed to give you what you really want and match your lifestyle, with smart apps that make life at home more fun and full of great experiences. Chefs will love the food app, while sports fans will cheer the dynamic new sport app. It also has a fitness app for those who want to stay in shape, an art education app that&rsquo;s great for kids, and a next-level gaming app that gamers will rave about, with a wide range of titles to choose from and easy pairing with your mobile or wearable as a controller. This is just the beginning of the amazing customised contents and services you can expect.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>More vibrant colours for better images</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Using an advanced picture quality improvement algorithm, Samsung&rsquo;s Wide Colour Enhancer drastically improves the quality of any image and uncovers hidden details. Now see colours as they were meant to be seen with Wide Colour Enhancer.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Watch movies from your USB</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With ConnectShare Movie, simply plug your USB memory drive or HDD into the TV and instantaneously enjoy movies, photos or music. Now, you can experience a wide variety of content in the comfort of your living room on your TV.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Bringing a full multimedia experience into your living room</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With High Definition Multimedia Interface (HDMI) inputs, the Samsung TV will transform your living room into a multimedia entertainment centre. HDMI provides high-speed transmission of high definition digital data from multiple devices straight into your TV.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '', '', 'JCG1027', NULL, '15102039', NULL, 'visible', 90295, 85995, 1, 'samsung-48-led-tv-ua48j5200ak-smart.jpg', 'samsung-48-led-tv-ua48j5200ak-smart-2.jpg', 'samsung-48-led-tv-ua48j5200ak-smart-3.jpg', 'samsung-48-led-tv-ua48j5200ak-smart-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-48-led-tv-ua48j5200ak-smart', '2017-09-13 19:54:28', '2017-09-13 19:54:28'),
(81, 7, 1, 1, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung 55" LED TV UA55M6500AKXKE - Curved, FHD, Smart', '<div class="sub-header" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Product Information</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 438.75px;">\r\n<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="background-color:transparent; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:408px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Product code</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">UA55M6500AKXKE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Screen Size (inches)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">55</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Resolution</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">Full HD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Features</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">USB, HDMI, Digital tuner, Smart TV, Curved</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Display Type</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">LED</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">SKU</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">15102087</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Samsung UA55M6500AKXKE 49&quot; Curved LED TV</li>\r\n	<li>Ultra clean view</li>\r\n	<li>Auto Depth Enhancer</li>\r\n	<li>Micro Dimming Pro</li>\r\n	<li>PurColour</li>\r\n	<li>Immersive curved design</li>\r\n	<li>One remote control</li>\r\n	<li>Smart View</li>\r\n	<li>Smart Hub</li>\r\n	<li>Auto detection</li>\r\n	<li>Connect share movie</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ultra clean view</strong><br />\r\nAnalysing original content with an advanced algorithm, Ultra Clean View gives you higher quality images with less distortion. Enjoy the clear picture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Auto Depth Enhancer</strong><br />\r\nExperience another level of immersive viewing. Auto Depth Enhancer adjusts multi-layer contrast levels for an enhanced sense of depth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Micro Dimming Pro</strong><br />\r\nExperience accurate shadow detail and colour. Dividing the screen into zones, Micro Dimming Pro analyses each one for deeper blacks and purer whites.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PurColour</strong><br />\r\nGet a natural colour experience with Purcolour. Dive into your TV entertainment and see all the colours of nature in accurate detail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Immersive curved design</strong><br />\r\nGet a better viewing experience with the curved design. You&rsquo;ll feel right in the centre of the action with the wider field of view and uniformed viewing distance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>One remote control</strong><br />\r\nGet the ultimate control in the palm of your hand. Control all devices connected with just the one remote control. With Voice Control, you&rsquo;ll never have to flip through channels again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Smart View</strong><br />\r\nJust connect your mobile to your big screen and enjoy all your content. And with the Smart View app, you can seamlessly control everything from your mobile.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Smart Hub</strong><br />\r\nSee everything in one place. One Depth gathers a variety of content for you on one screen. Get easy access to different content providers and check out the thumbnail previews before diving in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Auto detection</strong><br />\r\nFind and recognise all your connected devices faster. Samsung TV automatically displays device names, and makes all your input selections a breeze.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connect share movie</strong><br />\r\nPlug your favourite entertainment and media into your TV &ndash; watch videos, play music, or view photos through a USB connection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '', '', 'JCG1028', NULL, '15102087', NULL, 'visible', 125995, 119995, 1, 'samsung-55-led-tv-ua55m6500akxke-curved-fhd-smart.jpg', 'samsung-55-led-tv-ua55m6500akxke-curved-fhd-smart-2.jpg', 'samsung-55-led-tv-ua55m6500akxke-curved-fhd-smart-3.jpg', 'samsung-55-led-tv-ua55m6500akxke-curved-fhd-smart-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-55-led-tv-ua55m6500akxke-curved-fhd-smart', '2017-09-13 19:59:53', '2017-09-13 19:59:53'),
(82, 7, 1, 1, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung 60" LED TV UA60KU7000 - Ultra HD, Smart', '<div class="sub-header" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Product Information</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 438.75px;">\r\n<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="background-color:transparent; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:408px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Product code</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">UA60KU7000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Screen Size (inches)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">60</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Resolution</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">Ultra HD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Features</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">USB, HDMI, Digital tuner, Smart TV</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Display Type</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">LED</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">SKU</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">15102054</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Life in ultra-high definition</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The definition of UHD 4K Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The feature laden Samsung UHD TV gives viewers an unparalleled experience in Colour and resolution.<br />\r\nAmongst this TV&rsquo;s plethora of eye exciters are its Purcolour and HDR abilities. So what can you expect?<br />\r\nWell for starters clearer expression of detail and more life-like colour regardless of ambient lighting levels. Watch TV come to life.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Bright and lively whales tale image is on Samsung UHD TV screen." src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-picture-main.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Conventional display</strong><img alt="Wider Colour spectrum bar and bright and clear flower image explains purcolour" src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-purcolour-conventionl.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Pur Colour</strong><img alt="Wider Colour spectrum bar and bright and clear flower image explains purcolour" src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-purcolour.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Pur Colour</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Purcolour technology brings images to life in just the way nature intended<br />\r\nfor us to see them. The clear expression and abundance of true-to-life tones<br />\r\nwill astound your eyes and excite your senses as it recreates more natural<br />\r\nand realistic colours onscreen.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="A half of screen is conventional and half is an uhd 4k screen." src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-picture-uhd4k.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" />&nbsp;<strong>UHD 4K</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Conventional</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>UHD 4K</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>4K UHD brings out the finest details in all your viewing material.<br />\r\nWith 3840 x 2160 pixels onscreen every nuance is clear and ready<br />\r\nfor you to feast your eyes upon. Resolution up to four times<br />\r\nthat of Full HD TV ensures you&#39;ll experience sharper, more<br />\r\naccurate images with immaculate true-to-life colour expression.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="A Right perspective angle of samsung uhd TV with bright landscape onscreen image." src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-picture-hdr.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>HDR</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>You may not have realized how much you were missing<br />\r\nin your day to day viewing before HDR brought the light<br />\r\nout of the shadows. Expect images with higher brightness<br />\r\nas a whole new world of detail is revealed and<br />\r\nbrought to life. All images come closer to reality<br />\r\nthanks to HDR technology.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Icon for UHD Upscaling" src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-picture-icon-uhd-upscaling.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>UHD Upscaling</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung UHD TV automatically optimises general content<br />\r\nso you&#39;ll always enjoy a UHD-level viewing experience<br />\r\nno matter the original quality. By using a 4-step upscaling process,<br />\r\ndetails are enhanced as frame noise is eliminated.<br />\r\nThe resulting picture quality is beautifully clear<br />\r\nand generally better all-round.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Icon for UHD Dimming" src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-picture-icon-uhd-dimming.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>UHD Dimming</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung UHD TV takes full advantage of its processing power<br />\r\nto exercise total software control of picture enhancement.<br />\r\nThe screen itself is divided up into hundreds of zones<br />\r\nthat are each individually analysed and adjusted to optimise colour,<br />\r\nbrightness and sharpness. The result is more accurate and sharper images.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Smart Hub</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Turn on the TV and everything you need is on the screen. Whether it&rsquo;s streamed movies, games, or a live broadcast, going from one to the other<br />\r\nis the same as flipping through channels. It&rsquo;s that easy and that intuitive. And of course you only need one single remote for it all.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Smart hub UI called Eden is on Samsung TV onscreen." src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-smart.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Icon for smart hub" src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/resource/img/overview-smart-ico1.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /><strong>Smart Hub</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>There&rsquo;s so much to watch, from so many sources. With the Smart Hub,<br />\r\nyou&rsquo;ll find it all in one place just by turning on the TV. Switching from one source<br />\r\nto the next is effortless, adjusting the TV settings is child&rsquo;s play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Icon for smart view" src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/resource/img/overview-smart-ico4.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /><strong>Smart View</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Install the Smart View app on your smartphone and PC, and you can share<br />\r\nthe content on the devices directly to your Samsung TV.<br />\r\nFrom photos and videos to music, it&rsquo;s so much better when enjoyed on<br />\r\nthe bigger screen.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Icon for game" src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/resource/img/overview-smart-cloud_game_only.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /><strong>Game</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you have a game console or not, the option to play games straight<br />\r\nfrom the cloud on your Samsung TV is one you&rsquo;ll get used to pretty quickly.<br />\r\nAll you need is a game controller and Internet connection to start playing your favourite games<br />\r\nvia Samsung Smart Hub&rsquo;s Game Panel.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><small>*Games function requires Internet access and Game controller, sold separately.<br />\r\n*Certain applications and services may not be available in all regions and may not be available on certain models. Please check the model specifications for details<br />\r\n*Performance may vary according to home network environment.</small><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Tech Specs</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="KU7000 60spec-1,363.6 mm (W), 789.5 mm (H, without stand), 852.8 mm (H, with stand), 64.0 mm (D, without stand), 369.4 mm (D, with stand)" src="http://www.samsung.com/za/tv/KU7000/img/samsung-tv-uhd-ku6000-dimension-60inch.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></