(84, 7, 1, 1, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung UA55H8000 55" LED TV - CURVED, 3D, SMART, 1000CMR', '<div class="sub-header" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Product Information</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 438.75px;">\r\n<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="background-color:transparent; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:408px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Product code</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">UA55H8000</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Screen Size (inches)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">55</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Resolution</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">Full HD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Features</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">USB, HDMI, Digital tuner, Smart TV, 3D, Curved</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Display Type</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">LED</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">SKU</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">2120211</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>55&#39;&#39;</li>\r\n	<li>DVB-T2 - Digital</li>\r\n	<li>Micro Dimming Ultimate</li>\r\n	<li>Quad core +</li>\r\n	<li>Instant On</li>\r\n	<li>Multi Link Screen (Dual)</li>\r\n	<li>Auto Depth Enhancer</li>\r\n	<li>Voice Control</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi Built in</li>\r\n	<li>Smart view 2.0</li>\r\n	<li>Smart hub</li>\r\n	<li>Web browser</li>\r\n	<li>Time Shift</li>\r\n	<li>Eco Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Soccer Mode (Advanced)</li>\r\n	<li>All share</li>\r\n	<li>Smart View</li>\r\n	<li>4 HDMI</li>\r\n	<li>3 USB</li>\r\n	<li>1 Digital Audio Out (Optical)</li>\r\n	<li>Contents Streaming</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Mirroring</li>\r\n	<li>Samsung SMART View</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="&nbsp;" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA55H8000ARXUM-94-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" title="&nbsp;" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>The art of the Curve, designed for immersive viewing</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="The art of the Curve, designed for immersive viewing" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA55H8000ARXUM-95-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" title="The art of the Curve, designed for immersive viewing" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">With a curved screen, your viewing experience reaches another level of immersive realism. It provides a panoramic view that wraps around you and draws you into the picture. The screen is curved at the right angle to provide the optimal viewing distance for your living room. Also, the gently curved screen gives you uniform and balanced viewing from all areas of the screen.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Curved screen elevates the feeling of depth</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Curved screen elevates the feeling of depth" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA55H8000ARXUM-62-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" title="Curved screen elevates the feeling of depth" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box;">Get ready to experience images more lifelike than ever before. With Samsung&rsquo;s Auto Depth Enhancer, your Curved Full HD TV will give you a greater feeling of depth by applying different levels of contrast enhancement on different areas of the screen, making your entertainment more immersive and enjoyable. You truly have to see it to believe it.</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box;">\r\n<h2>Curved design brings elegance and an immersive experience</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Curved design brings elegance and an immersive experience" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA55H8000ARXUM-75-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" title="Curved design brings elegance and an immersive experience" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box;">A curved design means great viewing as well as a great look. Its uniquely elegant curved design brings sophistication and style to your home, with clean and beautiful curves and subtle touches of metal taping and mood lighting. It also means more immersive viewing. It wraps around you, giving you an incredible panoramic picture that you&rsquo;ve never experienced before.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '', '', 'JCG1031', NULL, '2120211', NULL, 'visible', 305545, 290995, 1, 'samsung-ua55h8000-55-led-tv-curved-3d-smart-1000cmr.jpg', 'samsung-ua55h8000-55-led-tv-curved-3d-smart-1000cmr-2.jpg', 'samsung-ua55h8000-55-led-tv-curved-3d-smart-1000cmr-3.jpg', 'samsung-ua55h8000-55-led-tv-curved-3d-smart-1000cmr-4.jpg', 'samsung-ua55h8000-55-led-tv-curved-3d-smart-1000cmr-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-ua55h8000-55-led-tv-curved-3d-smart-1000cmr', '2017-09-13 20:26:20', '2017-09-13 20:26:20'),
(85, 7, 1, 1, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung UA55HU7200 55" LED TV - CURVED UHD, Smart', '<div class="sub-header" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Product Information</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 438.75px;">\r\n<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="background-color:transparent; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:408px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Product code</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">UA55HU7200</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Screen Size (inches)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">55</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Resolution</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">Ultra HD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Features</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">USB, HDMI, Digital tuner, Smart TV, Curved</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Display Type</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">LED</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">SKU</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">2120244</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>UHD Picture Quality</li>\r\n	<li>UHD Upscaling</li>\r\n	<li>Color Brilliance</li>\r\n	<li>UHD Dimming</li>\r\n	<li>Ultra Clear Panel</li>\r\n	<li>Wide Color Enhancer</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-Link Screen (Quad)</li>\r\n	<li>Smart Hub</li>\r\n	<li>Quad Core</li>\r\n	<li>Samsung Smart Control</li>\r\n	<li>SkypeTM Ready</li>\r\n	<li>Web Browser</li>\r\n	<li>Smart view 2.0</li>\r\n	<li>Future ready</li>\r\n	<li>Aero Design</li>\r\n	<li>Narrow Bezel</li>\r\n	<li>Soccer Mode</li>\r\n	<li>Triple Protector</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>Stunning UHD viewing with lifelike vibrant colors</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to Color Brilliance, you can see everything as nature intended. Tones are reproduced with stunning precision &ndash; just like you&rsquo;re really there. Everything you see on the screen is bright and rich. Colors come alive with beautiful intensity and images look natural and lifelike. Now you can dive into ultra-vibrant UHD viewing that is truly brilliant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung TV Vibrant colors" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA50HU7000RXUM-198854-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>UHD upscaling enhances the quality of all of your viewing</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the Samsung UHD Picture Engine, you can enjoy various kinds of content with near UHD-level picture quality, even if it&rsquo;s not from a UHD source. Samsung&rsquo;s innovative processing enhances broadcast TV shows and movies as well as video on demand and more. That means not only does it process UHD sources at crisp 4K resolution, it even converts lower-resolution content to a level of clarity that&rsquo;s almost like Ultra High Definition.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung TV UHD Upscaling" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA50HU7000RXUM-108981-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>A more detailed picture made for UHD resolution</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung&rsquo;s advanced UHD dimming technology brings the ideal level of contrast and color to your UHD viewing. The higher resolution of UHD also means that the picture requires more processing for a highly-detailed image. That&rsquo;s why Samsung UHD dimming technology has been developed to process black and white as optimally as possible and produce colors that are far more vivid.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung TV UHD Resolution" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA50HU7000RXUM-110472-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>4 times the Full HD resolution</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ultra HD viewing means you can see every intricate detail on the screen clearer than ever. Your Samsung UHD TV offers a resolution four times higher than Full HD, with accurate true-to-life color. Enjoy a picture that&rsquo;s optimized for even greater clarity and detail than you&rsquo;ve ever seen before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung TV four times the Full HD Resolution" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA50HU7000RXUM-126280-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Future Ready</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>TV technology is always evolving and so does Samsung UHD TV. With UHD Evolution Kit*, your Samsung UHD TV can be updated to be compatible with future UHD standards without buying a new TV. Get ready for future UHD standards with Future Ready*. * UHD Evolution Kit sold separately. * This feature is based on current UHD connectivity, broadcasting standards and Blu-ray standardization initiatives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung TV Future ready" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA50HU7000RXUM-76-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Great multitasking with Multi-Link Screen (Quad)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung&rsquo;s Multi-Link Screen brings your entertainment experience to a whole new level by providing multiple-screen viewing. The Multi-Link Screen (Quad) feature lets you use up to four different screens simultaneously on the UHD screen however you want. That means that you can watch live TV on one screen while on another you can browse On TV, and with the remaining two screens you can watch video clips from YouTube while searching for more things to watch. Experience the joys of having four UHD TVs in one. * Multi-Link Screen experience may vary by region or territory. * Features may vary depending on TV model&#39;s specifications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung TV great multitasking with multi-link screen quad" src="http://hotpoint.co.ke/img/cms/LED%202/UA50HU7000RXUM-252582-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '', '', 'JCG1032', NULL, '2120244', NULL, 'visible', 304495, 289995, 1, 'samsung-ua55hu7200-55-led-tv-curved-uhd-smart.jpg', 'samsung-ua55hu7200-55-led-tv-curved-uhd-smart-2.jpg', 'samsung-ua55hu7200-55-led-tv-curved-uhd-smart-3.jpg', 'samsung-ua55hu7200-55-led-tv-curved-uhd-smart-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-ua55hu7200-55-led-tv-curved-uhd-smart', '2017-09-13 20:37:36', '2017-09-13 20:37:36'),
