(87, 7, 1, 1, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung UA55MU7000 55" LED TV UHD - Smart', '<div class="sub-header" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<h2>Product Information</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-9" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 438.75px;">\r\n<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="background-color:transparent; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:408px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Product code</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">UA55MU7000AKXKE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Screen Size (inches)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">55</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Resolution</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">Ultra HD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Features</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">USB, HDMI, Digital tuner, Smart TV</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Display Type</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">LED</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">SKU</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">15102088</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>55&quot; 4K Ultra HD TV</li>\r\n	<li>Smart LED</li>\r\n	<li>UHD Up Scaling</li>\r\n	<li>UHD Dimming</li>\r\n	<li>Quad-Core Processor</li>\r\n	<li>Dolby Digital Plus</li>\r\n	<li>Web Browsing</li>\r\n	<li>Apps</li>\r\n	<li>Mirroring(TV&harr;Mobile)</li>\r\n	<li>DVB-T2* Eco Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>3 HDMI &amp; 2 USB Inputs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>INNOVATION IS IN THE DETAILS</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Innovation is in the Details" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-innovation-is-in-the-details-63553714?%24FB_TYPE_A_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Images are simulated and for illustration purposes only.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>EXTREME CONTRAST WITH HDR1000</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience the illuminating power and bold contrast of High Dynamic Range. See every single detail and enjoy cinematic clarity in every scene in almost any lighting condition.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="HDR1000/Extreme" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-hdr1000-extreme-63553676?%24FB_TYPE_A_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>* The peak brightness is up to 1000 nits and may vary depending on the model and size of the TV.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>DYNAMIC CRYSTAL COLOUR</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With over a billion shades of colours from the 10-bit panel of the Premium UHD TV, see the full spectacle of life with greater intensity and dynamic vibrancy. Prepare to be amazed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Dynamic Crystal Colour" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-dynamic-crystal-colour-61672619?%24FB_TYPE_A_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>FAST AND FURIOUS</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy smooth, fast action without the blur. Motion Rate 200 brings sports and other fast moving content to life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Fast and Furious" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-motion-rate-240-61672627?%24FB_TYPE_B_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>SEE EVERY DETAIL</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Discover captivating details with Precision Black even in the darkest scenes. Powerful contrast and local dimming technology makes scenes sharp and precise.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="See Every Detail" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-precision-black-63553692?%24FB_TYPE_C_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>CLEAN AND SIMPLE</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Maximize your TV enjoyment by cleaning up all messy cables in the back. The Clean Cable Solution and One Connect make everything neat and simple.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Clean and simple" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-clean-and-simple-63553698?%24FB_TYPE_A_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>CLEAN CABLE SOLUTION</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Keep all your wires neatly connected. The sleek design of the TV&rsquo;s back hides all connections inside.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Clean Cable Solution" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-clean-cable-solution-63553680?%24FB_TYPE_B_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>ONE CONNECT</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Connect every device* easily with One Connect. You get a clutter-free approach that enhances your viewing pleasure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Compatible devices only</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="One Connect " src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-one-connect-61672621?%24FB_TYPE_C_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>360&deg;BOUNDLESS DESIGN</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>See polished perfection from every angle. Powered on or off, 360&deg; Design blends perfectly with any room d&eacute;cor with its minimalistic bezel and clean back design. Slim and virtually bezel-less on 3 sides, it makes every scene riveting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="360Boundless Design" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-360--design-63553710?%24FB_TYPE_A_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>SMARTER THAN EVER</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Now you really can just sit back and enjoy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Smarter than ever " src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-uhd-mu7000-63560367?%24FB_TYPE_A_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Netflix streaming membership required.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>ONE REMOTE CONTROL</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Get the ultimate control in the palm of your hand. Control all connected devices1 with just one remote control. With Voice Control, you&rsquo;ll never have to flip through channels again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="One remote control" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-one-remote-control-63553684?%24FB_TYPE_A_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>1&nbsp;Compatible devices only<br />\r\n*Netflix streaming membership required</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>SMART VIEW</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Connect your mobile to the big screen and enjoy all your content. And with the Smart View app, you can seamlessly control everything from your mobile.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Smart View" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/sg-feature-smart-view-63553718?%24FB_TYPE_A_JPG%24" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Supports Android 4.1 and above, iOS 7 and above, Windows 7 and above.<br />\r\nWatch movies like Marvel Studios&rsquo; Doctor Strange, Capta