\r\n	<li>Comes With 3 Dishwasher Capsules</li>\r\n	<li>Inox Finish</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><a href="http://www.whirlpool.co.uk/appliances-1/dishwashers-3/whirlpool-supreme-clean-dishwasher-in-stainless-steel-wfc-3c24-p-x-uk/859991013890/#" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-decoration-line: none;">Technology / Features</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Innovative technology, special features and user-friendly controls for optimal cleaning and drying results, reduced cleaning effort, and ease-of-use through automatic settings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.whirlpool.co.uk/appliances-1/dishwashers-3/whirlpool-supreme-clean-dishwasher-in-stainless-steel-wfc-3c24-p-x-uk/859991013890/#" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-decoration-line: none;"><img alt="wh_hc_6thsensedish_col_14" src="http://www.whirlpool.co.uk/digitalassets/LogoAndIcon/web200/LO201410090_200.png" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.whirlpool.co.uk/appliances-1/dishwashers-3/whirlpool-supreme-clean-dishwasher-in-stainless-steel-wfc-3c24-p-x-uk/859991013890/#" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-decoration-line: none;"><img alt="wh_hc_powerclean_sq_14" src="http://www.whirlpool.co.uk/digitalassets/LogoAndIcon/web200/LO201410091_200.png" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="http://www.whirlpool.co.uk/appliances-1/dishwashers-3/whirlpool-supreme-clean-dishwasher-in-stainless-steel-wfc-3c24-p-x-uk/859991013890/#" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-decoration-line: none;"><img alt="wh_hc_startdelay_web_15" s