(345, 8, 10, 29, 2, 8, NULL, 'Bosch WAK2427SZA Washing Machine Front Load 7KG Silver', '<p><strong>Key&nbsp;Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class="short_description" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>VarioPerfect TM:&nbsp;</strong>takes 65% less time or uses 50% less energy &ndash; thanks to freely selectable program options.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Champion energy saver A+++:&nbsp;</strong>no other washer washes more efficiently.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>VarioDrum:&nbsp;</strong>especially gentle and efficient washing thanks to a unique drum structure.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>ActiveWater&trade;:&nbsp;</strong>saves water and costs thanks to a 2-step automatic load adjustment system.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>ECARF Quality Seal:&nbsp;</strong>specially developed with allergy sufferers and sensitive skin in mind.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><img alt="ANTIVIBRATION" src="http://media3.bsh-group.com/Feature_Icons/47x47/ANTIVIBRATION_A01_en-ZA.jpg" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /><img alt="VARIOPERFECT" src="http://media3.bsh-group.com/Feature_Icons/47x47/VARIOPERFECT_A01_en-ZA.jpg" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /><img alt="LABEL_WASHINGEFFICIENCYCLASSA" src="http://media3.bsh-group.com/Feature_Icons/47x47/LABEL_WASHINGEFFICIENCYCLASSA_A01_en-ZA.jpg" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /><img alt="CAPACITY1_7" src="http://media3.bsh-group.com/Feature_Icons/47x47/CAPACITY1_7_A01_en-ZA.jpg" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>7KG Front loading washing ma