(366, 8, 10, 32, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung WD18H7300KP Front Load Washer Dryer DIM 18/10KG', '<p>Samsung&nbsp;WD18H7300KP</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="short_description" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<p><strong>Product Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Washing 18Kg</li>\r\n	<li>Drying 10Kg</li>\r\n	<li>1100 Rpm</li>\r\n	<li>Transparent Crystal blue porthole design</li>\r\n	<li>Easy opening handle</li>\r\n	<li>Eco bubble technology</li>\r\n	<li>Digital inverter motor (10 years warranty)</li>\r\n	<li>5 temperature options</li>\r\n	<li>5 rinse options</li>\r\n	<li>5 spin options</li>\r\n	<li>5 dry levels</li>\r\n	<li>4 dispensing options</li>\r\n	<li>Special options &ndash; delay end, bubble shot, energy saving</li>\r\n	<li>2 Drum cleaning options &ndash; Eco drum clean and Drying drum</li>\r\n	<li>Silver finish</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>CHARACTERISTICS</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Less than 18 kg loads.&nbsp;More time &quot;for me&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A high load capacity of 18 kg (washed) and 10 kg (dry) means you can wash piles of laundry in a single load, saving you time and effort, without the hassle of frequent washing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Less than 18 kg loads.  More time &quot;for me&quot;" src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-32-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Based on bath towels 24 x 44 *.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wash and rinse piercing</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Eco Bubble &trade; technology serves to generate foam quickly activates the detergent, which removes stains more easily.&nbsp;two jets of water can also shoot to help detergent to soak the clothes before you flush waste.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Wash and rinse piercing " src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-22-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Automatically dispenses detergent</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The auto dispenser dispenses detergent and fabric softener to not have to!&nbsp;Just fill the compartment once a month *, then you will use only the correct amount of detergent per load.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Automatically dispenses detergent " src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-57-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Based on internal assessments;&nbsp;using 5 kg of laundry, normal amount of use, four times a week.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Crystal Blue Door</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A door Crystal Big Blue premium refracted lights to create a beautiful spectrum of colors and gives a stylish and sophisticated look that complements any modern interior.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Crystal Blue Door " src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-60-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Disinfects air your clothes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Air Wash technology deodorizes and disinfects clothing and bedding so you always have a scent of freshly laundered.&nbsp;By using superheated air, unpleasant odors and bacteria and allergens are removed without boiling or chemical use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Disinfects air your clothes " src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-89-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Silent washing at any time</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The technology VRT (Vibration Reduction Technology) reduces noise and vibration during washing.&nbsp;The drum bolilleros remain balanced, even at high speeds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Silent washing at any time " src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-37-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>It works intelligently.&nbsp;It keeps you young</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The digital inverter motor operates without an additional power supply and does not require carbon brushes.In this way, a guarantee of 10 years said.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="It works intelligently.  It keeps you young" src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-81-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>intelligent testing</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Checking is an intelligent automatic monitoring system errors that diagnoses problems and gives you quick solutions through an application for smartphones *.&nbsp;&iexcl;In this way, you save time and avoid unnecessary calls a technician!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="intelligent testing " src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-94-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Washing drum Eco</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The drum washing function Eco kept clean and sanitary drum, diaphragm and glass doors by using hot water and a cycle high speed.&nbsp;It is environmentally friendly and saves you money on detergents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Washing drum Eco " src="http://www.samsung.com/pe/consumer-images/product/washing-machines/2015/WD18H7300KP-PE/features/WD18H7300KP-PE-47-0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Diamond shaped drum</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The diamond-s