(390, 8, 10, 30, 2, 10, NULL, 'Whirlpool Washing Machine Front Load 8KG Silver Z.Motor ', '<p><strong>KeyFeatures:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>8kg Front Load Washing Machine</li>\r\n	<li>1200 Rpm</li>\r\n	<li>A+++ Energy Efficiency</li>\r\n	<li>6th Sense Sensor Technology</li>\r\n	<li>Sense Inverter Motor</li>\r\n	<li>Soft Move Technology</li>\r\n	<li>Fresh Care Technology</li>\r\n	<li>Premium Led Display Panel</li>\r\n	<li>Black and Silver Jog Dial</li>\r\n	<li>10 Wash Programs (Eco Cotton, Cotton, Mixed, Synthetics, Delicates, Wool, Rapid 30, Colors, Rinse+Spin, Spin)</li>\r\n	<li>3 Direct Button Options (Colors 15 Degrees, Fresh Care, Auto Dosing)</li>\r\n	<li>6 Indirect Button Options (Pre-Wash, Hot Finish, Bio Stains 15 Degrees, Heavy Soil, Intensive Rinse, Rapid)</li>\r\n	<li>3 Additional Functions (Rinse+Hold, Delay End Cycle, Child Lock)</li>\r\n	<li>Silver Finish</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:arial,sans-serif; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:407.778px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Width (cm)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">59.5</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Height (cm)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">85.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Depth (cm)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">61.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Capacity (kg)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">8</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6th Sense Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensors detect the level of soiling to adjust the cycle time and water intake for maximum performance with minimum resources.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Zen Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Zen