>Spin drying performance class</strong>&nbsp;B</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Water consumption annual (l/annum) - NEW (2010/30/EC))</strong>&nbsp;9900</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1224', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 88195, 83995, 1, 'whirlpool-washing-machine-fscr80214-front-load-8kg-silver-z-motor-free-2kg-ariel-detergent-1l-downy-softener.jpg', 'whirlpool-washing-machine-fscr80214-front-load-8kg-silver-z-motor-free-2kg-ariel-detergent-1l-downy-softener-2.jpg', 'whirlpool-washing-machine-fscr80214-front-load-8kg-silver-z-motor-free-2kg-ariel-detergent-1l-downy-softener-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'whirlpool-washing-machine-front-load-8kg-silver-z-motor', '2017-09-16 05:37:38', '2017-09-16 05:37:38'),
(391, 8, 10, 30, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Washing Machine Front Load, 9KG, Add Wash - White', '<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>9kg Add Wash Front Loader</li>\r\n	<li>1400 RPM</li>\r\n	<li>14 Wash Programs (Super Speed Wash, Super Eco Wash, Bedding, Delicates, Baby Care, Outdoor Care, Dark Garment, Cotton, Cotton Eco, Synthetics, Wool, Denim, Rinse+Spin, Eco Drum Clean)</li>\r\n	<li>3 Additional Options (Intensive, Pre-Wash, Bubble Soak)</li>\r\n	<li>Delay End Option</li>\r\n	<li>White Finish</li>\r\n	<li>Note On Add Wash Function - Can Only Be Used On Washing Programs with Temperature Of 50 Degrees And Below</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<table class="table table-condensed table-striped" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:arial,sans-serif; margin-bottom:20px; max-width:100%; width:407.778px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Width (cm)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">60.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Height (cm)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">85.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Depth (cm)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">55.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style="text-align:left; vertical-align:top">Capacity (kg)</th>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top">9</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<div class="row" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="col-sm-12" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; float: left; width: 1170px;">\r\n<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>AddWash&trade; lets you add to the wash during the wash</li>\r\n	<li>Wash cool and save energy using ecobubble&trade; technology</li>\r\n	<li>Wash an average sized load in just 59 minutes with Super Speed Wash</li>\r\n	<li>Bubble Soak guarantees intensive stain removal</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h1>Add to the wash during the Wash</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Add to the wash during the Wash  image" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww70k5410uw-eu-sec01_bg?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Add to the wash during the Wash" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww70k5410uw-eu-sec01_video_thumb?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Add to the wash during the wash</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Open the innovative AddWash&trade; door to quickly drop in anything extra during the wash* &ndash; whether that&rsquo;s a stray sock you missed, extra softener, or a hand-washed garment for final rinsing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*AddWash&trade; door can be opened at any time when the drum temperature is below 50 &deg;C.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image of a woman taking off her child\'s clothes next to a WW6500 washing machine which is in the middle of a cycle." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/uk-feature-washer-ww90k6410qw-60932509?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image showing a WW6500 stopping its cycle." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww8ak6404qw-eg-sec02_bg_02?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image showing the WW6500\'s drum, as well as icons representing items the user has forgotten to add to the wash, and rinse-only items and fabric softener  all of which can be added via the Add Door." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww8ak6404qw-eg-sec02_bg_03?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Forgotten Items" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/uk-feature-washer-ww90k6410qw-60932532?$ORIGIN_PNG$&amp;fmt=png-alpha" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" />&nbsp;<img alt="Additional softner" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/uk-feature-washer-ww90k6410qw-60932549?$ORIGIN_PNG$&amp;fmt=png-alpha" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" />&nbsp;<img alt="Rinse-only items" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/uk-feature-washer-ww90k6410qw-60932561?$ORIGIN_PNG$&amp;fmt=png-alpha" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Undeniable performance of bubbles</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our efficient ecobubble&trade; technology mixes air, water and detergent to create bubbles that penetrate your clothes faster, helping you wash at cooler temperatures. Better for the environment and your bills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Tested in accordance with IEC 60456-2010 / 4 kg Wash Load / Super Eco Wash cold (WF80F5E5U4W) vs. Cotton 40&deg; without Eco Bubble (WF0702WKU). Individual results may vary.<br />\r\n** Based on the Performance Lab Test report by Springboard Engineering on EMPA strips, between normal detergent solution and bubble technology without mechanical action.<br />\r\n*** Drum pattern may not be identical with actual product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image showing eco bubbles emerging from the drum and penetrating into the wash." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww12k8412ow-fq-c0001?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Powerful Cleaning in Less Than an Hour</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Twin Water Supply fills your machine faster, and a clever Spin Speed Rinse accelerates your cycle, cutting a standard 5 kg wash (that&#39;s 25 t-shirts) to just 59 minutes. Meaning less time waiting, more time for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><img alt="An Image showing that Super speed function" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww8ak6404qw-eg-sec05_icon_01?$ORIGIN_PNG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" />Super speed</li>\r\n	<li><img alt="An Image showing that Super spray function" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww8ak6404qw-eg-sec05_icon_02?$ORIGIN_PNG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" />Super spray</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image showing that the entire washing cycle  including washing, rinsing and drying  takes a total of 59 minutes." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww8ak6404qw-eg-sec05_bg_02?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Intensive Stain Removal</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether its cotton, synthetics or baby clothes, add a 30 minute Bubble Soak to any of your preferred programmes at the touch of a button. Then let our unique ecobubbles penetrate deep into the fabrics to loosen tough stains &ndash; giving you a thorough and efficient clean after every soak.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Tested in accordance with IEC 60456 5th edition / 8 kg Wash Load / Bubble Soak Wash (WF80F5E5U4) vs. Cotton 40 / 60&deg;, Synthetic 60&deg; and Denim 40&deg; without Bubble Soak (WF0702WKU).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image showing the inside of the machine\'s drum, as the bubble soak function removes stains from clothes." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww12k8412ow-fq-e0001?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Extraordinarily beautiful design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Crystal Gloss Door in Ocean Blue, offers the ultimate in aesthetic pleasure and can infuse your home with an ocean-like calm. The handle is also 45 degrees higher, so it opens easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image showing the WW6500\'s blue door." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww8ak6404qw-eg-sec07_bg_01?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Quiet, reliable performance</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The quiet Digital Inverter Motor gives you long-lasting, reliable performance. Less noise, less vibration and less wear and tear &ndash; it even has a 10 year warranty.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image showing the Digital Inverter ten-year warranty sticker on the front of the WW6500." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww8ak6404qw-eg-sec07_bg_02?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Support at your fingertips</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Smart Check is an automatic error-monitoring system that detects and diagnoses problems at an early stage. Using a Smartphone App*, this useful feature provides quick and easy troubleshooting solutions, saving you from the inconvenience of unnecessary engineer callouts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="An image showing a user diagnosing washing machine issues on their smartphone next to a WW6500 machine." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/global-feature-washer-ww8ak6404qw-eg-sec07_bg_04?$ORIGIN_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>* Available on Android and iOS.</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1225', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 109195, 103995, 1, 'samsung-ww90k6410qw-eu-washing-machine-