(410, 9, 16, 40, 2, 15, NULL, '"HP Pavilion X360-15.6"Core i5- 8GB RAM-1TB HDD-WIN 10 "TOUCH"', '<div><strong>Key Features</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>Screen size&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 15.6</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Resolution(Display)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1920 x 1080</div>\r\n\r\n<div>RAM&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8GB</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Hard Drive&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1000 GB</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Graphics&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Intel HD Graphics 520</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Wireless&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Yes, Bluetooth,</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Battery&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Yes</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Operating System&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Windows 10</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Brand&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;HP</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Number of Cores&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2&nbsp;cores</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>Technical Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Operating System</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Windows 10</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Processor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel Core i5-7200U (2 cores, 3 MB Level 3 cache, 2.5 GHz with Turbo Boost up to 3.5 GHz)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>15.6 inches</li>\r\n	<li>IPS, WLED backlight</li>\r\n	<li>Touchscreen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Graphics Card</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel HD Graphics 520</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1000GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>System Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>8GB Ram</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optical Drive</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Not included</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Audio</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dual stereo speakers with Bang &amp; Olufsen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inputs &amp; Controls</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Touchpad with multi-touch support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Input/Output Ports</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2 x USB 3.0</li>\r\n	<li>1 x USB 2.0</li>\r\n	<li>1 x HDMI output</li>\r\n	<li>1 x audio-in / audio-out combo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Slots</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card reader</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connectivity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dual-band 802.11a/b/g/n/ac WiFi</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>HD webcam with two microphones</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Power</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>3-cell battery</li>\r\n	<li>Battery Life: up to 8 hours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Security Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lock slot</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Silver</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;Offering a lightweight, convertible slim design, the HP X360 is ideal for work or play. It features a HD touchscreen display, Intel Core i5 7th Generation &nbsp;processor, built-in Wi-Fi, and up to nine hours of battery life per charge for longer usage.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>15.6&quot; Full multitouch screen for hands-on control</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0FDNMWNAFAMZ/fdd65fb9699d8d9c5fb2361aa8c64a6f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The high resolution boasts impressive color and clarity. Touch, tap, glide and make the most of Windows 10. IPS technology. WLED backlight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>6th Gen Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5-7200U mobile processor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for core i5" src="https://shop-media.intel.com/api/v2/helperservice/getimage?url=http://images.icecat.biz/img/gallery/28496297_3145.jpg&amp;height=550&amp;width=550" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ultra-low-voltage platform. Dual-core, four-way processing performance. Intel Turbo Boost Technology delivers dynamic extra power when you need it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8GB system memory for advanced multitasking</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Substantial high-bandwidth RAM to smoothly run your games and photo- and video-editing applications, as well as multiple programs and browser tabs all at once.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While offering less storage space than a hard drive, a flash-based SSD has no moving parts, resulting in faster start-up times and data access, no noise, and reduced heat production and power draw on the battery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>360&deg; flip-and-fold design</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0FDNMWNAFAMZ/3a587b034c91b1fc9b285420603952c8.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0FDNMWNAFAMZ/ce4e679f8e87f7f995be5405c741576e.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Offers versatile functionality with laptop, audience, tabletop, presentation and tablet modes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Intel&reg; HD Graphics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for intel hd graphics logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0FDNMWNAFAMZ/194cfa9fe47e81c4baacc5a802253ad3.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>On-processor graphics with shared video memory provide everyday image quality for Internet use, basic photo editing and casual gaming.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bluetooth interface syncs with compatible devices</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for bluetooth logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0FDNMWNAFAMZ/075aa46ef4ae7aca534218720997db7e.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wirelessly transfer photos, music and other media between the laptop and your Bluetooth-enabled cell phone or MP3 player, or connect Bluetooth wireless accessories.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Built-in HD webcam with two microphones</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for hd webcam hp logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0FDNMWNAFAMZ/f6b9d7f3e72244b3a5e62518a3dcdbb9.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Makes it easy to video chat with family and friends or teleconference with colleagues over Skype or other popular applications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1250', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 62999, 59999, 1, 'hp-pavilion-x360-15-6-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-win-10-touch.jpg', 'hp-pavilion-x360-15-6-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-win-10-touch-2.jpg', 'hp-pavilion-x360-15-6-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-win-10-touch-3.jpg', 'hp-pavilion-x360-15-6-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-win-10-touch-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'hp-pavilion-x360-15-6-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-win-10-touch', '2017-09-16 13:54:12', '2017-09-16 13:54:12'),
