(412, 9, 16, 40, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo 320 "14" - Intel - 500GB HDD - 4GB RAM Grey Color', '<p>KEY FEATURES</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Memory: 4GB RAM, 500GB HDD</li>\r\n	<li>Display Size: 14 inch LED backlit&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Graphics: Intel HD</li>\r\n	<li>Colour: Grey</li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">OS: Not Installed</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Intel Celeron N3350</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Technical Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen Size: 14&quot; HD&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Type: HD LED&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution:&nbsp;1366 x 768</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Processor:&nbsp;Intel Celeron N3350 1.1GHz processor</li>\r\n	<li>Operating System: Not Installed</li>\r\n	<li>Graphics:&nbsp;Integrated Intel&reg;&nbsp;Graphics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Memory: 4GB DDR3L</li>\r\n	<li>Harddisk:&nbsp;500GB HDD</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connectivity&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Webcam:&nbsp;0.3M Single microphone</li>\r\n	<li>Audio:&nbsp;1 x 1.5W speaker</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth&reg;</li>\r\n	<li>WiFi 802.11 b/g/n, Bluetooth&reg;&nbsp;4.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connectors</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1 x USB 3.0</li>\r\n	<li>1 x USB 2.0</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI-out</li>\r\n	<li>4-in-1 card reader</li>\r\n	<li>Audio combo jack</li>\r\n	<li>RJ-45</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Up to 4 hours with 30 WHr battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>If you don&#39;t have a ton of money to spend, but you need a solid device with a pretty but not gorgeous build, the Lenovo IdeaPad 100 is a suitable laptop. It can be upgraded to perform at a really high level, but we&#39;re not sure how much those upgrades will cost you. Proceed with cautious optimism &ndash; this could be a fantastic deal if Lenovo affordably prices the customizations.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0388KGNAFAMZ/3872e379f7016e3153f562f62541d71e.jpg" style="border:medium none; height:195px; vertical-align:top; width:300px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Full HD Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Boost of a high permance laptop with a crisp clear 15.6inch&nbsp;screen. Available in Ebony Black the Lenovo Ideapad 100 gives you the option of an HD (1366 x 768) or Full HD (1920 x 1080) display - both delivering bright, crisp visuals in 16:9 widescreen format.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Up to 15" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0388KGNAFAMZ/2f372c7fa954f265cba726ba8168afb2.jpg" style="border:medium none; vertical-align:top" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Dolby Advanced Audio</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Ideapad 100 delivers a fuller sound through Dolby Advanced Audio - for a more satisfying home entertainment experience.&nbsp;Why purchase an external optical drive? Simply select an Ideapad 100 model with an integrated DVD/CD-RW drive and you can load programs, listen to CDs, or watch movies on the go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0388KGNAFAMZ/433c7df77e952f78afbb43979c395cb8.jpg" style="border:medium none; vertical-align:top" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>AccuType Keyboard</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring a modern look and feel, the acclaimed AccuType keyboard has island-style, ergonomic keys that allow a more fluid, spacious, comfortable, and accurate typing experience than standard keyboard designs.&nbsp;Move data between the Ideapad 100 and other devices quickly with USB 3.0 SuperSpeed. Up to ten times faster than previous USB technologies, it&#39;s also backward-compatible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="AccuType Keyboard" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0388KGNAFAMZ/cec47421797b5cc096451dc5b0194500.jpg" style="border:medium none; vertical-align:top" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Ample Storage</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With up to 500GB HDD storage, you won&#39;t have to worry about where to put all your data, videos, music, or photos.&nbsp;With 802.11 a/c WiFi, you can enjoy 3x faster Internet access than the standard 802.11 b/g/n.&nbsp;The built-in webcam and microphone makes web conferences and online video chats a snap.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0388KGNAFAMZ/fa66166f79558f5f4226d89a5e0e9306.jpg" style="border:medium none; vertical-align:top" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1252', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 27299, 25999, 1, 'lenovo-ideapad-320-14-intel-n3350-500gb-hdd-4gb-ram-no-os-grey-color.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-320-14-intel-n3350-500gb-hdd-4gb-ram-no-os-grey-color-2.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-320-14-intel-n3350-500gb-hdd-4gb-ram-no-os-grey-color-3.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-320-14-intel-n3350-500gb-hdd-4gb-ram-no-os-grey-color-4.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-320-14-intel-n3350-500gb-hdd-4gb-ram-no-os-grey-color-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-320-14-intel-500gb-hdd-4gb-ram-grey-color', '2017-09-16 14:46:13', '2017-09-16 14:46:13'),
(413, 9, 17, 43, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo S510 - 4 GB RAM - 500 GB HDD - Intel Core i5-19.5" TFT', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">KEY FEATURES</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel Core i5 6100 3.7GHz Processor</li>\r\n	<li>4GB Memory, Storage 500GB 7200 RPM Hard Disk Drive, &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>DVD Recordable drive</li>\r\n	<li>Intel Integrated HD Graphics, DOS.</li>\r\n	<li>Bundled with Lenovo 19.5&quot; Monitor.</li>\r\n	<li>No Operating System</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Specifications:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Processor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Processor Brand - Intel&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Processor Name - Core i5 (6th Generation)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Processor Speed &ndash; 3.7GHz</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>RAM Size - 4 GB&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>RAM Type - DDR4&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable memory - Up to 32GB&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Memory Slot - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hard Disk Size - 500 GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System - DOS&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ports</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>USB 2.0 - 2&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>USB 3.0 - 1&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Headphone Jack - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Memory Card Reader - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Microphone Jack - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optical Disk Drive</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Optical Drive Type - DVDRw&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>The Lenovo s510 desktop computer is great for a budget, but still packs plenty of power. It&#39;s energy-efficient to minimize costs, yet features a sleek, modern look. And like all Lenovo products, it boasts plenty of great Lenovo software, preloaded.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Elegance, Efficiency, and Power" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive loading" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1KCV1KNAFAMZ/201b8c2063a81d10cbd7a6c40e82ac30.jpg" style="background:url(&quot;data:image/gif; border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" title="" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Up to 6th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; i Processor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The latest 6th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; I processor delivers 11% faster performance than the previous generation processor, and with SSD technology and DDR4 memory, you&rsquo;ll experience extraordinary productivity.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Up to Windows 10 Pro</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Windows 10 Pro is designed to empower you and your business. It allows you to do great things across your devices securely with anyone, anywhere, and at any time. Fitting a variety of budgets, it&#39;s also very easy to use. So you can get more done right from the start.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Enhanced Security</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>An array of security features such as Smart USB Protection, which restricts port access while allowing keyboard and mouse inputs,will provide you with peace of mind.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt="Green &amp; Sustainable with Fast Wireless Connectivity" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive loading" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1KCV1KNAFAMZ/754979de65467c64500e95bd674261ba.jpg" style="background-attachment:initial; background-clip:initial; background-image:url(&quot;data:image/gif; background-origin:initial; background-position:center center; background-repeat:no-repeat; background-size:initial; border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:inline; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" title="" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Green &amp; Sustainable</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The S510 has earned the green certifications of Energy Star 6.1, GREENGUARD&reg;, WEEE and more. Green certification means decreased power consumption, which translates to lower power costs for your small business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fast Wireless Connectivity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advanced WiFi design ensures reliable, seamless internet connectivity with no need for messy, disruptive cables. What&rsquo;s more, 2 front-facing USB 3.0 ports allow you to conveniently connect peripherals or transfer data.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1168', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 59849, 56999, 1, 'lenovo-s510-tower-desktop-4-gb-ram-500-gb-hdd-intel-core-i5-no-operating-system-black-color-19-5-tft.jpg', 'lenovo-s510-tower-desktop-4-gb-ram-500-gb-hdd-intel-core-i5-no-operating-system-black-color-19-5-tft-2.jpg', 'lenovo-s510-tower-desktop-4-gb-ram-500-gb-hdd-intel-core-i5-no-operating-system-black-color-19-5-tft-3.jpg', 'lenovo-s510-tower-desktop-4-gb-ram-500-gb-hdd-intel-core-i5-no-operating-system-black-color-19-5-tft-4.jpg', 'lenovo-s510-tower-desktop-4-gb-ram-500-gb-hdd-intel-core-i5-no-operating-system-black-color-19-5-tft-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-s510-4-gb-ram-500-gb-hdd-intel-core-i5-19-5-tft', '2017-09-16 15:20:34', '2017-09-16 15:20:34');
