(416, 9, 17, 45, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo S510 Desktop Tower- 4GB RAM - 500GB HDD 19.5" TFT', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size:14px">Key Features</span></strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel Core i3 6100 3.7GHz Processor</li>\r\n	<li>4GB Memory, Storage 500GB 7200 RPM Hard Disk Drive, &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>DVD Recordable drive</li>\r\n	<li>Intel Integrated HD Graphics, DOS.</li>\r\n	<li>Bundled with Lenovo 19.5&nbsp;Monitor.</li>\r\n	<li>No Operating System</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">The Desktop comes with</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lenovo tower</li>\r\n	<li>Monitor</li>\r\n	<li>Keyboard</li>\r\n	<li>Connecting cables</li>\r\n	<li>User manual</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="background-color:rgb(255, 240, 245); color:rgb(255, 51, 0)">Product Specifications:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Processor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Processor Brand - Intel&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Processor Name - Core i3 (6th Generation)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Processor Speed &ndash; 3.7GHz</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>RAM Size - 4 GB&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>RAM Type - DDR4&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable memory - Up to 32GB&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Memory Slot - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hard Disk Size - 500 GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System - DOS&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ports</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>USB 2.0 - 2&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>USB 3.0 - 1&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Headphone Jack - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Memory Card Reader - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Microphone Jack - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI - Yes&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optical Disk Drive</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Optical Drive Type - DVDRw&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>The Lenovo s510 desktop computer is great for a budget, but still packs plenty of power. It&#39;s energy-efficient to minimize costs, yet features a sleek, modern look. And like all Lenovo products, it boasts plenty of great Lenovo software, preloaded.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Elegance, Efficiency, and Power" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive loading" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0OM3GKNAFAMZ/201b8c2063a81d10cbd7a6c40e82ac30.jpg" style="background:url(&quot;data:image/gif; border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" title="" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Up to 6th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; i Processor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The latest 6th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; I processor delivers 11% faster performance than the previous generation processor, and with SSD technology and DDR4 memory, you&rsquo;ll experience extraordinary productivity.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Up to Windows 10 Pro</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Windows 10 Pro is designed to empower you and your business. It allows you to do great things across your devices securely with anyone, anywhere, and at any time. Fitting a variety of budgets, it&#39;s also very easy to use. So you can get more done right from the start.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Enhanced Security</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>An array of security features such as Smart USB Protection, which restricts port access while allowing keyboard and mouse inputs,will provide you with peace of mind.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt="Green &amp; Sustainable with Fast Wireless Connectivity" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive loading" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0OM3GKNAFAMZ/754979de65467c64500e95bd674261ba.jpg" style="background-attachment:initial; background-clip:initial; background-image:url(&quot;data:image/gif; background-origin:initial; background-position:center center; background-repeat:no-repeat; background-size:initial; border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:inline; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" title="" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Green &amp; Sustainable</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The S510 has earned the green certifications of Energy Star 6.1, GREENGUARD&reg;, WEEE and more. Green certification means decreased power consumption, which translates to lower power costs for your small business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fast Wireless Connectivity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advanced WiFi design ensures reliable, seamless internet connectivity with no need for messy, disruptive cables. What&rsquo;s more, 2 front-facing USB 3.0 ports allow you to conveniently connect peripherals or transfer data.&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1175', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 46725, 44500, 1, 'lenovo-s510-desktop-tower-4gb-ram-500gb-hdd-intel-core-i3-no-operating-system-black-19-5-tft.jpg', 'lenovo-s510-desktop-tower-4gb-ram-500gb-hdd-intel-core-i3-no-operating-system-black-19-5-tft-2.jpg', 'lenovo-s510-desktop-tower-4gb-ram-500gb-hdd-intel-core-i3-no-operating-system-black-19-5-tft-3.jpg', 'lenovo-s510-desktop-tower-4gb-ram-500gb-hdd-intel-core-i3-no-operating-system-black-19-5-tft-4.jpg', 'lenovo-s510-desktop-tower-4gb-ram-500gb-hdd-intel-core-i3-no-operating-system-black-19-5-tft-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-s510-desktop-tower-4gb-ram-500gb-hdd-19-5-tft', '2017-09-16 16:15:20', '2017-09-16 16:15:20'),
