(425, 9, 16, 40, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo 110 - 15.6" -  INTEL CORE I7, 8GBRAM, 1TB - Black', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong><br />\r\nDisplay Size: 15.6 inch<br />\r\nStorage: 1TB HDD, 8GB RAM<br />\r\nProcessor: 7th Generation Intel Core i7<br />\r\nOperating System: Windows 10 Home<br />\r\nGraphics: AMD Radeon R5 M430 2 GB(DDR3L)</p>\r\n', '<p>Product Specifications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor: 7th Generation&nbsp;<br />\r\nOperating System: Windows 10 Home<br />\r\nGraphics: AMD Radeon R5 M430 2 GB(DDR3L)<br />\r\nWebcam: 0.3 MP with Analog Microphone<br />\r\nMemory: 8 GB<br />\r\nStorage: 1 TB HDD 9.5MM 5400RPM<br />\r\nBattery: Up to 4 Hours 4Cell 32WH<br />\r\nDisplay: 15.6 HD (1366 x 768) TN GL (Slim)<br />\r\nWeight: Starting at 5.1 lbs (2.3 kg)<br />\r\nWLAN: WiFi 802.11 ac<br />\r\nBluetooth: Bluetooth 4.1<br />\r\nPorts: 1 x USB 3., 1 x USB 2.0</p>\r\n', '<p>This laptop comes with a 15.6 inch Full HD&nbsp; display delivering bright, crisp visuals in 16:9 widescreen format. What&#39;s more, The Ideapad 110 comes with Lenovo Photo Master 2.0 - a modern photo library with powerful, easy-to-use navigation and editing tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Customizable Graphics</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Strike your own balance between cost and graphical power. Choose between integrated Intel graphics or discrete, high-end AMD graphics. Discrete graphics give you a boost when it comes to getting creative with video and photo editing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>AccuType Keyboard</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lenovo Ideapad 110 featurtes a modern look and feel, the acclaimed AccuType keyboard has island-style, ergonomic keys that allow a more fluid, spacious, comfortable, and accurate typing experience than standard keyboard designs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Awesome Sound</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With Lenovo Ideapad 110 you can finally get ready for a truly satisfying home entertainment experience. Thanks to advanced Dolby technology and stereo speakers, your music and movies will sound big and loud on the Ideapad 110.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1267', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 73343, 69850, 1, 'lenovo-lenovo-ideapad-110-15-6-intel-core-i7-8gbram-1tb-win-10-black.jpg', 'lenovo-lenovo-ideapad-110-15-6-intel-core-i7-8gbram-1tb-win-10-black-2.jpg', 'lenovo-lenovo-ideapad-110-15-6-intel-core-i7-8gbram-1tb-win-10-black-3.jpg', 'lenovo-lenovo-ideapad-110-15-6-intel-core-i7-8gbram-1tb-win-10-black-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-110-15-6-intel-core-i7-8gbram-1tb-black', '2017-09-17 13:49:53', '2017-09-17 13:49:53');
