.9 (mm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="background-color:transparent; text-align:right; vertical-align:middle; width:279px">Weight</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top; width:auto">Starting at 3.42 lbs (1.55 kg)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="background-color:transparent; text-align:right; vertical-align:middle; width:279px">Colors</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top; width:auto">Silver</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="background-color:transparent; text-align:right; vertical-align:middle; width:279px">WiFi/Bluetooth<sup>&reg;</sup></td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top; width:auto">\r\n			<div style="box-sizing: border-box;">802.11 AC (1x1) WiFi + Bluetooth<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;4.1</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="background-color:transparent; text-align:right; vertical-align:middle; width:279px">Ports</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:top; width:auto">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>2x USB 3.0</li>\r\n				<li>1 X USB Type-C Thunderbolt</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<h2>Extremely thin &amp; light</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 720s is startlingly sleek. Pop it in your bag, and work or watch anywhere. It&rsquo;ll never weigh you down.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Sleek new design with aluminum finish</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Treated with the same technique used to shape and polish diamonds, the IdeaPad 720s has been redesigned with premium details and angled edges to look even thinner than it already is.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem right" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-IdeaPad-720s-13-feature-1.jpg?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8MTQ5MzV8aW1hZ2UvanBnfGhiMy9oMDMvOTQ0MzA4Nzc3NzgyMi5qcGd8MDU4ZDk5Mzk3YjQ1NTY2OTQyY2Y0NmQzOTUyY2EwYTg5NTdjNjcxMGRhNDc3MTI1M2ZmZTkxZGIzZTMzMTFiZQ" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper right">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Stay moving with long battery life &amp; always-on charging</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>With up to 14 hours of battery life*, you&rsquo;ll be able to stay moving all day. The IdeaPad 720s also features always-on charging, so you&rsquo;ll be able to charge other devices via USB port even when your laptop&rsquo;s powered off. You&rsquo;ll never feel anchored to an outlet. *MobileMark 2014</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Powerful performance to get things done</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 720s offers 7th generation Intel Core i7 processing and additional high-performance PCIe SSD storage. Download movies, store photos and videos, and more. And with up to 8GB memory, you&rsquo;ll be able to multi-task with ease and speed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem left" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-IdeaPad-720s-13-feature-2.jpg?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NTA5NDJ8aW1hZ2UvanBnfGg2Yi9oOTQvOTQ0MzA4NzcxMjI4Ni5qcGd8NWNiODI1ZmZiNzc4NmJlZTczODU5MmEwYzQ0OTgyMjZlYzJjM2ZlNGJiNzA3ZDczMGJlMDczZGMzZWMxNDczZA" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Advanced graphics performance with NVIDIA</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 720s is designed to keep up with your entertainment and productivity needs. Whether you&rsquo;re gaming, creating or editing content, your IdeaPad 720s has you covered.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Truly immersive audio</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring JBL Premium Audio speakers, the IdeaPad 720s offers Dolby Audio for loud, clear audio that renders detail across a wide range of sounds at any volume.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem right" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-IdeaPad-720s-13-feature-4.jpg?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NjI1MTR8aW1hZ2UvanBnfGg5Mi9oOTkvOTQ0MzA4NzkwODg5NC5qcGd8OWQzOTdkYWEzN2M1YjgxZTdiNjU2NmMxZjkzMGYzMjI1ZDgyZjdhNzBkZjA0YWM4YTZhNzBhOWMwZWZhNjg2Mg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper right">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Swift, secure login with fingerprint reader</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Streamline your day with Windows Hello, which works with an optional fingerprint reader to ensure safe, secure login in less than two seconds&mdash;that&rsquo;s three times faster than the average time it takes to type in a password. You&rsquo;ll also be able to sign into various partner apps like DropBox, with just one touch of your finger. That&rsquo;s one less thing to worry about.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The world&rsquo;s fastest port</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 720s comes with a Thunderbolt&trade; 3 USB-C port&mdash;the revolutionary connection technology supporting high-res displays, high-performance data devices and fast charging. Hook up your laptop to multiple displays*, then sync and backup at up to 40 Gbps&mdash;eight times the speed of USB 3.0! Now you can capture and edit multiple video streams in real time, or daisy-chain other devices to simplify your workflow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>*Connecting to a display requires a USB-C to HDMI or DisplayPort cable, depending on display interface. Connecting up to 2 displays requires compatible hub/extenders.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem left" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;">\r\n<p><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-IdeaPad-720s-13-feature-5.jpg?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8Njc4OTZ8aW1hZ2UvanBnfGhkYy9oZDkvOTQ0MzA4Nzg0MzM1OC5qcGd8MDlmOTIyNWY1ZDhhMmJkMTU3ZjJiMzYwNDk5N2E5YTk0NTU5NTUyNGI2ZWIyY2ExY2NjYjgwZWUyMDExNDIxNQ" style="background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255); border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(85, 85, 85); display:inline; font-family:lato,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:16px; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1268', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 132299, 125999, 1, 'ideapad-720s-laptop-14.jpg', 'ideapad-720s-laptop-14-2.jpg', 'ideapad-720s-laptop-14-3.jpg', 'ideapad-720s-laptop-14-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'ideapad-720s-laptop-14', '2017-09-17 14:13:54', '2017-09-17 14:13:54'),
(428, 9, 17, 43, 1, 14, NULL, 'Dell Vostro -3900 - Desktop Tower -color -Black + Monitor', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size:14px">Key Features</span></strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel&reg; H81 Chipset</li>\r\n	<li>500GB - 2.0TB 7200RPM SATA Hard Drive</li>\r\n	<li>Internal 300 Watt Power Supply (PFC, EPA)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chipset</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel&reg; H81 Chipset</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optical Drive</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>16X CD/DVD burner (DVD+/-RW) with double layer write capability</li>\r\n	<li>16X DVD-ROM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connectivity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Integrated Giga bit 10/100/1000 Ethernet</li>\r\n	<li>Optional Dell Wireless card (DW1540), 2x2, 802.11abgn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Security</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>McAFee</li>\r\n	<li>Optional Hard Drive Protection SW Solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Physical security &ndash; Cable lock chassis security slot and padlock loop</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ports</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Front : (2) USB 2.0, MCR 19:1 (optional) Mic and Headphone Jacks</li>\r\n	<li>Rear : (2) USB 3.0, (2) USB 2.0, (2) PS2, HDMI, VGA, RJ-45 (10/100/1000 Ethernet)</li>\r\n	<li>3-stack audio jacks supporting 5.1 surround sound</li>\r\n	<li>Media Card Reader : 19-in-1 media card reader (optional)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Slots</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2 DIMM slots , PCIe x1: 2 Slots, PCIe x16 (Graphics): 1 Slot, PCI: 1 Slot</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Chassis</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bays : 3.5&quot; Bays: 2 internal; 5.25&quot; Bays: 2 external bays</li>\r\n	<li>Line Voltage : PFC - 180-264V/4.5A, 47-63HZ ; EPA - 90-264V/ 8A, 47-63HZ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>500GB - 2.0TB 7200RPM SATA Hard Drive</li>\r\n	<li>Dual drives</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Power</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal 300 Watt Power Supply (PFC, EPA)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>Next-generation performance</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Put real power behind your everyday tasks</strong>, from video conferencing to creating presentations, with up to a 4th Gen Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7 processor.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Multitask effortlessly</strong>&nbsp;and take advantage of the latest productivity tools with up to&nbsp;<br />\r\nWindows 8.1 Pro.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Boost graphics performance</strong>&nbsp;with integrated Intel&reg; HD Graphics, or step up to NVIDIA or AMD graphics options with 1GB memory*.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Dependable, hassle-free design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Count on long-term performance</strong>&nbsp;from a tested and proven design with a mean time between failure (MTBF) rate of 500,000 hours.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Conveniently connect your devices and media</strong>&nbsp;with six USB ports, an optional optical drive and a 19-in-1 media card reader.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Ready for today and tomorrow</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Support a wide range of devices and legacy peripherals</strong><span style="color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:roboto,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px">&nbsp;with options that include a DVI port, parallel or serial card, PCI slot and two PS2 ports.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Easily upgrade to a high-end graphics card</strong><span style="color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:roboto,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px">&nbsp;with expansion slots and a robust 300W power supply.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Add storage space as needed</strong><span style="color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:roboto,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px">, thanks to an expandable design that supports up to two 2TB hard drives</span>*<span style="color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:roboto,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px">&nbsp;and 16GB memory</span><span style="color:rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family:roboto,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:14px">.</span></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1184', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 61480, 58000, 1, 'dell-vostro-3900-desktop-tower-color-black-monitor.jpg', 'dell-vostro-3900-desktop-tower-color-black-monitor-2.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'dell-vostro-3900-desktop-tower-color-black-monitor', '2017-09-17 14:27:31', '2017-09-17 14:27:31'),
(429, 9, 16, 40, 2, 19, NULL, 'IdeaPad 710S Plus Touch (13")', '<div><strong>Key Features</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>Processor Up to 7th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7-7500U Processor (2.70GHz 4MB)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Operating System : Windows 10 Home</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Graphics&nbsp; : Up to Intel&reg; HD Graphics 620Up to NVIDIA&reg; GeForce&reg; GT 940MX 2GB</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Webcam / Microphone&nbsp; : 720p with Single Microphone</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Memory :&nbsp; Up to 8GB DDR4 2400 MHz (Onboard)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Storage&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;Up to 512GB PCIe SSD</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<div class="tabbedBrowse-module tab-content tab-gen" id="tab-tech_specs" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1116px; float: left; padding: 2em; outline: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Lato, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-other" style="box-sizing: border-box;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-wrapper" style="box-sizing: border-box; background: transparent; padding: 0px;">\r\n<div class="techSpecs-wrapper" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: inherit;">\r\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div>Processor : Up to 7th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7-7500U Processor (2.70GHz 4MB)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Operating System : Windows 10 Home</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Graphics:&nbsp; Up to Intel&reg; HD Graphics 620 Up to NVIDIA&reg; GeForce&reg; GT 940MX 2GB</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Webcam / Microphone : 720p with Single Microphone</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Memory: Up to 8GB DDR4 2400 MHz (Onboard)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Storage :Up to 512GB PCIe SSD</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Audio :2 x JBL&reg; Certified Stereo SpeakersDolby Audio&trade; Premium</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Battery:&nbsp; Up to 7 Hours</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Display: 13.3&quot; FHD (1920 x 1080) IPS Anti-Glare Multitouch with integrated camera</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Dimensions : (W x D x H) 12.16&quot; x 8.66&quot; x 0.58&quot; / 309 x 220 x 14.8 mm</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Weight: Starting at 2.6 lbs (1.179 kg)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Colors:Platinum Silver</div>\r\n\r\n<div>WiFi : 802.11 AC (2x2)Bluetooth&reg; Bluetooth&reg; 4.0</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Ports :&nbsp; 1 x USB-C (DisplayPort&trade;)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1 x USB 3.0 (always-on charging)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1 x USB 2.0</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Audio Combo Jack : 4-in-1 Card Reader (SD, SDHC, SDXC, MMC)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2><span style="font-family:lato,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:36px">Features</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-other" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Lato, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-wrapper tabbedBrowse-wrapper" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: visible; background: transparent; padding: 0px; position: relative;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>Do Great Things with Windows 10&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>Combining the best of Windows you already know, Windows 10 Home has many great improvements you&rsquo;ll love. From fast start-ups to the expanded Start menu, and an all-new browser, to Cortana&mdash;your very own digital personal assistant. Now, even across multiple devices, you can get more things done, more quickly, more smoothly.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-windows-10-1.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8MTIzNTA0fGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoYTEvaDAwLzk0NDg5NzAyMjM2NDYucG5nfDhkY2FhMDhiNjA1YmM2NTk3ZTdlZTZlOTZjOGQ2NzcyNmQ5MDcyMmMyZjllODk1Mzk1MTNiNmM5ZjE2Y2VhODY" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<h2>Cutting-Edge Design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With its 0.2 in (5 mm) narrow bezel, the IdeaPad 710S Plus is 50% thinner than many other laptops&mdash;offering head-turning style to match jaw-dropping performance.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Crystal-Clear Display</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 710S Plus&#39;s high-resolution 13.3&quot; screen delivers surperb detail, color, and clarity. For high-definition movies and extreme gaming, the optional NVIDIA discrete graphics card guarantees a more intense viewing experience.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-display-graphics-silver-2.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8MjEzNTY0fGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoYjgvaDc4Lzk0MDE3ODkwODc3NzQucG5nfDkyYThiN2FkMGFhZTNkMDU2Yjc4MGU3ODQ2ODBlY2YxYWIwNDA3ZTU0YjBmMDk1YzAwMzYyMjAwZmJlOWQwMWY" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>Fast Security at Your Fingertips</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 710S Plus comes with an extra layer of convenience and security. Instead of remembering a cumbersome password, simply swipe your finger across the built-in fingerprint reader to unlock your laptop. You can even set the reader up to allow multiple users to log in to their personal accounts.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-fingerprint-reader-silver-3.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8Mjk5MTE5fGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoNjIvaGFkLzk0MDE3ODkxODYwNzgucG5nfGE0ZDE5NTE0ZTk4ZjcxMTcxZTQwYTBkMWZlZmE3ZDAxYTU2OWNlOTRjOTZiN2NlOTU4ZDk2MjE1MDQ0N2VhZDM" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>Ready for an Always-On Lifestyle</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>This thin and lightweight laptop is always ready for anything, anywhere with up to 7 hours of battery life. Plus, with USB always-on charging, you can even charge other devices even when your laptop is in sleep mode.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Advanced SSD Technology</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>A new kind of solid state drive (SSD) technology, PCIe SSD &nbsp;promises faster read/write times compared to older SSDs. Now, you can load multiple programs and large files in a snap.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-thin-ssd-4.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8MjEzMzJ8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGg1Yi9oYmEvOTI4NjMxNzk2NTM0Mi5wbmd8MTA4ODE2ZTAyN2FiNzIxMzRmNjgzMmUxNGU2NmY3MzhkMzQwYzQyMjkwMDI3MDI0NDc0MmU2NGEwM2EzOTA0ZA" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>Blazing-Fast Internet</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>Thanks to the lightning-fast 802.11ac connection, you can stream&nbsp;media much&nbsp;faster than previous technology&mdash;so you can watch your favorite online videos, upload photos on social media, or just enjoy listening to your favorite music without buffering.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Superior Stereo Sound</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>With built-in JBL stereo speakers and Dolby Audio&trade; Premium, you can expect an awesome sound experience. It&#39;s like having a personal home theater built into your IdeaPad 710S Plus.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;">\r\n<p><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-sound-silver-5.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8Mjg5MzIxfGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoOTYvaDM2Lzk0MDE3ODkyODQzODIucG5nfGE0OTQ2MDI2Nzg3ODljOTc1YjhjNDc5NTk2ZTY4NzAyOGY5MTgzN2JmYzgzMDZhNmM1MDVjYzkzZmRjMWM3OWI" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Lato, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1269', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 127049, 120999, 1, 'ideapad-710s-plus-touch-13.jpg', 'ideapad-710s-plus-touch-13-2.jpg', 'ideapad-710s-plus-touch-13-3.jpg', 'ideapad-710s-plus-touch-13-4.jpg', 'ideapad-710s-plus-touch-13-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'ideapad-710s-plus-touch-13', '2017-09-17 14:29:29', '2017-09-17 14:29:29');
