(430, 9, 16, 40, 2, 19, NULL, 'IdeaPad 710S Plus (13")', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Up to 7th Gen Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7 processor</li>\r\n	<li>Windows 10 Home</li>\r\n	<li>13.3&quot; FHD (1920x1080) IPS Anti-Glare display with integrated camera</li>\r\n	<li>Up to 16 GB DDR4 memory</li>\r\n	<li>Up to 512 GB SSD storage</li>\r\n	<li>No Optical Disc Drive</li>\r\n	<li>Up to Intel&reg; HD 620 graphics</li>\r\n	<li>802.11 AC (2x2) WiFi + Bluetooth&reg; 4.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div>Processor :Up to 7th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7-7500U Processor (2.70GHz 4MB)&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Operating System&nbsp; :Windows 10 Home</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Graphics :Up to Intel&reg; HD Graphics 620</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Webcam/Microphone : 720p with Single Microphone</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Memory :Up to 16GB DDR4 2400 MHz (Onboard)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Storage: Up to 512GB PCIe SSD</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Audio:&nbsp;2 x JBL&reg; Certified Stereo Speakers Dolby Audio&trade; Premium</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Battery: Up to 7 Hours</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Display: 13.3&quot; FHD (1920 x 1080) IPS Anti-Glare with integrated camera</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Dimensions: (W x D x H) 12.16&quot; x 8.66&quot; x 0.58&quot; / 309 x 220 x 14.8 (mm)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Weight: Starting at 2.6 lbs (1.18 kg)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Colors: Silver</div>\r\n\r\n<div>WiFi : 802.11 AC (2x2) WiFi</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Bluetooth&reg; :&nbsp;&nbsp;Bluetooth&reg; 4.1</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Ports&nbsp; :&nbsp;1 x USB-C (DisplayPort&trade;)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1 x USB 3.0 (always-on charging)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1 x USB 2.0</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Audio Combo Jack</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4-in-1 Card Reader (SD, SDHC, SDXC, MMC)</div>\r\n', '<h2><span style="font-family:lato,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:36px">Features</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<div