e: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<h2>Cutting-Edge Design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With its 0.2 in (5 mm) narrow bezel, the IdeaPad 710S Plus is 50% thinner than many other laptops&mdash;offering head-turning style to match jaw-dropping performance.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Crystal-Clear Display</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 710S Plus&#39;s high-resolution 13.3&quot; screen delivers surperb detail, color, and clarity. For high-definition movies and extreme gaming, the optional NVIDIA discrete graphics card guarantees a more intense viewing experience.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-display-graphics-silver-2.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8MjEzNTY0fGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoYjgvaDc4Lzk0MDE3ODkwODc3NzQucG5nfDkyYThiN2FkMGFhZTNkMDU2Yjc4MGU3ODQ2ODBlY2YxYWIwNDA3ZTU0YjBmMDk1YzAwMzYyMjAwZmJlOWQwMWY" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>Fast Security at Your Fingertips</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 710S Plus comes with an extra layer of convenience and security. Instead of remembering a cumbersome password, simply swipe your finger across the built-in fingerprint reader to unlock your laptop. You can even set the reader up to allow multiple users to log in to their personal accounts.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-fingerprint-reader-silver-3.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8Mjk5MTE5fGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoNjIvaGFkLzk0MDE3ODkxODYwNzgucG5nfGE0ZDE5NTE0ZTk4ZjcxMTcxZTQwYTBkMWZlZmE3ZDAxYTU2OWNlOTRjOTZiN2NlOTU4ZDk2MjE1MDQ0N2VhZDM" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>Ready for an Always-On Lifestyle</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>This thin and lightweight laptop is always ready for anything, anywhere with up to 7 hours of battery life. Plus, with USB always-on charging, you can even charge other devices even when your laptop is in sleep mode.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Advanced SSD Technology</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>A new kind of solid state drive (SSD) technology, PCIe SSD &nbsp;promises faster read/write times compared to older SSDs. Now, you can load multiple programs and large files in a snap.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-thin-ssd-4.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8MjEzMzJ8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGg1Yi9oYmEvOTI4NjMxNzk2NTM0Mi5wbmd8MTA4ODE2ZTAyN2FiNzIxMzRmNjgzMmUxNGU2NmY3MzhkMzQwYzQyMjkwMDI3MDI0NDc0MmU2NGEwM2EzOTA0ZA" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>Blazing-Fast Internet</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>Thanks to the lightning-fast 802.11ac connection, you can stream&nbsp;media much&nbsp;faster than previous technology&mdash;so you can watch your favorite online videos, upload photos on social media, or just enjoy listening to your favorite music without buffering.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Superior Stereo Sound</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>With built-in JBL stereo speakers and Dolby Audio&trade; Premium, you can expect an awesome sound experience. It&#39;s like having a personal home theater built into your IdeaPad 710S Plus.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;">\r\n<p><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710splus-13-sound-silver-5.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8Mjg5MzIxfGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoOTYvaDM2Lzk0MDE3ODkyODQzODIucG5nfGE0OTQ2MDI2Nzg3ODljOTc1YjhjNDc5NTk2ZTY4NzAyOGY5MTgzN2JmYzgzMDZhNmM1MDVjYzkzZmRjMWM3OWI" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1270', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 148049, 140999, 1, 'ideapad-710s-plus-13.jpg', 'ideapad-710s-plus-13-2.jpg', 'ideapad-710s-plus-13-3.jpg', 'ideapad-710s-plus-13-4.jpg', 'ideapad-710s-plus-13-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'ideapad-710s-plus-13', '2017-09-17 14:46:42', '2017-09-17 14:46:42'),
