(432, 9, 16, 40, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo Ideapad 710S (13")', '<ul>\r\n	<li>7th Gen Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5 processor</li>\r\n	<li>Windows 10 Home</li>\r\n	<li>13.3&quot; FHD (1920x1080) IPS Anti-Glare display with integrated camera</li>\r\n	<li>8 GB LPDDR3 memory</li>\r\n	<li>256 GB SSD storage</li>\r\n	<li>Intel&reg; HD 620 graphics</li>\r\n	<li>802.11 AC (2x2) WiFi + Bluetooth&reg; 4.0</li>\r\n	<li>2 x USB 3.0 (1 with always-on charging), HDMI-out, 4-in-1 card reader (SD, MMC, SDHC, SDXC), audio combo jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div>Processor&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;7th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5-7200U Processor (2.50GHz 3MB)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Operating System&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Windows 10 Home</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Graphics&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Intel&reg; HD Graphics 620</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Memory&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 8GB LPDDR3 1866 MHz (Onboard)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Webcam&nbsp; &nbsp; 720pStorage 256GB PCIe SSD</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Audio&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; JBL&reg; Stereo Speakers with Dolby&reg; Audio Premium</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Battery&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Up to 8 Hours Local Video Playback</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Display&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 13.3&quot; FHD (1920 x 1080) IPS Anti-Glare with integrated camera</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Dimensions&nbsp; &nbsp; (W x D x H) 12.09&quot; x 8.42&quot; x 0.55&quot; / 307 x 214 x 13.9 (mm)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Weight&nbsp; &nbsp;2.56 lbs (1.16 kg)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>WiFi&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;802.11 AC (2x2) WiFi + Bluetooth&reg; 4.0</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Connectors&nbsp; &nbsp;2 x USB 3.0 (1 x always-on charging)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4-in-1 Card Reader (SD, SDHC, SDXC, MMC)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Audio Combo Jack</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Micro HDMI&trade;-out</div>\r\n', '<div class="mediaGallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: visible; width: 1180px; padding: 0px; position: relative; margin: 1em 0px 0px; float: left; text-align: center; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Lato, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">\r\n<p>ULTRA-PORTABLE. TOP-NOTCH PERFORMANCE. NO COMPROMISE.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbed-browse-content-wrapper " style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1180px; float: left; clear: both; position: relative; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Lato, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1180px;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-module tab-content" id="tab-features" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1180px; float: left; padding: 2em; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px;">\r\n<h2><span style="font-family:lato,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:36px">Features</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-other" style="box-sizing: border-box;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-wrapper tabbedBrowse-wrapper" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: visible; background: transparent; padding: 0px; position: relative;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>No-Compromise Performance</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>PC performance has never been faster. Intel&reg; 7th Gen Core&trade; i processors will take your productivity and entertainment to the next level. Boot up and access your applications more quickly with PCIe solid-state drives that provide faster data access and increased data stability compared to traditional hard drives. They also give you better battery life with up to 8 hours of video playback. And with Windows 10 you&#39;ll get the best combination of the Windows you already know, plus lots of great improvements you&rsquo;ll love.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Accelerate Productivity</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Multitasking is no problem with the Ideapad 710S. It can support up to 16GB of memory to make sure all your applications keep up with you. Build images, edit video, or run other graphic intensive programs with the optional Intel&reg; Iris&trade; graphics card. It renders graphics more efficiently-separately from the CPU- giving you a more visually remarkable, more fluid and more enjoyable experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-710s-13-windows-10-home-1.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8MTY5NzcxfGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoOTIvaGU1Lzk0NDg5NzAwOTI1NzQucG5nfGY0ZTM5Y2Y5NmYyMDllMGZkMTE1NWNmZGUyMzM3YzEzNzhmNTllMzJhOWFhMjg1YzFmMWI1OTRmM2U5ZTI5ODY" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">Designed for Work, Rest, &amp; Play</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Eye-Catching Display</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>With its 13.3&quot; Full HD (1920 x 1080) IPS display, the Ideapad 710S gives you bright, sharp visuals. But what will really catch your eye is the extremely narrow .2&quot; thin bezel - almost 50% thinner than most laptops of its class - providing an almost seamless viewing area.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Stylish Details</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>From the magnesium-aluminum casing to the diamond-cut touchpad, the Ideapad 710S looks and feels like the premium laptop it is designed to be. The backlit keyboard and the 180-degree hinge add flexibility to a powerful, sophisticated, and beautiful machine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/710S-FeatureImage2.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NDY5ODJ8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGgzMi9oOTEvOTI1MjQ1ODk1NDc4Mi5wbmd8OTgwNzQ4OTU1NDM0NDU3ZjY5NmVkNTJiYTgxOTVkNTdjZmEzZDU1NjliMzMzNWM3OWJjODE0NmM2YTgyNDQ3Mw" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">Vibrant Display with Ultrathin Bezel</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Supercharged Audio</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The Ideapad 710S delivers an immersive cinema experience with the thrill of live performance. Its built-in JBL&reg; stereo speakers combine to give you the full-impact of surround sound, anywhere.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Super-Fast Connectivity</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Accessing the internet and connecting to other devices is almost seamless with 802.11 a/c WiFi and Bluetooth&reg; 4.0 technology. In fact, 802.11 a/c WiFi gives you three times the connection speeds of 802.11 b/g/n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/710S-FeatureImage3.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8OTM0OTB8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGhlOS9oZDkvOTI1MjQ1OTA1MzA4Ni5wbmd8MmE2NGY2YjA4OWY3NmNjZmMzOWQ5ODhiZTMzNTYxMzM5ZWI2NDBhOWZlNjIwM2ZhYTM0MmJiZTE3NzYxZTUwNg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">Surround Sound and Seamless WiFi</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper ">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Smile, Swap, and Sort&mdash;In Seconds</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The Ideapad 710S comes with Lenovo&reg; Photo Master 2.0: a modern photo library with powerful, easy-to-use navigation and editing tools. With features such as Auto Face Swap and Smart Event Sort, you can quickly organize and optimize your photos to perfection.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>McAfee LiveSafe&reg; Free Trial</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Keep your entire digital life secure with the comprehensive protection afforded by McAfee LiveSafe software. LiveSafe protects cross-device, through the cloud, and locally to ensure total security for your data and identity. Enjoy a free 30-day trial with purchase. Or, upgrade to the full version during the purchase process and enjoy peace-of-mind security from day one.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem " style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/710S-FeatureImage4.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NzM0NjV8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGgxZC9oNjMvOTI1MjQ1OTE1MTM5MC5wbmd8YWE0YzY1MTA4ZGI4MTM3NTJhNzNhMjlkOTU4MzUwMTMyYTk3OGJjMTY4ZTE2ZDU5MGFjMmE3Nzk2ODZiZjIwYg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">Photo Editing Tools and Library</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1271', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 137549, 130999, 1, 'lenovo-ideapad-710s-13.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-710s-13-2.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-710s-13-3.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-710s-13-4.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-710s-13-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-ideapad-710s-13', '2017-09-17 15:06:44', '2017-09-17 15:06:44'),
(433, 9, 17, 43, 2, 13, NULL, ' Apple iMac  21.5 inch  - 2.8GHz  - 8GB RAM - 1TB HDD-sliver', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size:14px">Key Features</span></strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>21.5-inch LED-backlit IPS Display, 1920 x 1080 Resolution</li>\r\n	<li>2.8GHz quad-core Intel Core i5,&nbsp;Turbo Boost up to 3.3GHz</li>\r\n	<li>8GB RAM (Configurable to 16GB)</li>\r\n	<li>1TB (5400-rpm) Hard Drive</li>\r\n	<li>Intel Iris Pro Graphics 6200</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">The computer comes with:</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>iMac</li>\r\n	<li>Apple Magic Keyboard</li>\r\n	<li>Apple Magic Mouse 2</li>\r\n	<li>Power cord</li>\r\n	<li>Lightning to USB cable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#ff0000"><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Product specifications</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Size -&nbsp;21.5-inch (diagonal)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Type -&nbsp;LED-backlit display with IPS technology</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution -1920 x1080 pixels with support for millions of colors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Processor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel&nbsp;Core&nbsp;i5 dual-core</li>\r\n	<li>2.8GHz (Turbo Boost up to 3.3GHz)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Operating System</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mac&nbsp;OS Sierra</li>\r\n	<li>Apps includes: Photos, iMovie, GarageBand, Pages, Numbers, Keynote, Safari, Mail, Messages, FaceTime, Calendar, Notes, App Store, iTunes, iBooks, Maps, Contacts, Reminders</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>8GB of 1867MHz LPDDR3 onboard memory</li>\r\n	<li>Configurable to 16GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1TB (5400-rpm) hard drive</li>\r\n	<li>Configurable up to 2TB Fusion Drive, or 256GB of flash storage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Graphics</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel Iris Pro Graphics 6200</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Video&nbsp;Support and&nbsp;Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>FaceTime HD camera</li>\r\n	<li>Simultaneously supports full native resolution on the built-in display and up to 4096 by 2304 pixels on an external display.</li>\r\n	<li>Support for extended desktop and video mirroring modes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Audio</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Stereo speakers</li>\r\n	<li>Dual microphones</li>\r\n	<li>3.5 mm headphone jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connections and&nbsp;Expansion</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Four USB 3 ports (compatible with USB&nbsp;2)</li>\r\n	<li>3.5 mm headphone jack</li>\r\n	<li>SDXC card slot</li>\r\n	<li>Two Thunderbolt 2 ports (Mini DisplayPort output,&nbsp;Support for HDMI, DVI, VGA, and dual-link DVI)(adapters sold separately)</li>\r\n	<li>10/100/1000BASE-T Gigabit Ethernet (RJ-45 connector)</li>\r\n	<li>Kensington lock slot</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wireless</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi:&nbsp;802.11ac Wi-Fi wireless networking,&nbsp;IEEE 802.11a/b/g/n compatible</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth 4.0 wireless technology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Input</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Magic Keyboard</li>\r\n	<li>Magic Mouse 2</li>\r\n	<li>Magic Trackpad 2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Power Requirements</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Line voltage:&nbsp;100&ndash;240V AC</li>\r\n	<li>Frequency:&nbsp;50Hz to 60Hz, single phase</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>The 21.5 inch<strong>&nbsp;</strong>Apple iMac&nbsp;MK442/A&nbsp;has a stunningly thin design, brilliant display, and is great for browsing the web, watching movies, and doing amazing things with documents, photos, and videos. With fifth-generation Intel Core processor, high-performance Intel Iris Pro Graphics 6200&nbsp;technology,&nbsp;faster, bigger&nbsp;storage, 802.11ac Wi-Fi, and latest&nbsp;OS Sierra, the 21.5-inch iMac delivers the ultimate desktop experience&mdash;without taking up a lot of space on your desktop.&nbsp;&nbsp;Superb display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pixel by pixel, this new iMac with the latest retina technology is a masterpiece.&nbsp;A beautiful, impossibly thin display of color and contrast &mdash; and zero&nbsp;compromise,&nbsp;lets you&nbsp;see everything with pinpoint accuracy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://www.jumia.co.ke/src" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/AP044EL08JRS8NAFAMZ/2300a890f136dfbdbdea219a585ac659.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:14px"><strong>Super Thin Enclosure</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The iMac is just 5mm thin at its edge, just the right size to do something big. This does not only mean that it is beautiful but also takes a fraction of your space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size:14px">Incredible Power and Technology</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inside the incredibly thin enclosure, the iMac packs incredible power and technology.&nbsp;With powerful Intel Core i5 processor, super-fast graphics, four fast USB 3.0 ports, Thunderbolt I/O and enormous storage capacity, the&nbsp;iMac can do it all.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1187', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 204014, 194299, 1, 'apple-imac-mk442b-a-21-5-inch-mac-os-sierra-2-8ghz-quad-core-intel-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-color-sliver.jpg', 'apple-imac-mk442b-a-21-5-inch-mac-os-sierra-2-8ghz-quad-core-intel-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-color-sliver-2.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'apple-imac-21-5-inch-2-8ghz-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-sliver', '2017-09-17 15:26:14', '2017-09-17 15:26:14'),
(434, 9, 16, 40, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo  IdeaPad 520 (15") ', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Up to 7th Gen Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7 processor</li>\r\n	<li>Windows 10 Home</li>\r\n	<li>15.6&quot; FHD (1920x1080) IPS LED Anti-Glare display with integrated camera</li>\r\n	<li>Up to 12 GB DDR4 memory</li>\r\n	<li>Up to 1 TB HDD storage</li>\r\n	<li>Up to NVIDIA&reg; GeForce&reg; GT 940MX 4 GB graphics or Intel&reg; HD 620 graphics</li>\r\n	<li>Up to five hours&#39; battery life with MobileMark 2014</li>\r\n	<li>802.11 AC (1x1) WiFi + Bluetooth&reg; 4.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div><span style="font-size:14px"><strong>Specifications</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<div>Processor : Up to 7th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7-7500U Processor (2.70GHz 4MB)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Operating System : Windows 10 Home</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Graphics&nbsp; :Up to Intel&reg; HD Graphics 620 Up to NVIDIA&reg; GeForce&reg; GT 940MX 4GB</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Webcam / Microphone&nbsp; :720 HD with array microphone</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Memory&nbsp; :Up to 12GB DDR4 2133 MHz</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Storage : Up to 1TB 5400 RPM</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Audio : Harman speakers with Dolby Audio</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Battery : **Up to 5 hours with MobileMark 2014</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Display : 15.6&quot; FHD (1920 x 1080) IPS LED Anti-Glare</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Dimensions&nbsp; : (W x D x H) 14.89&quot; x 10.2&quot; x .90&quot; / 378 x 260 x 22.9 (mm)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Weight : Starting at 4.8 lbs (2.17 kg)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Colors : Iron Grey</div>\r\n\r\n<div>WiFi/Bluetooth&reg;&nbsp; &nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;802.11 AC (1x1) WiFi + Bluetooth&reg; 4.1</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<h2><span style="font-family:lato,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:36px">Features</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-other" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Lato, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-wrapper tabbedBrowse-wrapper" style="box-sizing: border-box; overflow: visible; background: transparent; padding: 0px; position: relative;">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Thin and Light</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Ultraportable yet very powerful, the Lenovo Ideapad 520&nbsp;is perfect for those who like to work, game, or be entertained on the go. In fact, the Ideapad 520&nbsp;weighs only 3.3 lb (1.5 kg) and is only .76&rdquo; (19.3 mm) thin- up to 20% thinner and 30% lighter than most laptops in its class.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Elegant Design</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The Ideapad 520 has a look that shows off an impeccable attention to detail. The aluminum cover with nickel plated logo, aluminum palm rest, and diamond-cut touchpad lend an air of class you won&rsquo;t find in just any laptop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem right" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-510s-13-light-thin-design-1.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8MTE3MzE5fGltYWdlL3BuZ3xoOGIvaDAyLzk0NDkwMDk1MTI0NzgucG5nfDdlZDFiZmU5YjJlNjNkYWM0ZTE2NzhmYzAzZmUxMmViNmE5OGRmYzU5ZWJhYzFjNTYyZGJmOTEyNmVlMGVmNjA" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">I</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper right">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Work, Relax, and Play</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The new standard for PC performance has arrived with Intel&reg; 6th Gen Core&trade; processors. This blazing fast, feature-packed processor family with built-in security is ready to take your productivity, creativity, and entertainment to the next level. What&rsquo;s more, by enabling the exciting Windows 10 features, 7th Gen Intel Core processors empower you to unleash your imagination and explore the possibilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Do Great Things</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Combining the best of the Windows you already know, Windows 10 has many great improvements you&rsquo;ll love: fast start-ups, the expanded Start menu, an all-new browser, and Cortana&mdash;your very own digital personal assistant. Now, even across multiple devices, you can get more things done, more quickly, more smoothly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem left" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/510S-FeatureImage-2.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NDU0MDh8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGg4Yi9oNTMvOTQzMjI2ODA3OTEzNC5wbmd8YjA5YWNiMjFhMGMyYWZmMzRiOTJlYmI4NGQ0NWJjNjdmOTBmZDg3YjQwMDRiMDI2NzEwZThkYTdjMmM4MDBmNw" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">Ideapad 510S: Do great things with the best Windows ever</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Graphics Options</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Strike your own balance between cost and graphics power. For everyday PC use and rich, stunning visuals wherever you go, stick with the integrated Intel&reg; HD graphics. But if you need serious gaming or creative muscle, go with the discrete, high-end AMD graphics option.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Pump up the Volume</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Certified by Harman&reg; Audio, the dual stereo speakers are designed to enhance your movie and music experience. So kick back, hit the play button and enjoy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem right" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/510S-FeatureImage-3.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8ODgyNjN8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGg5Yy9oMTkvOTQzMjI2ODM0MTI3OC5wbmd8Mjc4YTM3Y2ZlODc5NGE0OTNjNTg5MWQ5YTIwZTJhZWNjMTE3ZmRmMzJkM2VjMTZkMjllY2MxZjY4OGM5MjM0YQ" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">Ideapad 510S: Stereo speakers, certified by Harman&reg; Audio</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper right">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Storage Options</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>With your choice of 1 TB HDD or 256 GB SSD storage you won&#39;t have to worry about where to put all your data, videos, music, and photos.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Extra Peace of Mind</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Leaving your laptop unattended in a busy caf&eacute; could be an expensive call. Fortunately, the Ideapad 520&nbsp;is compatible with Kensington MiniSaver cable locks (sold separately). These sturdy, easy-to-use locks enable you to quickly secure your device and prevent others from stealing it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem left" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/510S-FeatureImage-4.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NTQ2ODl8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGhhNi9oNjQvOTQzMjI2ODQzOTU4Mi5wbmd8YTQzYmZjYmE5YzI1YzA2ZDcyZDcxMDI0MGQ1ZDdiZTBiZTYxYTZlMWE0NGNiMjVkMmNhOTljOTYzOWE1NzllZA" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">lenovo-laptop-ideapad-520-15-photo-master-5</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1272', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 73499, 69999, 1, 'lenovo-ideapad-520-15.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-520-15-2.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-520-15-3.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-520-15-4.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-520-15-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-ideapad-520-15', '2017-09-17 15:35:47', '2017-09-17 15:35:47'),
(435, 9, 17, 45, 1, 15, NULL, 'HP Monitor - 23 inch Display - Black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size:14px">Key Features</span></strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 23&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1920 x 1080 (FHD)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>1 x HDMI Inputs,&nbsp; VGA input, 1 DVI</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Product Specifications</strong></span></h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display size: 58.4 cm (23 in) diagonal&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution (native): FHD (1920 x 1080 @ 60 Hz)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Tilt: -2 to +25 degrees&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Display type: IPS with LED Backlight&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Input connector</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1 VGA</li>\r\n	<li>1 DVI (with HDCP support)</li>\r\n	<li>1 HDMI (with HDCP support)&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>More features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Brightness: 250 cd/m&sup2;</li>\r\n	<li>Contrast ratio1000:1 static, Up to 8,000,000:1 dynamic</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Response time</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>7 ms gray to gray (with overdrive)</li>\r\n	<li>14 ms gray to gray (typical)</li>\r\n	<li>28 ms gray to gray (max)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Enjoy your favorite images and on-screen content in vivid FHD on the all new HP 23&quot; diagonal LED Backlit Monitor. When you&#39;re looking for the best specs at the right price, this display delivers with trusted HP performance and a sleek redesign.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Crisp and Clear Images</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy the vivid picture quality of the 23-inch diagonal Full HD display with the clarity of 1920x1080 resolution, Up to 8,000,000:1 dynamic contrast ratio, exceptional 14ms response time, and VGA, DVI-D, and HDMI connectivity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Earth Conscious</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The LED backlit LCD monitor is designed to use less power and meets strict energy efficiency guidelines set by the Environmental Protection Agency and U.S. Department of Energy.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1188', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 27559, 25999, 1, 'hp-monitor-23-inch-display-black.jpg', 'hp-monitor-23-inch-display-black-2.jpg', 'hp-monitor-23-inch-display-black-3.jpg', 'hp-monitor-23-inch-display-black-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'hp-monitor-23-inch-display-black', '2017-09-17 16:27:11', '2017-09-17 16:27:11');
