="configuratorItem-mtmTable-text" id="configuratorItem-mtmTable-text" style="box-sizing: border-box;">\r\n	<h4>Wireless</h4>\r\n\r\n	<p>802.11 AC(1x1)</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Keep up with every aspect of your work and home life with this Lenovo Ideapad laptop. The 15-inch screen on this laptop offers more than enough room for work or streaming video, making this Lenovo Ideapad laptop an ideal choice for business trips or schoolwork.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Lenovo logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1LZ440NAFAMZ/4a409f7f6043c63178b2de95f660f6b5.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:329px; margin:1px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:658px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Productivity &amp; Comfort</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Ideapad 320&nbsp;has a number of features to maximize your productivity and comfort. The improved hinge design is more robust and allows for smooth 180-degree action to a flat position. The frameless keyboard allows your fingers to move freely without bumping, and the textured palm rest resists fingerprints and helps keep your hands in place without slipping &ndash; perfect for speedy touch-typing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1LZ440NAFAMZ/3b747de6ecf332d8a7ad9fd331ee12ad.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1LZ440NAFAMZ/3b747de6ecf332d8a7ad9fd331ee12ad.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:448px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:590px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Powered for Fun</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Ideapad 320&nbsp;is powered by an Intel processor with integrated graphics, giving you plenty of processing power for casual surfing, streaming, and playing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for intel integrated graphics" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1LZ440NAFAMZ/538135308e54e13337857877ffd538bb.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Lightning-Fast Web Browsing</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>802.11 a/c WiFi connectivity comes standard on the Ideapad 320, making it perfect for blazing-fast browsing, streaming, and downloading. 802.11 a/c WiFi delivers up to 3 times the connection speeds of 802.11 b/g/n.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for 802.11 a/c logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1LZ440NAFAMZ/8813adb0c059e004738f87a26576a6c9.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Smile, Swap, and Sort - in Seconds</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Lenovo Photo Master 2.0 is a modern photo library with powerful, easy-to-use navigation and editing tools. With features such as Auto Face Swap and Smart Event Sort, you can now organize and optimize photos on your Ideapad 320 to perfection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Lenovo Photo Master 2.0" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1LZ440NAFAMZ/f8118940db9c2315b28b10363cb1f40d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1274', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 42000, 40000, 1, 'lenovo-ideapad-320-laptop-15-amd.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-320-laptop-15-amd-2.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-320-laptop-15-amd-3.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-320-laptop-15-amd-4.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-320-laptop-15-amd-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-ideapad-320-laptop-15-amd', '2017-09-17 20:22:40', '2017-09-17 20:22:40'),
(440, 9, 16, 40, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo IdeaPad 320 Laptop (15 Inches)', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intel&reg; Pentium&reg; N4200 Processor (1.10GHz 2MB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating System</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Windows 10 Home 64</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display Type</p>\r\n\r\n<p>15.6&quot; HD AntiGlare (1366x768) with integrated camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.0GB DDR3L 1600MHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hard Drive</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1TB 5400 RPM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Optical Drive</p>\r\n\r\n<p>DVD Recordable</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Warranty</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One year</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphics</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intel&reg; HD Graphics 505</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 Cell 30 Watt Hour Li-Polymer</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keyboard</p>\r\n\r\n<p>English Keyboard</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wireless</p>\r\n\r\n<p>802.11 AC(1X1)</p>\r\n', '<p>Processor :&nbsp; &nbsp;Intel Pentium Quad Core N4200 processor (1.10Ghz 2MB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating System :&nbsp; Windows 10 Home</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Graphics&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; &nbsp;Intel Integrated Graphics</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Webcam / Microphone&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;0.3MP camera with single mic</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;4GB DDR4</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage :&nbsp; 1TB SATA HDD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio&nbsp; &nbsp;: 2 x 1.5W speakers with Dolby Audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery&nbsp; &nbsp;: Up to 5 hours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display&nbsp; &nbsp;: 15&quot; HD (1366x768) anti-glare</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; &nbsp;(W x D x H) 14.9&quot; x 10.2&quot; x .9&quot; / 378 x 260 x 22.9 (mm)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; &nbsp; 4.85 lbs / 2.2 kg</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Colors&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; &nbsp;Coral Red&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WiFi/Bluetooth&reg;&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; &nbsp;WiFi 1x1 AC + BT4.1</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ports</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>2 x USB 3.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x USB-Type C</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1x HDMI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x 4-in-1 card reader (SD, SDHC, SDXC, MMC)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1 x RJ-45 LAN</p>\r\n', '<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<h2>Performance You Can Count On</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to Intel&reg; Pentium&reg; Quad Core N4200 processing, plus up to 4 GB DDR3L memory, responsive and reliable performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Durability Down to the Finish</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We redesigned the IdeaPad 320 with a sleek unibody chassis and is available in tone-on-tone color options: Denim Blue and Coral Red. Better yet, the IdeaPad 320 is designed to keep up with you. We treated it with a special protective finish to guard against wear and tear, and added rubber detailing on the bottom cover to maximize ventilation and extend product life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem right" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-320-15-red-feature-1.jpg?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8Mjg0NzF8aW1hZ2UvanBlZ3xoMzgvaGYzLzk1NDk3MDc3MzkxNjYuanBnfDBjMzY1ZTkwNmIyMzQ5NGY4MDllOWNmM2JmYjllZWM4NmQzMDgyOTkwNWJmZTcwZmQ3ZjJkZDViMWQxY2U1MzY" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper right">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Keep it Simple With Lenovo App Explorer</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With Lenovo App Explorer, choose only the apps you want. It&#39;s a straightforward and secure way to personalize your computer, and an essential part of Lenovo&#39;s commitment to cleaner, safer PCs.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Redesigned Touchpad, for Improved Responsiveness</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We redesigned the touchpad on the IdeaPad 320, for a better user experience with multifinger gestures. Touch, click and zoom &mdash; you&#39;ll feel the difference.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem left" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-320-15-blue-feature-4.jpg?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NTQ1NTd8aW1hZ2UvanBlZ3xoZmIvaDk1Lzk1NDk3MDc4Mzc0NzAuanBnfDMxNmM4NTY3NmFmMjEyODU4Y2YxOTI4NzU0ZjkyMzcyZjIzODJhZGRiZGIyOGYwOTI5YTQ3MzYzYmI0NDU4ZDA" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Streamline Your Day With Windows 10</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 320 brings you Windows 10 Home, featuring a host of exciting new features. Want to find a local Indian restaurant, or need gift suggestions? Ask Cortana &mdash; your very own digital personal assistant. Cortana works with more than a thousand apps and services to ensure you&#39;ll always have the answers you need. Best of all, it works across all your Windows 10 devices to keep you organized.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem right" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-320-15-red-feature-3.jpg?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NTE2MTB8aW1hZ2UvanBlZ3xoZGYvaDFjLzk1NDk3MDc5MzU3NzQuanBnfDc5YTI2NWVhNmQyOWRhZWNlYTc5M2VkZWE3Y2Q3ZjQwZjAxYmRhYmRmY2E1ZDRjNjBkZmNhZmViMGE4Y2QxZDU" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper right">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Easy Access to Movies and More</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 320 comes equipped with a DVD drive, so you&#39;ll be able to watch and listen to the movies and music you already own and love.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Audio Clarity at any Volume</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring Dolby Audio-optimized speakers, the IdeaPad 320 delivers crystal-clear audio with minimal distortion at any volume. Stream your favorite playlist or video chat with family &mdash; you&#39;ll hear every detail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem left" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;">\r\n<p><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ide