(441, 9, 16, 40, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo IdeaPad 110s (11") Laptop', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intel&reg; Celeron&reg; N3160 Processor (1.60GHz 2MB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating System</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Windows 10 Home 64</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display Type</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11.6&quot; HD AntiGlare (1366x768) with integrated camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.0GB DDR3 1600 MHz (Onboard)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hard Drive</p>\r\n\r\n<p>32GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Optical Drive</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No Optical Disc Drive</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<div>Processor&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; &nbsp;Up to Intel&reg; Celeron&reg; N3160 Processor (1.60GHz 2MB)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Operating System :&nbsp; &nbsp;Windows 10 Home</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Graphics :&nbsp; &nbsp;Up to Intel&reg; HD Graphics 400</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Webcam / Microphone&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; 0.3MP with Microphone</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Memory :&nbsp; &nbsp;Up to 2GB DDR3 1600 MHz (Onboard)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Storage :&nbsp; Up to 32GB&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Audio&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;2 x 1W speaker</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Battery :&nbsp; &nbsp;31.9WHr; Up to 7 Hours Video Playback</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Display&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;11.6&quot; HD (1366 x 768) Anti-Glare with integrated camera</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Dimensions&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; (W x D x H) 11.49&quot; x 7.95&quot; x 0.7&quot; / 292 x 202 x 17.8 (mm)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Weight&nbsp; :&nbsp; Starting at 2.5 lbs (1.13 kg)</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Colors&nbsp; :&nbsp; Platinum Silver</div>\r\n\r\n<div>WLAN :&nbsp; &nbsp;802.11 AC WiFi</div>\r\n\r\n<div>LAN&nbsp; &nbsp;:&nbsp; &nbsp;10/100M</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Bluetooth&reg;&nbsp; &nbsp;: Bluetooth&reg; 4.0</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Ports</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>1 x USB 3.0</div>\r\n\r\n<div>2 x USB 2.0</div>\r\n\r\n<div>3.5 mm Combo Audio Jack</div>\r\n\r\n<div>1 x HDMI&trade;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>4-in-1 Card Reader (SD, SDHC, SDXC, MMC)</div>\r\n', '<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<h2>Do Great Things With Windows 10</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Combining the best of Windows you already know, Windows 10 Home has many great improvements you&rsquo;ll love. From fast start-ups to the expanded Start menu, and an all-new browser, to Cortana&mdash;your very own digital personal assistant. Now, even across multiple devices, you can get more things done, more quickly, more smoothly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem right" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-110s-11-windows-10-home-1.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NDcxMDR8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGgyNy9oODMvOTMxMTUzMDc3ODY1NC5wbmd8YTkyODRiNmQ4NmU0ODRhMzkwNDZlMWI4ZWY1NDI5ZmVhZTNmODg2ZmEyYjdmNTAwNGViN2JjYWQzOTRiZjQ3Nw" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper right">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Blazing Fast WiFi</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re watching videos, playing games or simply browsing the web, you&rsquo;ll appreciate having the speed of 802.11 ac WiFi, which offers up to 3 times the connection speed of b/g/n and lets you connect with less lag time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Enjoy Long Lasting Processing</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Fitted with up to the latest Intel&reg; Pentium&reg; processor, your IdeaPad 110s has never operated smoother. Experience brilliant PC performance as you multitask effortlessly. Get the essentials done at work, communicate with friends and family, or use multimedia on the go. Whatever your pleasure, this laptop won&rsquo;t let you down.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem left" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; clear: left; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 1;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-110s-11-multimedia-2.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NTc5NDF8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGhhMi9oNWMvOTMxMTUzMDcxMzExOC5wbmd8YzA0Y2M1NTk2NjYwMzZiNmJmNGJhZWQzMDhjNWE3NTlhZDQ1NTVhNWJmMzk1MzUzMWZkZTMzNmI2YzY0ODMyNg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">Great for multimedia on the go.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper left">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 469.875px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Crystal Clear HD Display</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Say goodbye to standard definition. The IdeaPad 110s comes with HD graphics, delivering vibrant, sharp visuals&mdash;superb for movies, gaming, and photo sharing.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Productivity and Comfort</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 110s has a number of features to maximize your productivity and comfort. The improved hinge design is more robust and allows for smooth 180-degree action to a flat position&mdash;great for screen sharing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaItem right" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: right; clear: right; margin-right: 0px; width: 613.797px; padding: 5px; text-align: center; order: 2;"><img alt="" class="lazy lazyLoadAfterDOMInteractive" src="http://www3.lenovo.com/medias/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-110s-11-hd-display-3.png?context=bWFzdGVyfHJvb3R8NDQ3Njd8aW1hZ2UvcG5nfGgyMC9oZWIvOTMxMTUzMDY0NzU4Mi5wbmd8MDU3OWZjYzQ2MzU5YzBlMzg1OWQ1ODZiNjNlZjAxZGY4OTBjZmRkOGY3ODY5YTU4MGRjZmE5ZjQyZWIzMTI5Mw" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:inline; max-height:90vh; max-width:100%" title="" />\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-mediaCaption" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.75em; padding: 0px 1.5em 2em; line-height: 1.2;">The IdeaPad 110s; delivering vibrant, sharp visuals.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-textWrapper fullwidth" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1116px; padding: 5px; float: right; clear: right; order: 2;">\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class="tabbedBrowse-features-featureText" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1106px; float: left; clear: left; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2em; line-height: 1.4;">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Excellent Value for Years</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>The IdeaPad 110s is equipped with everything you need and nothing you don&rsquo;t. It&rsquo;s also capable of handling new software and upgrades for years to come&mdash;bringing you greater value.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>A Perfect Balance for Life on the Move</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Combining a reliable CPU, quality components, and solid engineering, the IdeaPad 110s delivers an outstanding balance of performance and reliability at an affordable price. What&#39;s more starting at just 2.5lbs / 1.15kg and .7&quot; / 17.8 mm thin, with an 11.6&quot; display, this device is highly mobile, and can be taken anywhere. You can also choose from four vibrant colors&mdash; platinum silver and red.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1276', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 25200, 24000, 1, 'lenovo-ideapad-110s-11-laptop.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-110s-11-laptop-2.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-110s-11-laptop-3.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-110s-11-laptop-4.jpg', 'lenovo-ideapad-110s-11-laptop-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-ideapad-110s-11-laptop', '2017-09-17 20:55:09', '2017-09-17 20:55:09');
