(442, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy Grand Prime Plus G532F, 5.0-inch, 4G Dual Sim, Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Key Features</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1.4 GHz Quad-Core Processor</li>\r\n	<li>5.0 inch screen</li>\r\n	<li>8 MP Rear Camera + 5 MP Front Camera</li>\r\n	<li>8GB Memory, 1.5GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>4G LTE</li>\r\n	<li>1.5 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Size (Main Display): 5.0&quot; (126.4mm)</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution (Main Display): 540 x 960 (qHD)</li>\r\n	<li>Technology (Main Display): PLS TFT LCD</li>\r\n	<li>Color Depth (Main Display): 16M</li>\r\n	<li>S Pen Support: No</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Processor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CPU Speed: 1.4GHz</li>\r\n	<li>CPU Type: Quad-Core</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Operating System</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>RAM Size (GB): 1.5 GB</li>\r\n	<li>ROM Size (GB): 8</li>\r\n	<li>External Memory Support: MicroSD (Up to 256GB)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Network/Bearer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SIM: Dual-SIM</li>\r\n	<li>SIM size: Micro-SIM (3FF)</li>\r\n	<li>Infra: 2G GSM, 3G WCDMA, 4G LTE FDD</li>\r\n	<li>2G GSM: GSM850, GSM900, DCS1800, PCS1900</li>\r\n	<li>3G UMTS: B1(2100), B2(1900), B5(850), B8(900)</li>\r\n	<li>4G FDD LTE: B1(2100), B3(1800), B5(850), B7(2600), B8(900), B20(800)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connectivity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>USB Interface: Micro USB</li>\r\n	<li>USB Version: USB 2.0</li>\r\n	<li>Location Technology: GPS, Glonass</li>\r\n	<li>Earjack: 3.5mm Stereo</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi: 802.11 b/g/n 2.4GHz</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi Direct</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth Version: Bluetooth v4.2</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth Profiles: A2DP, AVRCP, DI, HFP, HID, HOGP, HSP, MAP, OPP, PAN, PBAP</li>\r\n	<li>PC Sync.: Smart Switch (PC version)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sensors</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors: Accelerometer, Proximity Sensor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internet Usage Time(3G) (Hours): Up to 9</li>\r\n	<li>Internet Usage Time(LTE) (Hours): Up to 12</li>\r\n	<li>Internet Usage Time(Wi-Fi) (Hours): Up to 12</li>\r\n	<li>Video Playback Time (Hours): Up to 12</li>\r\n	<li>Standard Battery Capacity (mAh): 2600</li>\r\n	<li>Removable</li>\r\n	<li>Audio Playback Time (Hours): Up to 59</li>\r\n	<li>Talk Time (3G WCDMA) (Hours): Up to 12</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Samsung Product</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It has a 5.0-inch IPS display and&nbsp;a resolution of 960&times;540 pixels just qHD protected with Gorilla Glass. It has MediaTek MT6737T quad core processor (1.4Ghz ARM Cortex A-53) which essentially combines with 1.5 GB of RAM. The internal memory has a capacity of 8GB and can easily be expanded via a microSD card.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/84edbf168a55759fa673748b37d3d0be.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/84edbf168a55759fa673748b37d3d0be.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Premium Design</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Grand Prime Plus features a sturdy case design with a non-slip rear grip pattern to keep it securely in your hand at all times. It also comes in a selection of stylish colours to complement your lifestyle while making an impression.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/4562d5a24647138049d447857efba5d2.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/4562d5a24647138049d447857efba5d2.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Selfies that Shine</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its trusty LED flash and 5 MP front camera capture you in your best light, even in dark conditions. And with Quick Launch, you get instant camera access by simply double tapping the home button, even from Sleep Mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/47ee14b58c6a0ba90518468a7302b2a1.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/47ee14b58c6a0ba90518468a7302b2a1.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Powerful Performance</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With upgraded RAM support and enhanced chipset performance you can enjoy seamless webpage load times for a more responsive multimedia and gaming experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/427d4c25160d34cb58e0cc8b031fb532.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/427d4c25160d34cb58e0cc8b031fb532.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bigger and Better</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Designed to expand your world of entertainment and gaming even further for the ultimate experience. Its optimal 5.0&rdquo; display is just the right size to view what&rsquo;s on screen for maximum enjoyment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/484796a28eaca0ada5e23de29f205794.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/484796a28eaca0ada5e23de29f205794.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1191', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 14627, 13799, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-4g-dual-sim-gold.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-4g-dual-sim-gold-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-4g-dual-sim-gold-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-4g-dual-sim-gold-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-4g-dual-sim-gold-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-5-0-inch-4g-dual-sim-gold', '2017-09-18 13:17:05', '2017-09-18 13:17:05'),
(443, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy J7 Prime 32GB - 3GB RAM - 13MP 5.5 inch color black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size:5.5 inches Screen</li>\r\n	<li>Display Type:PLS TFT Capacitive Touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory:32GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Operating System:Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Primary Camera:13 MP, f/1.9, 28mm</li>\r\n	<li>Battery:Li-Ion 3300 mAh Capacity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>Product Specifications:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size: 5.5 inches (~73.3% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Display Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels (~401 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Display Type: IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Multi-touch: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Back Camera: 13 MP, f/1.9, 28mm, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, panorama, HDR</li>\r\n	<li>Video: Yes,&nbsp;1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Front Camera: 8 MP, f/1.9</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Exynos 7870</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Octa-core 1.6 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali-T830MP2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>System Memory: 3 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory: 16 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Card Slot: microSD, up to 256 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Software</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System: Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sound</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration, MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loud Speaker: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm Jack: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2G Network: GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 - SIM 1 &amp; SIM 2</li>\r\n	<li>3G Network: HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1900 / 2100</li>\r\n	<li>4G Network: LTE band 1(2100), 3(1800), 5(850), 7(2600), 8(900), 20(800), 38(2600), 40(2300)</li>\r\n	<li>SIM: Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Data</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GPRS: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Speed: HSPA, LTE Cat4 150/50 Mbps</li>\r\n	<li>WLAN: Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: Yes, v4.1, A2DP</li>\r\n	<li>USB: Yes, microUSB v2.0, USB On-The-Go</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Features</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors: Fingerprint, accelerometer, proximity</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging: SMS (threaded view), MMS, Email, IM, Push Email</li>\r\n	<li>Browser: HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>GPS: Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS</li>\r\n	<li>Radio: No</li>\r\n	<li>Java: No</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n	<li>Photo viewer/editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Multimedia</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Audio: MP3/WAV/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Video: Xvid/DivX/MP4/H.265 player</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Power</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Battery: Non-removable Li-Ion 3300 mAh battery</li>\r\n	<li>Talk time: Up to 21 h (3G)</li>\r\n	<li>Music play: Up to 84 h</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Body</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Full Metal Body Design</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions: 151.7 x 75 x 8 mm</li>\r\n	<li>Weight: 167 g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:18px">Simply one of the best</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Galaxy J7 Prime" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/162be1c873e6080a911a7806c13937bb.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:522px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:686px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Elegantly Refined</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Boasts a stunning brushed metal finish with zero camera protrusion to ensure an overall ultra slim design. Its enlarged screen features flowing curved edges for optimal viewing and comfortable single handed use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung J7 prime with elegant design" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/e54c7604a1ef2a07408a693cdd19e5f7.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:431px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:807px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Speedier Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Enhanced RAM and ROM support allows for smoother UI transitions and greater multitasking abilities. Smart Manager does the thinking for you by checking and optimising handset status, keeping you one step ahead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung galaxy j7 prime with fast processor" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/03186432e378da1c2acb32016f86248d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:448px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:840px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Brighten up your Photos</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring an F1.9 lens that allows for bright images even in low light settings, its 13MP camera ensures that all that you capture is beautifully crisp with vivid detail</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="J7 prime with best camera" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/f47e0fbe80a5797d6758fb14f18a28cb.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:446px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:836px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Control and Capture at Will</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Its Wide Selfie function together with its 8MP front camera lets you fit more people in group shots and capture beautiful scenery as it was meant to be seen. You can even use your palm to take photos with ease.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Best Smartphone" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/b6a3796d6540282c9ef154c4cb7ef71d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:443px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:831px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Safe and Sound</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Features a quick and secure solution to make sure that you are the only one that has access to your device. Its touch-based fingerprint sensor lets you unlock your device safely within a second.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Galaxy j7 prime with extra safety" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/d22eaec8803fb56818cbaf770a86f596.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:450px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:800px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Power Extended</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Now with even longer lasting battery power to pack in more multimedia and keep gamers in the action. Ultra Power Saving Mode turns off all background running apps to drastically minimise battery consumption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="J7 prime long lasting battery" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/679304cba9f4a561a230f5b7c147a260.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:490px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:872px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1192', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 28089, 26499, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-black.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-black-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-black-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-black-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-black-5.jpg', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-black', '2017-09-18 13:48:48', '2017-09-18 13:48:48'),
(444, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, ' Samsung Galaxy J5 pro - 3GB RAM, 16GB, Dual SIM--color-gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">KEY FEATURES</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 5.20-inch&nbsp;<br />\r\nStorage: 16 GB<br />\r\nRAM; 3GB<br />\r\nCamera; 13 MP<br />\r\nOperating System; Android 7<br />\r\nResolution; 720x1280 pixels</p>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>DISPLAY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen size (inches); &nbsp;&nbsp; 5.20</li>\r\n	<li>Touchscreen; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution ;&nbsp;&nbsp; 720x1280 pixels</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>HARDWARE</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Processor; &nbsp;&nbsp; 1.6GHz octa-core</li>\r\n	<li>Processor make; &nbsp;&nbsp; Exynos 7870</li>\r\n	<li>RAM; &nbsp;&nbsp; 3GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal storage; &nbsp;&nbsp; 32GB</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage ;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage type; &nbsp;&nbsp; microSD</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage up to (GB) ;&nbsp;&nbsp; 256</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nCAMERA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rear camera; &nbsp;&nbsp; 13-megapixel</li>\r\n	<li>Flash; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Front camera; &nbsp;&nbsp; 13-megapixel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSOFTWARE</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System ;&nbsp;&nbsp; Android 7.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nCONNECTIVITY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi standards supported; &nbsp;&nbsp; 802.11 b/g/n</li>\r\n	<li>GPS; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes, v 4.10</li>\r\n	<li>NFC; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Infrared; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>USB OTG; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>Headphones; &nbsp;&nbsp; 3.5mm</li>\r\n	<li>FM ;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Number of SIMs; &nbsp;&nbsp; 2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>SIM 1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SIM Type; &nbsp;&nbsp; Micro-SIM</li>\r\n	<li>GSM/CDMA; &nbsp;&nbsp; GSM</li>\r\n	<li>3G; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>4G/ LTE; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSIM 2&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GSM/CDMA; &nbsp;&nbsp; GSM</li>\r\n	<li>3G ;&nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>4G/ LTE; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSENSORS</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Compass/ Magnetometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>Proximity sensor; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Accelerometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Ambient light sensor; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Gyroscope; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Barometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature sensor ;&nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>BATTERY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-Removable Li-lon&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity:3000 mAh</li>\r\n	<li>Talk Time Up to &nbsp;21h</li>\r\n	<li>Music Play up to 83 h&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:20px">Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro smartphone</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The phone comes with a 5.20-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 720 pixels by 1280 pixels.The Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro is powered by 1.6GHz octa-core Exynos 7870 processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone packs 16GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 256GB via a microSD card. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro packs a 13-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 13-megapixel front shooter for selfies.The Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro runs Android 7.0 and is powered by a 3000mAh non removable battery. It measures 146.30 x 71.30 x 7.90 (height x width x thickness) . The Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro is a dual SIM (GSM and GSM) smartphone that accepts Micro-SIM. Connectivity options include Wi-Fi, GPS, Bluetooth, NFC, FM, 3G and 4G. Sensors on the phone include Proximity sensor, Accelerometer, Ambient light sensor and Gyroscope.<img alt="Elegant by nature" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/ae-feature-elegant-by-nature-68147893?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:394px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:700px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Share life as you see it</strong><br />\r\nIts rear 13 MP F1.7 camera captures clear photos with enhanced detail in low light while its intuitive interface enables one-handed functionality thanks to its moving shutter button so you can still take the shot while adjusting your pose or framing the scene.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="Share life as you see it" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/ae-feature-share-life-as-you-see-it-68147881?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:281px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Look great in every frame</strong><br />\r\nThe Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro lets you take bright and vivid selfies every time with more accurate detail even in low light thanks to its front LED and selfie flashes. You can also control the shutter by simple hand gesture.<br />\r\n<img alt="Look great in every frame" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/ae-feature-look-great-in-every-frame-68147889?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:394px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:700px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full speed ahead</strong><br />\r\nKeep usage running at optimal levels. Thanks to 3 GB of RAM, 32 GB of internal storage and up to 256 GB of optional expandable storage capacity with microSD support, the Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro ensures highly responsive and blazingly fast speeds to accelerate your workflow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1193', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 27559, 25999, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-gold.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-gold-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-gold-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-gold-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-gold-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-gold', '2017-09-18 14:22:11', '2017-09-18 14:22:11'),
(445, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy S7 Edge - 5.5 inch, 4GB RAM, Dual SIM, Color- Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">KEY FEATURES</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 5.5 inches Curved edge (~76.1% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 32 GB</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 4 GB&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Camera:<strong>&nbsp;</strong>(&nbsp;Primary) :12 MP, 5MP front</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 3600 mAh non-removable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>Product specifications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DISPLAY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size:5.5 inches (~76.1% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution:1440 x 2560 pixels (~534 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch</li>\r\n	<li>Protection:Corning Gorilla Glass 4</li>\r\n	<li>Always-on display</li>\r\n	<li>TouchWiz UI</li>\r\n	<li>Curved edge screen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PLATFORM</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Qualcomm MSM8996 Snapdragon 820&nbsp;or Exynos 8890 Octa</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Dual-core 2.15 GHz Kryo &amp; dual-core 1.6 GHz Kryo or&nbsp;Quad-core 2.3 GHz Mongoose + quad-core 1.6 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Adreno 530 or&nbsp;Mali-T880 MP12</li>\r\n	<li>Dual SIM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CAMERA</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:12 MP, f/1.7, 26mm, phase detection autofocus, OIS, LED flash,&nbsp;check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Features: 1/2.6&quot; sensor size, 1.4 &micro;m pixel size, geo-tagging, simultaneous 4K video and 9MP image recording, touch focus, face/smile detection, Auto HDR, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Video:2160p@30fps,&nbsp;1080p@60fps,&nbsp;720p@240fps, HDR, dual-video rec.,&nbsp;check quality.</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:5 MP, f/1.7, 22mm, dual video call, Auto HDR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SOUND</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert typesVibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COMMUNICATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN:Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth v:4.2, A2DP, LE, apt-X</li>\r\n	<li>GPS with A-GPS, GLONASS, BDS</li>\r\n	<li>NFC</li>\r\n	<li>USB:microUSB v2.0, USB Host</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SensorsFingerprint, accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass, barometer, heart rate, SpO2</li>\r\n	<li>MessagingSMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>Fast battery charging: 60% in 30 min (Quick Charge 2.0)</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless charging (Qi/PMA) - market dependent</li>\r\n	<li>ANT+ support</li>\r\n	<li>S-Voice natural language commands and dictation</li>\r\n	<li>OneDrive (115 GB cloud storage)</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/DivX/XviD/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BATTERY&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 3600 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:20px">&nbsp;Samsung Galaxy S7 edge</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy S7 edge is the smartphone you&rsquo;ll want to brag about. It provides a bigger, more stunning screen without compromise.&nbsp;Galaxy S7 edge is lightweight and is encapsulated by an envious, dual curved edge design&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Incredible Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy S7 edge has an extended edge design that puts more experiences at your fingertips. View information such as scores, stocks, news and more. Quick access to your favorite settings, and useful tools such as compass and ruler. And the Task Edge takes you to frequently accessed commands with just a swipe.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Water and Dust&nbsp;Resistant&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Worry less about daily wear and tear of your phone. Galaxy S7 Edge has an IP68 rating&nbsp;meaning not only protection against dust, it also repels splashes, spills and even dunks. Simply wipe it off and move along.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Expandable Memory</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Running out of memory shouldn&#39;t be a thing. So if 32GB isn&#39;t already enough, you can add an additional 200GB with a microSD card. No clouds, no hard drives.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Enhanced Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The first smartphone with dual-pixel technology has a fast autofocus for less blur and a new advanced sensor for catching details in low light. Capture moments as you actually see them.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1194', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 58299, 54999, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-5-5-inch-4gb-ram-dual-sim-cold-gold.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-5-5-inch-4gb-ram-dual-sim-cold-gold-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-5-5-inch-4gb-ram-dual-sim-cold-gold-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-5-5-inch-4gb-ram-dual-sim-cold-gold-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-5-5-inch-4gb-ram-dual-sim-cold-gold-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-s7-edge-5-5-inch-4gb-ram-dual-sim-color-gold', '2017-09-18 14:47:12', '2017-09-18 14:47:12'),
