(447, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy A5 2017, 3GB RAM, 16MP Camera, Dual SIm, color-black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Key Features</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen size: 5.0 inches</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Type: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>1.2GHz quad-core processor</li>\r\n	<li>2GB RAM, 16GB Internal</li>\r\n	<li>13MP Camera, 5MP front</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Product Specifications&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen Size: 5.0 inches (~71.0% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Type:&nbsp;Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution:&nbsp;720 x 1280 pixels (~294 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v4.4.4 (KitKat)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Qualcomm MSM8916 Snapdragon 410</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.2 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Adreno 306</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>RAM: 2GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal storage: 16GB</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage type: microSD</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage: up to&nbsp;&nbsp;64GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary :13 MP, 4128 x 3096 pixels, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Video: 1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:&nbsp;5 MP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Network</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Technology: GSM / HSPA / LTE</li>\r\n	<li>2G bands: GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 - SIM 1 &amp; SIM 2</li>\r\n	<li>3G bands: HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1900 / 2100</li>\r\n	<li>4G bands: LTE 800 / 850 / 900 / 1800 / 2100 / 2600&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Speed HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE Cat4 150/50 Mbps</li>\r\n	<li>GPRS</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi: Wi-Fi standards supported: 802.11 a/ b/ g/ n</li>\r\n	<li>GPS</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth&nbsp;v 4.00</li>\r\n	<li>NFC</li>\r\n	<li>Headphones: 3.5mm</li>\r\n	<li>USB Micro-USB</li>\r\n	<li>Charging via Micro-USB</li>\r\n	<li>Compass/ Magnetometer</li>\r\n	<li>Proximity sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Accelerometer</li>\r\n	<li>Ambient light sensor&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Features</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Messaging SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>Java via Java MIDP emulator</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 2300 mAh battery</li>\r\n	<li>Internet Usage Time(3G) (Hours): Up to 8</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Galaxy A5 (2017, Dual Sim)</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<strong>Galaxy A5</strong>&nbsp;offers a beautifully crafted full metal uni-body, slim design, superior hardware and the best possible social media experience. The&nbsp;<strong>Galaxy A5</strong>&nbsp;blends practicality and functionality comes equipped with an extraordinary Super AMOLED display and Adaptive Display technology to deliver clearer images with deep contrast and better viewing angles for more vivid, colorful content in virtually any environment, even under bright sunlight.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/logopedia/images/c/c1/PhotoGrid_1430295244178.jpg/revision/20150506041346" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:124px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:300px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Stylish&nbsp;Design&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The first Samsung smartphone with a full metal body, the Samsung Galaxy A5 boasts an innovative, luxurious design and a stunning 5&quot; HD Super AMOLED Capacitive Touchscreen display. You can feel the premium quality of the sleek full metal body in your hand. And with 4 unique colours, you can choose the Samsung Galaxy A5 that best fits your personality and style.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL18LGG8NAFAMZ/7e363093f09800b004ef7062a24aeff7.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:349px; margin:22px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:620px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Adaptive Display&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Alive Super Amoled Display and the Adapt Display deliver true-to-life colours on your Samsung Galaxy A5 which intelligently adapt to your surroundings. With its automatic Adjustable Audio, your Samsung Galaxy A5 will automatically increase or decrease the volume in response to the background noise around you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Smarter Selfie&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Samsung Galaxy A5 you don&rsquo;t need to touch the button when taking selfies. Snap a selfie with your voice or palm and make your friends think your own personal photographer is following you around. With the latest image detection and voice recognition software, the Samsung Galaxy A5 is taking the selfie to the next level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt="Smarter selfie shooting" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL18LGG8NAFAMZ/c09f1abe70424d16441f8fa251fbc486.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:203px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:382px" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Powerful Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with a 1.2 GHz Quad core processor, the Galaxy A5 runs at geek speeds. You&rsquo;ll be seamlessly watching movies, listening to music, and running multiple apps at blazing speeds. With support for the LTE Cat 4, you&#39;ll be downloading a lot faster than the guy next to you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL18LGG8NAFAMZ/0229a1e31c1d18bd51c2af40c27a955e.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:200px; margin:97px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:400px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Efficient Power Use</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Never miss important calls because of a dead battery. Ultra Power Saving mode dramatically reduces battery consumption by shutting down unnecessary functions, ensuring your phone is available when you really need it. A smarter battery for a smarter phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL18LGG8NAFAMZ/0ec6bee0b3c18c4d416a41be0c014572.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:388px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1196', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 37099, 34999, 1, 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-a5-2017-3gb-ram-16mp-camera-dual-sim.jpg', 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-a5-2017-3gb-ram-16mp-camera-dual-sim-2.jpg', 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-a5-2017-3gb-ram-16mp-camera-dual-sim-3.jpg', 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-a5-2017-3gb-ram-16mp-camera-dual-sim-4.jpg', 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-a5-2017-3gb-ram-16mp-camera-dual-sim-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-a5-2017-3gb-ram-16mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black', '2017-09-18 15:56:19', '2017-09-18 15:56:19'),
(448, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy J7 Prime 32GB - 3GB RAM - 13MP 5.5 inch color White Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Key Features</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size:5.5 inches Screen</li>\r\n	<li>Display Type:PLS TFT Capacitive Touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory:32GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Operating System:Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Primary Camera:13 MP, f/1.9, 28mm</li>\r\n	<li>Battery:Li-Ion 3300 mAh Capacity</li>\r\n	<li>Color: white gold</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Display &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Type:PLS TFT capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size:5.5 inches (~73.3% screen-to-body ratio)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution:1080 x 1920 pixels (~401 ppi pixel density)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multitouch &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Protection:Corning Gorilla Glass (market dependent)</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Platform &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>OS:Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chipset:Exynos 7870 Octa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPU:Octa-core 1.6 GHz Cortex-A53</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPU:Mali-T830MP2</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Storage</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal Memory:32GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3 GB RAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>microSD, up to 256 GB (dedicated slot)</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Camera</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Primary:13 MP, f/1.9, 28mm, autofocus, LED flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features:Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, panorama, HDR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video:1080p@30fps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secondary:8 MP, f/1.9</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Sound &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Alert types:Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Loudspeaker &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.5mm jack &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Comms &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>WLAN:Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bluetooth:v4.1, A2DP, LE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPS:with A-GPS, GLONASS/ BDS (region dependent)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>microUSB v2.0, USB On-The-Go</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Features&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensors:Fingerprint, accelerometer, proximity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Messaging:SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Browser:HTML5</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ANT+ support</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xvid/DivX/MP4/H.265 player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MP3/WAV/eAAC+/FLAC player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Photo/video editor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Document viewer</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Battery &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Non-removable Li-Ion 3300 mAh battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Talk time:Up to 21 h (3G)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Music play:Up to 84 h</p>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:18px">Simply one of the best</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Galaxy J7 Prime" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/162be1c873e6080a911a7806c13937bb.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:522px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:686px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Elegantly Refined</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Boasts a stunning brushed metal finish with zero camera protrusion to ensure an overall ultra slim design. Its enlarged screen features flowing curved edges for optimal viewing and comfortable single handed use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung J7 prime with elegant design" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/e54c7604a1ef2a07408a693cdd19e5f7.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:431px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:807px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Speedier Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Enhanced RAM and ROM support allows for smoother UI transitions and greater multitasking abilities. Smart Manager does the thinking for you by checking and optimising handset status, keeping you one step ahead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung galaxy j7 prime with fast processor" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/03186432e378da1c2acb32016f86248d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:448px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:840px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Brighten up your Photos</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring an F1.9 lens that allows for bright images even in low light settings, its 13MP camera ensures that all that you capture is beautifully crisp with vivid detail</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="J7 prime with best camera" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/f47e0fbe80a5797d6758fb14f18a28cb.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:446px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:836px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Control and Capture at Will</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Its Wide Selfie function together with its 8MP front camera lets you fit more people in group shots and capture beautiful scenery as it was meant to be seen. You can even use your palm to take photos with ease.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Best Smartphone" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/b6a3796d6540282c9ef154c4cb7ef71d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:443px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:831px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Safe and Sound</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Features a quick and secure solution to make sure that you are the only one that has access to your device. Its touch-based fingerprint sensor lets you unlock your device safely within a second.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Galaxy j7 prime with extra safety" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/d22eaec8803fb56818cbaf770a86f596.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:450px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:800px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Power Extended</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Now with even longer lasting battery power to pack in more multimedia and keep gamers in the action. Ultra Power Saving Mode turns off all background running apps to drastically minimise battery consumption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="J7 prime long lasting battery" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0S4O68NAFAMZ/679304cba9f4a561a230f5b7c147a260.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:490px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:872px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1197', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 26913, 25389, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-white-gold.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-white-gold-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-white-gold-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-white-gold-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-white-gold-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-j7-prime-32gb-3gb-ram-13mp-5-5-inch-color-white-gold', '2017-09-18 16:22:58', '2017-09-18 16:22:58');
