quo;s best subjects are rarely still for long. allows you to capture even moving objects &ndash; before the moment passes you by. Bringing together the power of an imaging sensor and a laser autofocus sensor, you can freeze movement in the sharpest detail, even when the light is low.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL15XX0SNAFAMZ/b438132286679894ae9ed5adc9e0195c.jpg" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Software that Learns from You</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>is the smartphone that gets smarter and more personal as you use it. It learns and adapts based on how you use your phone, giving you the best smartphone experience to date.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL15XX0SNAFAMZ/429d22f092a3407a032e7d9dcd8a7015.jpg" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1283', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 52499, 49999, 1, 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-64gb-ram-23mp-back-camera-dual-sim-black.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-64gb-ram-23mp-back-camera-dual-sim-black-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-64gb-ram-23mp-back-camera-dual-sim-black-3.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-64gb-ram-23mp-back-camera-dual-sim-black-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-xz-3gbram-64gb-23mp-camera-dual-sim-black', '2017-09-18 18:03:20', '2017-09-18 18:03:20'),
(454, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy J2, 8GB, 1GB RAM, 4G/LTE, color-Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size:20px">Key Features</span></strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 4.7 inches, Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>OS : Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Memory : Internal 8GB, 1GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A7</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: &nbsp;5 MP Rear, 2MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: Li-Ion 2 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen Size: 4.7 inches</li>\r\n	<li>Type: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 72 x 128 pixels (~294 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:&nbsp; Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Qualcomm MSM8916 Snapdragon 41</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A7</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali-T72</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 128 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 8GB, 1 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:&nbsp;5 MP, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;72p@3fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:&nbsp;2 MP, LED flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Network</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Technology: GSM / HSPA / LTE</li>\r\n	<li>2G bands: GSM 85 / 9 / 18 / 19 - SIM 1 &amp; SIM 2</li>\r\n	<li>3G bands: HSDPA 85 / 9 / 19 / 21</li>\r\n	<li>Speed: HSPA 21.1/5.76 Mbps</li>\r\n	<li>GPRS: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>4G: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sound</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Comms: WLANWi-Fi 82.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: v4.1, A2DP</li>\r\n	<li>GPS: Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS</li>\r\n	<li>Radio: FM radio with RDS; recording</li>\r\n	<li>USB: microUSB v2.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Features</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors: Accelerometer, proximity</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging: SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>Browser: HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>Java: No</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;ANT+ support</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Li-Ion 2 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Samsung GALAXY J2</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Samsung GALAXY J2&nbsp;with a huge storage of&nbsp;8GB is all set to amaze you with its excellent performance.&nbsp;This dual SIM smartphone enables you to browse web at superfast speed. With 1.3 GHz Quad-Core processor along with Android Lollipop operating system. From work to play and back, Galaxy J2 keeps you entertained wherever you go. Its rounded edge and slim profile accentuate its simple yet sleek, modern design. It&rsquo;s stylishly tactile in the palm of your hand.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Display</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Watch crystal clear videos on the large 11.93 (4.7) super AMOLED display of the Samsung Galaxy smartphone. With 54 x 96 pixels screen resolution, every image is displayed with excellent clarity and details. The super AMOLED display ensures deeper contrast and true-to-life colours for an immersive viewing experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ultra-Data Saving</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With ultra-data saving feature you can seamless save data while you stream videos, browse your favourite apps or shop online. This advanced feature compresses the data and restricts background apps from consuming data.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Capture Amazing Moments</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy J Series come with powerful camera that captures brilliant shots even in low light conditions. It also comes with an Advanced Mode that gives you an enhanced imaging experience. You can choose from different image Modes to suit different occasions so that you get pictures that look more real.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Seamless Performance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Powered by a 1.3 GHz&nbsp; Quad Core processor, the GALAXY J2&nbsp; will seamlessly perform a wide range of tasks including gaming, watching movies, and surfing the web. Also with support for HSPA+, you&rsquo;ll experience blazing-fast download and upload speeds. With the enhanced productivity and greater efficiency provided by the GALAXY J2, you can spend less time waiting and more time doing.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1202', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 13249, 12499, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-4g-lte-color-gold.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-4g-lte-color-gold-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-4g-lte-color-gold-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-4g-lte-color-gold-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-4g-lte-color-gold-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-4g-lte-color-gold', '2017-09-18 18:03:53', '2017-09-18 18:03:53'),
(455, 1, 21, 61, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy C9 Pro, 6.0 inch, 6GB RAM, Dual SIM - Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Key Features</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen Size: 6.0 inches&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Type: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory: 64GB, 6GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: Primary 16 MP, Secondary 16 PM</li>\r\n	<li>Battery:Li-Ion 4000 mAh Capacity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 6.0 inches (~75.5% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels (~367 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch</li>\r\n	<li>Protection: Corning Gorilla Glass (unspecified version)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Qualcomm MSM8976 Snapdragon 653</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Octa-core (4x1.95 GHz Cortex-A72 )</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Adreno 510</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 256 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 64 GB, 6 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 16 MP, f/1.9, phase detection autofocus, dual-LED (dual tone) flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, panorama, HDR</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 16 MP, f/1.9, 1080p</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sound &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker: with stereo speakers</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Communications&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN: Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, WiFi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: v4.2, A2DP, LE</li>\r\n	<li>GPS:&nbsp; with A-GPS, GLONASS/ BDS (region dependent)</li>\r\n	<li>NFC</li>\r\n	<li>Radio: Stereo FM radio with RDS</li>\r\n	<li>USB: Type-C 1.0 reversible connector</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Features &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors: Fingerprint (front-mounted), accelerometer, proximity, compass</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging: SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>Browser: HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>Fast battery charging</li>\r\n	<li>ANT+ support</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable 4000 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:20px">Samsung Galaxy C9</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Get the latest phone in town from Samsung. This Samsung Galaxy C9 Pro comes fully packed with amazing features that revolutionize the smartphone world. Move to the next level thanks to this Galaxy C9 Pro that ensure you get better view of all your content with its big screen, big capacity battery to keep you online throughout the day and fast performance.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>High Definition Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bigger is always better and this phone does not disappoint when it comes to size. Style comes redefined with the 15.2cm (6&rsquo;&rsquo;) FHD sAMOLED Display on the new Galaxy C9 Pro. Experience your world come alive in its full splendor as you set off on your quest for the extraordinary.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung Galaxy C9 Pro - Screen size" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL10PPBSNAFAMZ/36f3fc1b3b64a8b9ffad5061f32316a3.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:335px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:547px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Designed to dazzle</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Galaxy C9 will have your friends be amazed with its cool and stylish design. The new Galaxy C9 Pro has the looks that turn heads, with its slim design and 2.5D Gorilla Glass, be ready to increase your followers every time you carry it making it a perfect device to own.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for samsung galaxy c9 pro" src="https://www.pc-tablet.co.in/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Samsung-Galaxy-C9-Pro.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:699px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Spectacular Selfies</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Ensure you capture these amazing selfies thanks to this phone high quality front camera. Explore your adventurous side with a brilliant 16 MP front camera in the new Galaxy C9 Pro.&nbsp;Your selfies and groupfies will be envied when you share it all.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for samsung galaxy c9 pro" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL10PPBSNAFAMZ/8c38b3e8d4d1d9d6c02ab1d32104156f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:567px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Thrilling Speed&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Set the pace with the new Galaxy C9 Pro when it comes to performance as it is powered by a ground-breaking 6 GB RAM, the new Galaxy C9 Pro takes multitasking to the next level. Watch your favorite videos, download content, shuffle between apps &ndash; do it all in a jiffy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Samsung Galaxy C9 Pro" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL10PPBSNAFAMZ/a3be9fe99f1665f070712b73ead7b540.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:274px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:706px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1203', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 47249, 44999, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-c9-pro-6-0-inch-16mp-camera-6gb-ram-dual-sim-gold.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-c9-pro-6-0-inch-16mp-camera-6gb-ram-dual-sim-gold-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-c9-pro-6-0-inch-16mp-camera-6gb-ram-dual-sim-gold-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-c9-pro-6-0-inch-16mp-camera-6gb-ram-dual-sim-gold-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-c9-pro-6-0-inch-16mp-camera-6gb-ram-dual-sim-gold-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-c9-pro-6-0-inch-6gb-ram-dual-sim-gold', '2017-09-18 18:14:40', '2017-09-18 18:14:40');
