(456, 1, 21, 61, 2, 26, NULL, ' Sony Xperia XZ - 3GB RAM,64GB,23MP Camera - Dual SIM - Black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">KEY FEATURES</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.2 inches, 1080 x 1920 pixels</li>\r\n	<li>Dual SIM</li>\r\n	<li>64GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>23MP Camera, 13MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>Qualcomm MSM8996 Snapdragon 820</li>\r\n	<li>IP68 certified - dust proof and water resistant over 1.5 meter and 30 minutes</li>\r\n	<li>Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow), planned upgrade to v7.0 (Nougat)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div class="container ps-module" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Helvetica neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, Tahoma, Verdana, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; width: 1247.81px; max-width: 1400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\r\n<div class="grid no-grid-at-767 spec-title-wrap" style="margin: 0px auto 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; width: 1146px; max-width: 1190px; position: relative; display: table;">\r\n<div class="span9" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; float: left; min-height: 1px; width: 849.375px;">\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">SIM CAPABILITY</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Single SIM, Nano SIM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">MEMORY AND STORAGE</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>4GB RAM, 64GB UFS internal memory<sup>3</sup>, microSDXC support</p>\r\n\r\n<p>(up to 256GB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">WEIGHT</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.5 oz</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">DIMENSIONS</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.1&quot; x 3.0&quot; x 0.3&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">DISPLAY</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.2&quot; FHD HDR Display, TRILUMINOS&trade; Display for mobile, X-Reality&reg; for mobile,</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dynamic Contrast Enhancer, sRGB 138%</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">CAMERA</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>19MP Motion Eye&trade; camera , 1/ 2.3&quot; Exmor RS&trade; for mobile memory-stacked</p>\r\n\r\n<p>sensor, 960 fps Super slow motion video, Predictive Capture (motion / smile),</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Autofocus burst, 13 MP front camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">ON THE INSIDE</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualcomm<sup>&reg;</sup>&nbsp;Snapdragon&trade; 835 Mobile Platform</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="grid no-grid-at-567 spec-section" style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 2.5em auto 0px; padding: 0px 0px 3.75em; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(228, 231, 235); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box; width: 1146.63px; max-width: 1190px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<p>Once again Sony has improved upon their camera technology with the XZ which now includes triple image sensing technology. Now you can capture the sharpest images even in challenging low light conditions. Add the lastest Snapdragon 820 chip, a winning Sony design &amp; great software coupled with&nbsp;IP68 water- and dust-resistant and you have a keeper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Perfectly Tailored for You</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia XZ&rsquo;s uncluttered design is meant to fit seamlessly into your life. The soft, rounded form is comfortable to hold, while the stunning colours are designed to suit your style.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for xperia xz design" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0O9GLKNAFAMZ/4af64efac3407973a9e7d2448eb120f0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:852px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:546px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>World Leading Smartphone&nbsp;Camera Technology</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThe smartphone camera with advanced movement and colour capture. So life looks as beautiful as it is.&nbsp;Xperia XZ comes loaded with the advanced photography technologies you recognize from other Xperia smartphones. We&rsquo;ve also added triple image sensing technology to analyse, adapt and capture perfect shots in challenging conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for xperia xz" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0O9GLKNAFAMZ/7be3039f85518d057b3a5e4b8fd4a95b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:243px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:564px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fast Improved Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia XZ perfects the fundamentals of a great smartphone. Packed with innovations in technology, it boasts a photo-pro&rsquo;s camera, an intelligent battery and smart features that adapt to you. And it&rsquo;s all delivered in a stunning, evolved design.&nbsp;Life&rsquo;s best subjects are rarely still for long. Xperia XZ allows you to capture even moving objects &ndash; before the moment passes you by. Bringing together the power of an imaging sensor and a laser autofocus sensor, you can freeze movement in the sharpest detail, even when the light is low.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for xperia xz" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0O9GLKNAFAMZ/b438132286679894ae9ed5adc9e0195c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Software that Learns from You</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia XZ is the smartphone that gets smarter and more personal as you use it. It learns and adapts based on how you use your phone, giving you the best smartphone experience to date.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for xperia xz" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0O9GLKNAFAMZ/b6a5a6918258b236525c3e60c0429925.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1285', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 52499, 49999, 1, 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-ram-64gb-23mp-camera-dual-sim-black.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-ram-64gb-23mp-camera-dual-sim-black-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-ram-64gb-23mp-camera-dual-sim-black-3.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-ram-64gb-23mp-camera-dual-sim-black-4.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-ram-64gb-23mp-camera-dual-sim-black-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-xz-3gb-ram-64gb-23mp-camera-dual-sim-black', '2017-09-18 18:15:53', '2017-09-18 18:15:53'),
(457, 1, 21, 61, 2, 26, NULL, 'Sony Xperia XA Ultra 3GB RAM,16GB ,21.5MP Camera- Black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>Key Features</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen size + Type:<strong>&nbsp;</strong>6.0&quot; IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Octa-core (4x2.0 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; 4x1.0 GHz Cortex-A53)</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 21.5MP Rear, 16MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 16GB ROM, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>SIM: Nano-SIM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">SIM CAPABILITY</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual SIM, Nano SIM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">MEMORY AND STORAGE</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to 200 GB microSD&trade; card</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">WEIGHT</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>202g</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">DIMENSIONS</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>164 x 79 x 8.4mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">DISPLAY</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>15.2 cm Full HD curved display, Mobile BRAVIA engine 2, Super Vivid mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">FRONT CAMERA</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>16 MP front camera Exmor RS&trade; for mobile sensor, Front flash, OIS (Optical Image Stabilization), Low light photography</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">MAIN CAMERA</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>21.5MP Exmor RS&trade; for mobile sensor, Quick launch and capture, Hybrid Auto-Focus</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">ON THE INSIDE</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Google Android 6.0 (Marshmallow), MediaTek MT6755, 64 bit Octa Core processor</p>\r\n', '<p>Upgrade your phone to the latest Sony Xperia XA Ultra that comes with the most amazing features. This phone has a 21.5 MP camera with an all new hybrid autofocus, a 64-bit Octa-Core processor and a 6.0inch HD display with curved glass. Its memory can be expanded to up to 200 GB with a micro SD card, giving you ample room to store your images, files and apps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL1HTT40NAFAMZ/0d222acd466ce67d5d83cc4b53dac9aa.jpg" style="height:270px; margin-top:62px; width:650px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Full HD Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This Phone boasts of its full HD display with curved glass. Sony has designed this phone for the sole purpose of the best viewing experience and performance. The curved edge display adds to the overall design statement of the Xperia XA Ultra.&nbsp; The display stretches to the full width of the phone and uses the Mobile BRAVIA engine 2. It is also provided with a Super-Vivid Mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL1HTT40NAFAMZ/96f16d59ad37c242ec8aa51e5503df11.jpg" style="height:359px; margin-top:0px; width:638px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Powerful Processor</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Sony Xperia XA Ultra hosts a 64-Bit Octa-Core processor which makes multitasking as easy and lag-free as possible. The 64-Bit Octo-Core processor enhances performance and the 3GB RAM makes the phone suitable for high speed utilizations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\