or &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Accelerometer &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Ambient light sensor &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Gyroscope &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Barometer &nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery Capacity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>3300mAh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2 style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:20px">Samsung Galaxy Note 8</span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>See the bigger picture and communicate in a whole new way. With the Galaxy Note8 in your hand, bigger things are just waiting to happen.&nbsp;&nbsp;The Samsung Galaxy Note 8 is powered by 1.6GHz octa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 835 processor and it comes with 6GB of RAM.&nbsp;&nbsp;Galaxy Note 8 packs a 12-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 8-megapixel front shooter for selfies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>6.3&quot; Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>More screen means more space to do great things. Go big with the Galaxy Note8&#39;s 6.3&quot; screen. It&#39;s the largest ever screen on a Note device and it still fits easily in your hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Samsung Note 8" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0BJCMGNAFAMZ/ab1a55caa823049927da364e2523816d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The S Pen</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Use the S Pen to express yourself in ways that make a difference. Draw your own emojis to show how you feel or write a message on a photo and send it as a handwritten note. Do things that matter with the S Pen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Samsung Note 8" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0BJCMGNAFAMZ/7f142d10dca626c2380e77fdd7ce5671.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Photos, clear and steady even in low light</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Get crisp photos even when it&#39;s dark and it&#39;s difficult to keep your phone steady. The Galaxy Note8&#39;s dual camera has a wide-angle camera that comes with the great low-light capabilities that you&#39;ve come to expect from Galaxy phones, while the telephoto camera gives you 2x optical zoom for you to capture the near and far. Both have optical image stabilization so you get steady shots even when zoomed in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Samsung Note 8 camera" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0BJCMGNAFAMZ/e1651bd3e3d69efef863cd9bfa736c33.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Do more with the high-performing phone</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&#39;re downloading games or multitasking, it&#39;s fast and seamless on the Galaxy Note8 because the high-performing 10nm mobile processor and 6GB RAM make things run smoothly. Plus, with wireless charging, power is on your side.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Connect to a bigger world with Phone+</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy Note8 is your portal to a new world when connected to this range of devices and interfaces. It&#39;s a world where boundaries are pushed and barriers broken so you can see more, share more, and do a whole lot more&mdash;effortlessly.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1204', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 110249, 104999, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-note-8-6-3-inch-single-sim-6gb-ram-color-midnight-black.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-note-8-6-3-inch-single-sim-6gb-ram-color-midnight-black-2.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-note-8-6-3-single-sim-6gb-ram-black', '2017-09-19 16:09:07', '2017-09-19 16:09:07'),
