(463, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy S6, 16MP Camera, 3GB RAM, Single SIM - Gold', '<h1><strong>Key Features</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display:&nbsp;Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>OS:&nbsp;Android OS, v5.0.2 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Processor:&nbsp;Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2.1 GHz Cortex-A57</li>\r\n	<li>Camera:&nbsp;16 MP, 2988 x 5312 pixels, optical image stabilization, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 32GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Sim Type:&nbsp;Nano-SIM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.1 inches (~70.7% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1440 x 2560 pixels (~577 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch</li>\r\n	<li>Protection: Corning Gorilla Glass 4</li>\r\n	<li>TouchWiz UI</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.0.2 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Exynos 7420</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2.1 GHz Cortex-A57</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali-T760MP8</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal 32GB, 3 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 16 MP, 2988 x 5312 pixels, optical image stabilization, autofocus, LED flash, check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, Auto HDR, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;2160p@30fps,&nbsp;1080p@60fps,&nbsp;720p@120fps, HDR, dual-video rec., check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5 MP,&nbsp;1440p@30fps, dual video call, Auto HDR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth v4.1, A2DP, LE, apt-X</li>\r\n	<li>GPS, with A-GPS, GLONASS, Beidou</li>\r\n	<li>NFC</li>\r\n	<li>Infrared port</li>\r\n	<li>USB microUSB v2.0, USB Host</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Other Features</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors Accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass, barometer, heart rate, SpO2</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>Browser HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless charging (Qi/PMA) - market dependent</li>\r\n	<li>ANT+ support</li>\r\n	<li>S-Voice natural language commands and dictation</li>\r\n	<li>Smart stay</li>\r\n	<li>OneDrive (115 GB cloud storage)</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/DivX/XviD/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 2550 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Galaxy S6</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Next is the most beautiful smartphones ever created. The&nbsp;Galaxy S6. With their slim, seamless, full metal and glass construction, the sleek, ultra thin edged Galaxy S6 is unparalled and true epitome of image is everything.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Related image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0NVBNCNAFAMZ/7a672027b0870f0ebc70cd783dcdcf97.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Beautifully crafted</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>And while they may be the thinnest smartphone ever created, when it comes to cutting-edge technology and flagship Galaxy experience, these 5.1&quot; QHD Super AMOLED smartphones are certainly no lightweights. Crafted from the finest materials, the S6 has seamless metal and glass body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Galaxy S6" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0NVBNCNAFAMZ/a502ca37c911894eaecafb3c63c7aecd.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Smarter Charging</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>When you&#39;re on the go and short on time, fear not - the Galaxy S6 feature the ability to fast charge your battery, letting you watch 2 hours of HD video from just 10 minutes charging. And with their built-in wireless charging capabilities, the Galaxy S6 offer you all the convenience of charging without the need to plug in ensuring you&rsquo;re always powered and ready for what&#39;s next.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0NVBNCNAFAMZ/705cd3108ab206318f25935216106bf7.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Better Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&#39;re into capturing stunning &lsquo;selfies&rsquo; or spectacular sunsets, the 5-megapixel front camera and 16-megapixel rear camera are ready when you are. With a launch time of just 0.7 seconds, you can capture more of your favourite moments, as they happen. And thanks to its Optical Image Stabilisation, fast tracking auto focus and bigger, f1.9 aperture for better low light results, every shot will be as amazing as the next.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0NVBNCNAFAMZ/63c2fc835bf9eb25dab341bc09360793.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1205', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 31799, 29999, 1, 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-gold.jpg', 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-gold-2.jpg', 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-gold-3.jpg', 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-gold-4.jpg', 'samsung-samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-gold-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-gold', '2017-09-19 16:28:46', '2017-09-19 16:28:46');
