\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Video Playing ResolutionFHD (1920 x 1080)@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Audio Playing FormatMP3, M4A, 3GA, AAC, OGG, OGA, WAV, WMA, AMR, AWB, FLAC, MID, MIDI, XMF, MXMF, IMY, RTTTL, RTX, OTA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 3600 mAh battery&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Talk time &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Up to 23 h (3G)</li>\r\n	<li>Music play &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Up to 59 h</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 dir="ltr" style="text-align:center"><strong>Samsung Galaxy A7 (2017)&nbsp;</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>Secured from unpredicted events</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr">The new Galaxy A7 (2017) Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow) comes with protection that lets you enjoy life without a worry. Equipped with IP68 to withstand the elements of nature, it shields out everything from water to dust in most situations. It also features a non-removable Li-Ion 3600 mAh battery experience faster charging so you can get on with more important day to day essentials. Order it online on Jumia and have it delivered to your doorstep.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr"><img alt="Image shows the highly water-resistant capabilities of the Galaxy A7 (2017) thanks to its IP68 rating." src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/my-feature-galaxy-a7-2017-a720f-61216063?$Download-Source$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:786px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:800px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir="ltr"><strong>M