(471, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy A7(2017), 5.7 inch, 3GB RAM, 16MP Camera, Dual SIM, 4G LTE, color - black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li>Display&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.7 inches (~71.5% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution&nbsp; 1080 x 1920 pixels (~386 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Memory &nbsp;&nbsp; Internal 32 GB, 3 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Card slot&nbsp; microSD, up to 256 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n	<li>Camera&nbsp;&nbsp;Primary16 MP</li>\r\n	<li>Battery&nbsp;&nbsp; Non-removable Li-Ion 3000 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">THE SMARTPHONE COMES WITH:</div>\r\n\r\n<ul dir="ltr">\r\n	<li>Galaxy phone</li>\r\n	<li>User manual</li>\r\n	<li>Charger</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Technical Specification</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CPU Speed&nbsp; 1.9 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; CPU Type&nbsp; Octa-Core</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Size (Main Display) 5.7 inches (~73.6% screen-to-body ratio)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Technology (Main Display) Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp; Protection &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Corning Gorilla Glass 4&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp