mage" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL15WE8KNAFAMZ/674c49ffdd483de4c7e2b54459fdf6a5.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>8MP Front-Facing Camera</strong><br />\r\nThe Xperia XA1 ultra &#39;s front-facing camera has a wide-angle lens and a hand shutter to trigger the perfect selfie.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL15WE8KNAFAMZ/473266452a44b727d61a4c7572353b5c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Borderless Design</strong><br />\r\n5&rdquo; borderless display with scratch-resistant Corning Gorilla Glass and curved glass edges.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1296', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 28033, 26698, 1, 'sony-xperia-xa1-ultra-23mp-8mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-6inch-white.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xa1-ultra-23mp-8mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-6inch-white-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xa1-ultra-23mp-8mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-6inch-white-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-xa1-ultra-23mp-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-white', '2017-09-19 17:50:29', '2017-09-19 17:50:29'),
(475, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy J7 pro, 13MP Camera, 4G LTE, color- Gold', '<h2><strong>Key Features</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Size:</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>5.5 inch&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Storage:</strong>&nbsp;32 GB</li>\r\n	<li><strong>RAM</strong>; 3GB</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Camera</strong>; 13 MP</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Operating System;</strong>&nbsp;Android 7</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Resolution;&nbsp;</strong>1080x1920 Pixels</li>\r\n	<li>color: Gold</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>DISPLAY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen size (inches); &nbsp;&nbsp; 5.50</li>\r\n	<li>Touchscreen; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution; &nbsp;&nbsp; 1080x1920 pixels</li>\r\n	<li>Pixels per inch (PPI); &nbsp;&nbsp; 401</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>HARDWARE</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Processor; &nbsp;&nbsp; 1.6GHz octa-core</li>\r\n	<li>Processor make; &nbsp;&nbsp; Exynos 7870</li>\r\n	<li>RAM ;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal storage; &nbsp; &nbsp;32GB</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage type; &nbsp;&nbsp; microSD</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage up to (GB) ;&nbsp;&nbsp; 128</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>CAMERA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rear camera&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;13-megapixel</li>\r\n	<li>Flash&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Front camera&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;13-megapixel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>SOFTWARE</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Android 7.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>CONNECTIVITY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi standards supported ;&nbsp; 802.11 b/g/n</li>\r\n	<li>GPS; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes, v 4.10</li>\r\n	<li>NFC ;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Infrared; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>USB OTG; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Headphones; &nbsp;&nbsp; 3.5mm</li>\r\n	<li>FM ;&nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Number of SIMs&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2<br />\r\nSIM 1&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GSM/CDM&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; GSM</li>\r\n	<li>3G&nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>4G/ LT&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSIM 2&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; No<br />\r\n4G/ LT&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSENSORS</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Compass/ Magnetometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Proximity sensor; &nbsp;&nbsp; Ye</li>\r\n	<li>Accelerometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Ambient light sensor; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Gyroscope; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Barometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature sensor; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>BATTERY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>3600 mAh battery</li>\r\n	<li>Talk time Up to 24 h (3G)</li>\r\n	<li>Music playUp to 91 h</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro (Gold)</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro smartphone was launched in June 2017. The phone comes with a 5.50-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 1080 pixels by 1920 pixels at a PPI of 401 pixels per inch. Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro price in India starts from Rs. 20,900. The Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro is powered by 1.6GHz octa-core Exynos 7870 processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone packs 16GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 128GB via a microSD card. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro packs a 13-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 13-megapixel front shooter for selfies.The Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro runs Android 7.0 and is powered by a 3600mAh non removable battery. It measures 152.40 x 74.70 x 7.90 (height x width x thickness) .The Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro is a dual SIM (GSM) . Connectivity options include Wi-Fi, GPS, Bluetooth, NFC, USB OTG and 4G (with support for Band 40 used by some LTE networks in India). Sensors on the phone include Compass Magnetometer, Proximity sensor, Accelerometer, Ambient light sensor and Gyroscope.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<img alt="Image result for samsung logo" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQlTQqiWEAwjxxbMzittwRLKa4iwdN9vbCKwVYpudm9lf4xLP0A" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Elegant by nature</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>When style complements functionality. Designed with the strictest attention to detail, the new Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro features a stunning uniform metal finish with zero camera protrusion for superior grip and 2.5D Glass shielding its 5.5&rdquo; Full HD Super AMOLED display for added durability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Elegant by nature" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/my-feature-elegant-by-nature-69713695?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:450px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:800px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Share life as you see it</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its rear 13 MP F1.7 camera captures clear photos with enhanced detail in low light while its intuitive interface enables one-handed functionality thanks to its moving shutter button so you can still take the shot while adjusting your pose or framing the scene.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Share life as you see it" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/my-feature-share-life-as-you-see-it-69713689?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:450px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:800px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Look great in every frame</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro lets you take bright and vivid selfies every time with more accurate detail even in low light thanks to its front LED and selfie flashes. You can also control the shutter by simple hand gesture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Look great in every frame" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/my-feature-look-great-in-every-frame-69713677?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:450px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:800px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Personalized gatekeeper</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy J7 Pro is engineered with a touch-based fingerprint sensor authentication to ensure your data is seen by you alone. You can also use this method for mobile payments, online sign in and verifying online accounts to ensure maximum protection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Personalized gatekeeper" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/my-feature-personalized-gatekeeper-69713691?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:450px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:800px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1211', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 31799, 29999, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-j7-pro-13mp-camera-4g-lte-color-gold.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-pro-13mp-camera-4g-lte-color-gold-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-pro-13mp-camera-4g-lte-color-gold-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j7-pro-13mp-camera-4g-lte-color-gold-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-j7-pro-13mp-camera-4g-lte-color-gold', '2017-09-19 17:53:12', '2017-09-19 17:53:12'),
(476, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung S6 Edge, 16MP Camera, 3GB RAM, Single SIM - black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Key Features</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System: Android v5.0.2</li>\r\n	<li>Camera Specs: 16 MegaPixels</li>\r\n	<li>Screen: 5.1&quot; 16M Super AMOLED Capacitive Touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 32GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 2600mAh Non-Removable</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: ARM Octa Core; 3.6 GHz</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>NETWORK</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2G: GSM 850 - 900 - 1800 - 1900&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>3G: HSDPA 850 - 900 - 1900 - 2100&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>4G: LTE</li>\r\n	<li>Sim: Nano-Sim</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>DISPLAY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.1 inches&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Type: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen,&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1440 x 2560 pixels&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>MEDIA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>MEMORY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal: 32 GB</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 3 GB<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>CONNECTIVITY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN: Wi-Fi 802.11 a-b-g-n-ac&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: Bluetooth v4.1</li>\r\n	<li>USB: microUSB v2.0&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nCAMERA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 16 MP 2988 x 5312 pixels, Optical Image Stabilization, Autofocus, LED Flash&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5 MP&nbsp;1080p@30fps, Dual Video Call, Auto HDR&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;2160p@30fps,&nbsp;1080p@60fps,&nbsp;720p@120fps, HDR&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>BATTERY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Battery capacity: 2600 mAh&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>FEATURES</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System: Android OS v5.0.2 (Lollipop)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>CPU Speed: 3.6 GHz&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>CPU Type: Octa-core&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Other Features:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>ANT+ support&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>S-Voice natural language commands and dictation&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Smart stay&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>OneDrive (115 GB cloud storage)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/DivX/XviD/WMV/H.264 player&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Document editor&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>A brilliant smartphone running on the Android 5.0.2 operating system, the Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge SM-G925 features a sleek design and has been sturdily built to be tough. It sports a 5.1-inch capacitive touchscreen which offers a 1440 x 2560 pixels resolution so every picture will be crystal clear and texts will be bold. The intuitive interface of the Galaxy S6 Edge gives a smooth user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It comes preinstalled with handy applications and games that will keep you engaged all day. You also have the option of adding more through the application store. With a built-in memory of 128GB, you can adequately save all your pictures, videos, songs and more.<br />\r\n<strong>Dazzling Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One fascinating feature of the Samsung Galaxy S6 is its sleek and bold 5.1 inch amoled display. Enclosed in a dazzling design, it features a sturdy chassis with a curved back that makes it sit comfortably in the hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fast Charging</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with a non-removable 2600mah battery, the SM-G925 charges fast that you would hardly notice the power lapse on your phone, so you are always on the go and your business at top-speed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Rich interactions with your edge</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy life on the fast lane with interactions with apps and games on your phone.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1212', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 37099, 34999, 1, 'samsung-s6-edge-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black.jpg', 'samsung-s6-edge-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black-2.jpg', 'samsung-s6-edge-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black-3.jpg', 'samsung-s6-edge-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black-4.jpg', 'samsung-s6-edge-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-s6-edge-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black', '2017-09-19 18:16:00', '2017-09-19 18:16:00'),
(477, 1, 21, 61, 2, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy Grand Prime Plus, 5.0-inch,Dual Sim- black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:16px"><strong>Key Features</strong></span></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1.4 GHz Quad-Core Processor</li>\r\n	<li>5.0 inch screen</li>\r\n	<li>8 MP Rear Camera + 5 MP Front Camera</li>\r\n	<li>8GB Memory, 1.5GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>4G LTE</li>\r\n	<li>1.5 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NETWORK</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Technology&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; GSM/HSPA/LTE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2G bands&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 - SIM 1 &amp; SIM 2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3G bands&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1900 / 2100</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4G bands&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; LTE band 1(2100), 3(1800), 5(850), 7(2600), 8(900), 20(800)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speed&nbsp;&nbsp; HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE Cat4 150/50 Mbps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPRS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>EDGE&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LAUNCH</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Announced&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2016, November</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Status&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Available. Released 2016, November</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BODY&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 144.8 x 72.1 x 8.9 mm (5.70 x 2.84 x 0.35 in)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 160 g (5.64 oz)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SIM&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hybrid Dual SIM (Micro-SIM, dual stand-by)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DISPLAY</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Type&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; PLS TFT capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5.0 inches (~66.0% screen-to-body ratio)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 540 x 960 pixels (~220 ppi pixel density)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multitouch&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PLATFORM</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Android 6.0 (Marshmallow)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chipset&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mediatek MT6737T</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPU&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Quad-core 1.4 GHz Cortex-A53</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPU&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mali-T720MP2</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MEMORY</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Card slot&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; microSD, up to 256 GB (uses SIM 2 slot)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8 GB, 1.5 GB RAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CAMERA</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Primary&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8 MP, f/2.2, autofocus, LED flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 720p@30fps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secondary&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5 MP, f/2.2, LED flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SOUND</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alert types&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Loudspeaker&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.5mm jack&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COMMS</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>WLAN&nbsp;&nbsp; Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bluetooth&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.2, A2DP, LE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Radio&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; FM radio, RDS, recording</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; microUSB 2.0, USB On-The-Go</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensors&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Accelerometer, proximity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Messaging&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Browser&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; HTML</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Java&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; No</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- MP4/H.264 player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- MP3/WAV/eAAC+/FLAC player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Photo/video editor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Document viewer</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BATTERY&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Removable Li-Ion 2600 mAh battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Talk time&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Up to 12 h (3G)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Music play&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Up to 59 h</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MISC&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Colors&nbsp;&nbsp; Black, Gold, Silver</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SAR EU&nbsp; 0.53 W/kg (head)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.27 W/kg (body)&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:20px"><strong>Samsung Product</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It has a 5.0-inch IPS display and&nbsp;a resolution of 960&times;540 pixels just qHD protected with Gorilla Glass. It has MediaTek MT6737T quad core processor (1.4Ghz ARM Cortex A-53) which essentially combines with 1.5 GB of RAM. The internal memory has a capacity of 8GB and can easily be expanded via a microSD card.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/84edbf168a55759fa673748b37d3d0be.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/84edbf168a55759fa673748b37d3d0be.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Premium Design</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Galaxy Grand Prime Plus features a sturdy case design with a non-slip rear grip pattern to keep it securely in your hand at all times. It also comes in a selection of stylish colours to complement your lifestyle while making an impression.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/4562d5a24647138049d447857efba5d2.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/4562d5a24647138049d447857efba5d2.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Selfies that Shine</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its trusty LED flash and 5 MP front camera capture you in your best light, even in dark conditions. And with Quick Launch, you get instant camera access by simply double tapping the home button, even from Sleep Mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/47ee14b58c6a0ba90518468a7302b2a1.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/47ee14b58c6a0ba90518468a7302b2a1.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Powerful Performance</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With upgraded RAM support and enhanced chipset performance you can enjoy seamless webpage load times for a more responsive multimedia and gaming experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/427d4c25160d34cb58e0cc8b031fb532.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/427d4c25160d34cb58e0cc8b031fb532.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bigger and Better</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Designed to expand your world of entertainment and gaming even further for the ultimate experience. Its optimal 5.0&rdquo; display is just the right size to view what&rsquo;s on screen for maximum enjoyment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/484796a28eaca0ada5e23de29f205794.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0QURE8NAFAMZ/484796a28eaca0ada5e23de29f205794.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1213', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 15359, 14627, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-5-0-inch-4g-dual-sim-color-black.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-5-0-inch-4g-dual-sim-color-black-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-5-0-inch-4g-dual-sim-color-black-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-5-0-inch-4g-dual-sim-color-black-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-g532f-5-0-inch-4g-dual-sim-color-black-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-grand-prime-plus-5-0-inch-dual-sim-black', '2017-09-19 18:30:43', '2017-09-19 18:30:43');
