(478, 1, 21, 61, 2, 26, NULL, 'Sony Xperia X( 23MPCamera,64GB 3GB,Dual SIM,5Inch) -  White', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Main Camera: 1/2&rdquo; 23MP, Sony Exmor RS Sensor , Predictive Hybrid AF. ISO 12800, 24mm Wide Sony G Lens<br />\r\nFront Camera: 1/3&rdquo; 13MP &ndash; Sony Exmor R Sensor, 22mm Wide, ISO 6400<br />\r\nDisplay: 5&ldquo; Full HD 1080p (1920x1080), Dynamic Contrast Enhancer, sRGB 140%, 600cd<br />\r\nCPU/GPU: Qualcomm Snapdragon 650, 2x 1.8GHz 4x 1.2GHz, Qualcomm Adreno 510<br />\r\nMemory: 3GB RAM, 32GB Flash memory, Up to 200GB Expandable Memory<br />\r\nBattery: 2620mAh, QNOVO Adaptive Quick Charge Technology<br />\r\nCharger: Quick Charger Included<br />\r\nAndroid Version: 6.01 - Marshmallow<br />\r\nPS4 Remote Play Compatible: Yes<br />\r\nSound: Hi-Res Audio, Stereo Speakers, Digital Noise Canceling, DSEE HX, LDAC, AHC<br />\r\nSize: 5.6 x 2.73 x 0.31 in / 5.4 oz<br />\r\nCompatible Networks: with GSM/LTE&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">SIM CAPABILITY</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual SIM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">MEMORY AND STORAGE</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Up to 200 GB microSD&trade; card</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">WEIGHT</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>152g</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">DIMENSIONS</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>143 x 69 x 7.7mm</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">DISPLAY</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>12.7cm Full HD 1080p, TRILUMINOS Display for mobile, X-Reality for mobile, Dynamic Contrast Enhancement</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">CAMERA</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>23MP, 1/2.3&#39;&#39; Exmor&trade; RS for mobile sensor, Quick launch , Predictive Hybrid AF, 5x Clear Image Zoom, 24mm G Lens F2.0, Low-light photography: ISO 12800 , Full HD 1080p Video Recording</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-family:sst w01 bold,helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:inherit">ON THE INSIDE</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Google Android 6.0 (Marshmallow), Qualcomm&reg; Snapdragon 650 Processor, 64-bit capable</p>\r\n', '<p>The Sony Xperia X is powered by octa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon&nbsp;MSM8956 Snapdragon 650&nbsp;processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone packs 64GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 256GB via a microSD card. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Sony Xperia X packs a 23-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 13-megapixel front shooter for selfies. The Sony Xperia X runs Android&nbsp;v6.0&nbsp;and is powered by a&nbsp;2620mAh non removable battery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0MA8H8NAFAMZ/9860f74a26c41ec05f38826273c6ff78.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There&#39;s never a good time for your phone to quit. Whether you&#39;re mid-run,or deep in a group chat. Xperia X&#39;s marathon battery brings you up to two days of power from every charge, so you can do what you love for longer. Explore more, connect more, and skip the charger in your bag. While most smartphone batteries quickly decline in&nbsp;strength, Xperia X &nbsp;delivers our Sony&#39;s largest battery lifespan. Ground breaking Qnovo Adaptive Charging maintains battery health while charging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0MA8H8NAFAMZ/617b32476699b75dc14d47932add9e8c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:315px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:539px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h1><strong>Perfect Camera</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The most shareable moments tend to be the hardest to capture. To help you get the shots you want, the xperia X comes with Sony&#39;s flagship camera which is faster and smarter than ever &ndash; with quicker response times and even more intelligent focus.Xperia X&#39;s smart capture technology helps banish blur. Enabled by Sony&#39;s new Predictive Hybrid Autofocus, smart capture lets you choose a person or object and automatically track it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0MA8H8NAFAMZ/883a500a8d7b360b5cf89713a98f14a0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fits Life Like a Glove</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The xperia X is designed to comfortably fit your hand,your routines and your taste. We&#39;ve refined the user interface to make it more intuitive than ever,and continued with a form that makes a statement with its simplicity. Each of the Xperia X&#39;S colours has been designed o complement your personal taste without taking over.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0MA8H8NAFAMZ/6f99be178a0916625bac2ae957bf3e64.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:340px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:605px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1297', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 35699, 33999, 1, 'sony-xperia-x-23mpcamera-64gb-3gb-dual-sim-5inch-white.jpg', 'sony-xperia-x-23mpcamera-64gb-3gb-dual-sim-5inch-white-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-x-23mpcamera-64gb-3gb-dual-sim-5inch-white-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-x-23mpcamera-64gb-3gb-dual-sim-5inch-white', '2017-09-19 18:34:25', '2017-09-19 18:34:25'),
