eight: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">accelerometer&nbsp;proximity sensor and a compass.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1300', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 26250, 25000, 1, 'sony-xperia-m5-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-3gb-ram-5inches-white.jpg', 'sony-xperia-m5-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-3gb-ram-5inches-white-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-m5-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-3gb-ram-5inches-white-3.jpg', 'sony-xperia-m5-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-3gb-ram-5inches-white-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-m5-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-3gb-ram-5inches-white', '2017-09-19 19:03:01', '2017-09-19 19:03:01'),
(484, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy S6, 16MP Camera, 3GB RAM, Single SIM - Black', '<h2><strong>Key Features</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display:&nbsp;Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>OS:&nbsp;Android OS, v5.0.2 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Processor:&nbsp;Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2.1 GHz Cortex-A57</li>\r\n	<li>Camera:&nbsp;16 MP, 2988 x 5312 pixels, optical image stabilization, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 32GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Sim Type:&nbsp;Nano-SIM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.1 inches (~70.7% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1440 x 2560 pixels (~577 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch</li>\r\n	<li>Protection: Corning Gorilla Glass 4</li>\r\n	<li>TouchWiz UI</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.0.2 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Exynos 7420</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2.1 GHz Cortex-A57</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali-T760MP8</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal 32GB, 3 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 16 MP, 2988 x 5312 pixels, optical image stabilization, autofocus, LED flash, check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, Auto HDR, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;2160p@30fps,&nbsp;1080p@60fps,&nbsp;720p@120fps, HDR, dual-video rec., check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5 MP,&nbsp;1440p@30fps, dual video call, Auto HDR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth v4.1, A2DP, LE, apt-X</li>\r\n	<li>GPS, with A-GPS, GLONASS, Beidou</li>\r\n	<li>NFC</li>\r\n	<li>Infrared port</li>\r\n	<li>USB microUSB v2.0, USB Host</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Other Features</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors Accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass, barometer, heart rate, SpO2</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>Browser HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless charging (Qi/PMA) - market dependent</li>\r\n	<li>ANT+ support</li>\r\n	<li>S-Voice natural language commands and dictation</li>\r\n	<li>Smart stay</li>\r\n	<li>OneDrive (115 GB cloud storage)</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/DivX/XviD/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 2550 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Galaxy S6</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Next is the most beautiful smartphones ever created. The&nbsp;Galaxy S6. With their slim, seamless, full metal and glass construction, the sleek, ultra thin edged Galaxy S6 is unparalled and true epitome of image is everything.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Related image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0NVBNCNAFAMZ/7a672027b0870f0ebc70cd783dcdcf97.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Beautifully crafted</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>And while they may be the thinnest smartphone ever created, when it comes to cutting-edge technology and flagship Galaxy experience, these 5.1&quot; QHD Super AMOLED smartphones are certainly no lightweights. Crafted from the finest materials, the S6 has seamless metal and glass body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Galaxy S6" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0NVBNCNAFAMZ/a502ca37c911894eaecafb3c63c7aecd.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Smarter Charging</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>When you&#39;re on the go and short on time, fear not - the Galaxy S6 feature the ability to fast charge your battery, letting you watch 2 hours of HD video from just 10 minutes charging. And with their built-in wireless charging capabilities, the Galaxy S6 offer you all the convenience of charging without the need to plug in ensuring you&rsquo;re always powered and ready for what&#39;s next.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0NVBNCNAFAMZ/705cd3108ab206318f25935216106bf7.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Better Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&#39;re into capturing stunning &lsquo;selfies&rsquo; or spectacular sunsets, the 5-megapixel front camera and 16-megapixel rear camera are ready when you are. With a launch time of just 0.7 seconds, you can capture more of your favourite moments, as they happen. And thanks to its Optical Image Stabilisation, fast tracking auto focus and bigger, f1.9 aperture for better low light results, every shot will be as amazing as the next.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SA948EL0NVBNCNAFAMZ/63c2fc835bf9eb25dab341bc09360793.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1216', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 31799, 29999, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-s6-16mp-camera-3gb-ram-single-sim-black', '2017-09-19 19:08:18', '2017-09-19 19:08:18'),
(485, 1, 21, 61, 2, 26, NULL, ' Sony Xperia Z5 Premium (23MP,32GB, 3GB RAM,Dual SIM) -Black', '<div class="detail-features" style="box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 230px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">\r\n<div class="list -features -compact -no-float" style="box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; border-top: 1px solid rgb(233, 233, 233); padding: 10px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px;">\r\n<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong>Key Features</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory: 32GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Display Size:&nbsp;5.5 inches&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:inherit">4K Ultra HD display</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:inherit">23 MP Hybrid AF camera</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-family:inherit; font-size:inherit">Up to 2 days battery life</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="details-footer" style="box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; border-top: 1px solid rgb(233, 233, 233); padding: 10px 0px 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">\r\n<div class="price-box" style="box-sizing: border-box; float: left; width: 220px; margin-top: 5px;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size:&nbsp;5.5 inches (~70.4% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 2160 x 3840 pixels (~806 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch:&nbsp;up to 10 fingers</li>\r\n	<li>Protection:&nbsp;Scratch-resistant glass, oleophobic coating</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset:&nbsp;Qualcomm MSM8994 Snapdragon 810</li>\r\n	<li>CPU:&nbsp;Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2 GHz Cortex-A57</li>\r\n	<li>GPU:&nbsp;Adreno 430</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 200GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 32GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 23 MP, f/2.0, 24mm, phase detection autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features: 1/2.3&quot; sensor size, geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, HDR, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;2160p@30fps,&nbsp;1080p@60fps,&nbsp;720p@120fps, HDR, check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:&nbsp;5.1 MP, f/2.4, 1080p, HDR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Network</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Technology:&nbsp;GSM / HSPA / LTE</li>\r\n	<li>2G bands:&nbsp;GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900</li>\r\n	<li>3G bands:&nbsp;HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1900 / 2100 - E6853</li>\r\n	<li>4G bands:&nbsp;LTE band 1(2100), 2(1900), 3(1800), 4(1700/2100), 5(850), 7(2600), 8(900), 12(700), 17(700), 20(800), 28(700), 38(2600), 40(2300) - E6853</li>\r\n	<li>Speed:&nbsp;HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE Cat6 300/50 Mbps</li>\r\n	<li>GPRS:&nbsp;Up to 107 kbps</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE: Up to 296 kbps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sound</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n	<li>High-Res audio</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Comms</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN:&nbsp;Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, DLNA, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: v4.1, A2DP, apt-X</li>\r\n	<li>GPS with A-GPS, GLONASS/ BDS (market dependant)</li>\r\n	<li>NFC</li>\r\n	<li>Radio:&nbsp;FM radio with RDS</li>\r\n	<li>USB:&nbsp;microUSB v2.0 (MHL 3 TV-out), USB Host</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 3430 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>The&nbsp;<strong>Sony Xperia Z5 Premium</strong>&nbsp;is powered by a&nbsp;Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2 GHz Cortex-A57 processor. The phone packs 32GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 200GB via a microSD card. The 23&nbsp;megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 5.1-megapixel front camera let you take amazing photos everywhere you go.&nbsp;It runs on Android 5.1.1 and is powered by a Non-removable Li-Ion 3430 mAh battery to give you the ultimate user experience.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/0d222acd466ce67d5d83cc4b53dac9aa.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>4K Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Imagine the best of Sony TV technologies delivered in a smartphone. A super-vivid and sharp display, right in the palm of your hand. Meet Xperia Z5 Premium. With a 4K Ultra HD display, this 5.5&rdquo; smartphone packs in four times the resolution of Full HD for an unrivaled viewing experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/1e7c8025e573190f442843c4d2112e1f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:269px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Capture Important Moments in 4K</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With Xperia Z5 Premium you can capture the world in incredible high-resolution 4K video. This means your videos have four times the detail of Full HD. Add to that a host of Sony&rsquo;s Handycam technologies, including SteadyShot&trade; for stable videos, and you can count on flawless footage.&nbsp;The Xperia Z5 Premium scales up your photos and movies to incredible 4K quality, while retaining every detail. In fact, it makes everything look better than ever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/c1ab4f4eb43eef9e024ee8efe932bdd0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:221px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Beautiful Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia Z5 Premium isn&rsquo;t shy. It loves to be noticed. Available in chrome, black and gold, it is precision-etched with the Xperia&trade; mark and finished with a stunning mirror effect on the back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/7296d70cd9c91517c14c60a8a4aafce8.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Connect to your TV</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ve captured a stunning video, now show off every detail on a 4K TV. Connect instantly over Wi-Fi&reg; using DLNA, or use an MHL 3.0 connector. Enjoy your videos on your TV from your&nbsp;Xperia Z5 Premium&nbsp;at the comfort of your couch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/7ebda2ac00128a369c09ee510da07dde.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Long Lasting Battery</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>For this powerhouse of a 4K smartphone, Sony has gathered all its battery know-how to bring you up to two days&nbsp;battery life. Watch more films, listen to more music, carry on chatting and stay out without a care. When you do need topping up, Xperia Z5 Premium can be used together with our Quick Charger for hours of power in just 10 minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/8c9fcceab1bd103a5d4b000e5396a7e1.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:221px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fingerprint Sensor</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia Z5 Premium&rsquo;s power button has our new, integrated fingerprint sensor. Intuitively placed on the side of the phone, you can pick up and securely unlock your phone in a single movement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/51e688efe5a4eb39f78a02c230f0bd6b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:320px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1301', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 47039, 44799, 1, 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black-3.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black', '2017-09-19 19:16:33', '2017-09-19 19:16:33');
