(486, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung J1 ACE, 512MB RAM, 4GB, Dual SIM -color - Black', '<h2><strong><span style="font-size:20px">Key Features</span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size: 4.3&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>Display Type:&nbsp;&nbsp;Super AMOLED,&nbsp;480x800 pixels</li>\r\n	<li>Camera : 5.0 Megapixel, Front 2MP</li>\r\n	<li>RAM + Storage :&nbsp; 4 GB,&nbsp;512MB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Operating System : Android 4.4</li>\r\n	<li>Battery&nbsp;Type : Li - Ion&nbsp;1800 mAh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NETWORK&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Technology&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; GSM/HSPA/LTE</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>LAUNCH&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Announced&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2015, September</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Status&nbsp;&nbsp; Available. Released 2015, October</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BODY&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 130.1 x 67.6 x 9.5 mm (5.12 x 2.66 x 0.37 in)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weight 131 g (4.62 oz)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SIM&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Single SIM (Micro-SIM) or Dual SIM (Micro-SIM, dual stand-by)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DISPLAY&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Type&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.3 inches (~59.8% screen-to-body ratio)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 480 x 800 pixels (~217 ppi pixel density)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multitouch&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PLATFORM&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Android 4.4.4 (KitKat)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chipset&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Spreadtrum SC9830</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Marvell PXA1908 - J110L</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CPU&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A7 - J111F</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quad-core 1.2 GHz Cortex-A7</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A53- J110L</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPU&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mali-400MP2</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vivante GC7000 UL - J110L</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MEMORY&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Card slot&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; micro SD, up to 256 GB (dedicated slot)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4 GB, 512 MB RAM - J110L</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4 GB, 768 MB RAM - J110F, J110G</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8 GB, 1 GB RAM - J110M, J111F</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CAMERA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Primary&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5 MP, f/2.2, 31mm, autofocus, LED flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, panorama</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Video&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 720p@30fps</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secondary&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2 MP</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SOUND </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alert types&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Loudspeaker&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.5mm jack&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COMMS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>WLAN&nbsp;&nbsp; Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bluetooth&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.0, A2DP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Radio&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; FM radio, RDS, recording</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; microUSB 2.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensors&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Accelerometer, proximity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Messaging&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SMS (threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Browser&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; HTML</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Java&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; No</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- MP4/H.264 player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- MP3/WAV/eAAC+/Flac player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Photo/video editor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Document viewer</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BATTERY&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Removable Li-Ion 1900 mAh battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Talk time&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Up to 10 h (3G)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Music play&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Up to 68 h</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MISC&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Colors&nbsp;&nbsp; White, Black, Blue</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SAR&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.57 W/kg (head)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.22 W/kg (body)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SAR EU&nbsp; 0.69 W/kg (head)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0.53 W/kg (body)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Samsung Galaxy J1 Ace</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy J1 Ace J111F is 2016-released mid-range smartphone launched by the tech giant Samsung. It comes with myriad useful functionalities which are ideal for the current Android mobile phone enthusiasts. Featuring a stylish 9.5mm thin profile, the handset comes with 4.3-inch Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen sporting 800 x 480 pixels resolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy J1 is backed by a Quad-core 1.5GHz processor and 1GB of RAM. It offers prompt multitasking and fast web browsing on the go. It comes with 8GB internal storage further expandable up to 128GB through microSD card slot. The device offers good quality graphics that let you enjoy stunning viewing experience while watching your favourite video stuff. The Galaxy J1 runs Android OS with easy access to Google Play Store from where you can download apps, games and loads more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The smartphone has 5MP primary camera with features including autofocus, LED flash, touch focus, Geo-tagging, face detection, panorama and 720p video recording @30fps. There is another 2MP front camera for video calling and selfies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Other notable features of the mobile phone include 4G LTE connectivity, Dual SIM (One 3G/4G SIM and One 2G SIM), Wi-Fi 80.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, Bluetooth v4.0 with A2DP, GPS with A-GPS and GLONASS, Accelerometer, Proximity, microUSB v2.0, 3.5mm audio jack and Li-Ion 1900mAh battery.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1219', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 10599, 9999, 1, 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-black.jpg', 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-black-2.jpg', 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-black-3.jpg', 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-black-4.jpg', 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-black-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-black', '2017-09-19 19:27:54', '2017-09-19 19:27:54'),
(487, 1, 21, 61, 2, 26, NULL, 'Sony Xperia XZ Premium  (4GB RAM, 64GB  23 MP Camera Dual SIM) Black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>Key Features</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.2 inches, 1080 x 1920 pixels&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Dual SIM</li>\r\n	<li>64GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>23MP Camera, 13MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>Qualcomm MSM8996 Snapdragon 820</li>\r\n	<li>Dust proof and water resistant over 1.5 meter and 30 minutes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Technical Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SYSTEM&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:&nbsp;Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow), planned upgrade to v7.0 (Nougat)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset:&nbsp;Qualcomm MSM8996 Snapdragon 820</li>\r\n	<li>CPU:&nbsp;Quad-core (2x2.15 GHz Kryo &amp; 2x1.6 GHz Kryo)</li>\r\n	<li>GPU:&nbsp;Adreno 530</li>\r\n	<li>MEMORY:&nbsp;microSD, up to 256 GB (uses SIM 2 slot) - dual SIM</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 64 GB, 3 GB RAM&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DISPLAY&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size:&nbsp;5.2 inches (~70.9% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels (~424 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Protection:&nbsp;Corning Gorilla Glass (unspecified version)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>- Triluminos display<br />\r\n- X-Reality Engine</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CAMERA&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:&nbsp;23 MP, f/2.0, 24mm, EIS (gyro), phase detection and laser autofocus, LED flash, check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Features:&nbsp;1/2.3&quot; sensor size, geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, HDR, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;2160p@30fps,&nbsp;1080p@30fps,&nbsp;1080p@60fps, check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:&nbsp;13 MP, f/2.0, 22mm, 1/3&quot; sensor size, 1080p, HDR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>NETWORK</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GSM / HSPA / LTE</li>\r\n	<li>2G bands: GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 - SIM 1 &amp; SIM 2 (dual-SIM model only)</li>\r\n	<li>3G bands: HSDPA 800 / 850 / 900 / 1700(AWS) / 1900 / 2100 - F8331, F8332</li>\r\n	<li>4G bands: LTE band 1(2100), 2(1900), 3(1800), 4(1700/2100), 5(850), 7(2600), 8(900), 12(700), 13(700), 17(700), 19(800), 20(800), 26(850), 28(700), 29(700), 32(1500), 38(2600), 39(1900), 40(2300), 41(2500) - F8331, F8332</li>\r\n	<li>Speed:&nbsp;HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE Cat9 450/50 Mbps</li>\r\n	<li>GPRS:&nbsp;Yes</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE:&nbsp;Yes</li>\r\n	<li>SIM: Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Perfectly Tailored for You</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia XZ&rsquo;s uncluttered design is meant to fit seamlessly into your life. The soft, rounded form is comfortable to hold, while the stunning colours are designed to suit your style.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for xperia xz design" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0IOHN8NAFAMZ/4af64efac3407973a9e7d2448eb120f0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:852px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:546px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>World Leading Smartphone&nbsp;Camera Technology</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThe smartphone camera with advanced movement and colour capture. So life looks as beautiful as it is.&nbsp;Xperia XZ comes loaded with the advanced photography technologies you recognize from other Xperia smartphones. We&rsquo;ve also added triple image sensing technology to analyse, adapt and capture perfect shots in challenging conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for xperia xz" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0IOHN8NAFAMZ/7be3039f85518d057b3a5e4b8fd4a95b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:243px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:564px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fast Improved Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia XZ perfects the fundamentals of a great smartphone. Packed with innovations in technology, it boasts a photo-pro&rsquo;s camera, an intelligent battery and smart features that adapt to you. And it&rsquo;s all delivered in a stunning, evolved design.&nbsp;Life&rsquo;s best subjects are rarely still for long. Xperia XZ allows you to capture even moving objects &ndash; before the moment passes you by. Bringing together the power of an imaging sensor and a laser autofocus sensor, you can freeze movement in the sharpest detail, even when the light is low.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for xperia xz" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0IOHN8NAFAMZ/b438132286679894ae9ed5adc9e0195c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Software that Learns from You</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia XZ is the smartphone that gets smarter and more personal as you use it. It learns and adapts based on how you use your phone, giving you the best smartphone experience to date.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for xperia xz" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0IOHN8NAFAMZ/429d22f092a3407a032e7d9dcd8a7015.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1302', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 73499, 69999, 1, 'sony-xperia-xz-premium-4gb-ram-64gb-23-mp-camera-dual-sim-black.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-premium-4gb-ram-64gb-23-mp-camera-dual-sim-black-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-premium-4gb-ram-64gb-23-mp-camera-dual-sim-black-3.jpg', 'sony-xperia-xz-premium-4gb-ram-64gb-23-mp-camera-dual-sim-black-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-xz-premium-4gb-ram-64gb-23-mp-camera-dual-sim-black', '2017-09-19 19:34:48', '2017-09-19 19:34:48'),
