&nbsp; Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bluetooth&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4.0, A2DP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Radio&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; FM radio, RDS, recording</p>\r\n\r\n<p>USB&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; microUSB 2.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensors&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Accelerometer, proximity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Messaging&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; SMS (threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Browser&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; HTML</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Java&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; No</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- MP4/H.264 player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- MP3/WAV/eAAC+/Flac player</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Photo/video editor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>- Document viewer</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BATTERY&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Removable Li-Ion 1900 mAh battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Talk time&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Up to 10 h (3G)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Music play&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Up to 68 h</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MISC&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Colors&nbsp;&nbsp; White, Black, Blue</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SAR&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.57 W/kg (head)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1.22 W/kg (body)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SAR EU&nbsp; 0.69 W/kg (head)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0.53 W/kg (body)&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Samsung Galaxy J1 Ace</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy J1 Ace J111F is 2016-released mid-range smartphone launched by the tech giant Samsung. It comes with myriad useful functionalities which are ideal for the current Android mobile phone enthusiasts. Featuring a stylish 9.5mm thin profile, the handset comes with 4.3-inch Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen sporting 800 x 480 pixels resolution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy J1 is backed by a Quad-core 1.5GHz processor and 1GB of RAM. It offers prompt multitasking and fast web browsing on the go. It comes with 8GB internal storage further expandable up to 128GB through microSD card slot. The device offers good quality graphics that let you enjoy stunning viewing experience while watching your favourite video stuff. The Galaxy J1 runs Android OS with easy access to Google Play Store from where you can download apps, games and loads more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The smartphone has 5MP primary camera with features including autofocus, LED flash, touch focus, Geo-tagging, face detection, panorama and 720p video recording @30fps. There is another 2MP front camera for video calling and selfies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Other notable features of the mobile phone include 4G LTE connectivity, Dual SIM (One 3G/4G SIM and One 2G SIM), Wi-Fi 80.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, Bluetooth v4.0 with A2DP, GPS with A-GPS and GLONASS, Accelerometer, Proximity, microUSB v2.0, 3.5mm audio jack and Li-Ion 1900mAh battery.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1220', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 10599, 9999, 1, 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-white.jpg', 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-white-2.jpg', 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-white-3.jpg', 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-white-4.jpg', 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-white-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-j1-ace-512mb-ram-4gb-dual-sim-color-white', '2017-09-19 20:10:34', '2017-09-19 20:10:34'),
(489, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Galaxy S7 (Dual Sim), 32GB, 12MP Camera, 4GB RAM, color - Gold', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 5.1 inches (~72.1% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Memory : 32 GB,</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 4 GB&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Camera:<strong>&nbsp;</strong>(&nbsp;Primary) :12 MP,</li>\r\n	<li>Battery:&nbsp;Non-removable Li-Ion 3000 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>DISPLAY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>5.1 inches (~72.1% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>1440 x 2560 pixels (~577 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch</li>\r\n	<li>Protection:Corning Gorilla Glass 4</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Always-on display</li>\r\n	<li>TouchWiz UI</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PLATFORM</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chip: set:&nbsp;Qualcomm MSM8996 Snapdragon 820&nbsp;or Exynos 8890 Octa</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Dual-core 2.15 GHz Kryo &amp; dual-core 1.6 GHz Kryo or&nbsp;Quad-core 2.3 GHz Mongoose + quad-core 1.6 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>GPU:&nbsp;Adreno 530 or&nbsp;Mali-T880 MP12</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>MEMORY&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slotmicroSD, up to 200 GB (dedicated slot) -</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 32 GB, 4 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>CAMERA</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:12 MP, f/1.7, 26mm, phase detection autofocus, OIS, LED flash,&nbsp;check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Features: 1/2.6&quot; sensor size, 1.4 &micro;m pixel size, geo-tagging, simultaneous 4K video and 9MP image recording, touch focus, face/smile detection, Auto HDR, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Video:2160p@30fps,&nbsp;1080p@60fps,&nbsp;720p@240fps, HDR, dual-video rec.,&nbsp;check quality</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:5 MP, f/1.7, 22mm, dual video call, Auto HDR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>SOUND</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert typesVibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>COMMUNICATION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN:Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetoothv:4.2, A2DP, LE, apt-X</li>\r\n	<li>GPS with A-GPS, GLONASS, BDS</li>\r\n	<li>NFC</li>\r\n	<li>USB:microUSB v2.0, USB Host</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FEATURES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SensorsFingerprint, accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass, barometer, heart rate, SpO2</li>\r\n	<li>MessagingSMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>BrowserHTML5</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Fast battery charging: 60% in 30 min (Quick Charge 2.0)</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless charging (Qi/PMA) - market dependent</li>\r\n	<li>ANT+ support</li>\r\n	<li>S-Voice natural language commands and dictation</li>\r\n	<li>OneDrive (115 GB cloud storage)</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/DivX/XviD/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>BATTERY&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 3000 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Samsung Galaxy S7</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy S7 unlocks a Galaxy of technology that takes your smartphone experience to a new level. The bigger, more stunning screen completes the slimmer design.Why not have a phone that&rsquo;s water resistant, too?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Incredible Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy S7 proves that less can actually be more. The big screen on an incredibly slim design keeps you fully engaged in movies, games and more. Plus, with the always on display, you get the time or notifications without waking your screen. And when you&rsquo;re finished, just slip Galaxy S7 back into the pocket of your favourite jeans.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Big on screen, slim on profile" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-2?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=ffffff&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Water and Dust&nbsp;Resistant&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Worry less about daily wear and tear of your phone. Galaxy S7 has an IP68 rating&nbsp;meaning not only protection against dust, it also repels splashes, spills and even dunks. Simply wipe it off and move along.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Water-resistant smartphone" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-3?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=f6f6f6&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Take charge of the charge</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Fast, wireless charging++ lets you power Galaxy S7 from 0&ndash;100% in virtually no time. And with Samsung Galaxy&rsquo;s biggest battery* (3000 mAH) in their thinnest device, Galaxy S7 gives you power to keep going even on those extra long days.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Take charge of the charge" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-5?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=ffffff&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Faster Better camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy S7 has a dual&ndash;pixel camera with faster, more precise autofocus&nbsp;and a new low&ndash;light sensor. All combined, it means fewer blurry photos and crisp detail even in soft light. Also, get brighter selfies in low&ndash;light settings, thanks to the device&rsquo;s selfie flash.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Brighter, better, faster photos" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-4?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=e5e3e4&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1221', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 52999, 49999, 1, 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-white.jpg', 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-white-2.jpg', 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-white-3.jpg', 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-white-4.jpg', 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-white-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-gold', '2017-09-19 20:26:50', '2017-09-19 20:26:50'),
(490, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy J2,  8GB, 1GB RAM, 5MP Camera, 4G LTE color-White', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 4.7 inches, Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>OS : Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Memory : Internal 8GB, 1GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A7</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: &nbsp;5 MP Rear, 2MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: Li-Ion 2 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen Size: 4.7 inches</li>\r\n	<li>Type: Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 72 x 128 pixels (~294 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:&nbsp; Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Qualcomm MSM8916 Snapdragon 41</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A7</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali-T72</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 128 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 8GB, 1 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:&nbsp;5 MP, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;72p@3fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:&nbsp;2 MP, LED flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Network</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Technology: GSM / HSPA / LTE</li>\r\n	<li>2G bands: GSM 85 / 9 / 18 / 19 - SIM 1 &amp; SIM 2</li>\r\n	<li>3G bands: HSDPA 85 / 9 / 19 / 21</li>\r\n	<li>Speed: HSPA 21.1/5.76 Mbps</li>\r\n	<li>GPRS: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>4G: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sound</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Comms: WLANWi-Fi 82.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: v4.1, A2DP</li>\r\n	<li>GPS: Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS</li>\r\n	<li>Radio: FM radio with RDS; recording</li>\r\n	<li>USB: microUSB v2.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors: Accelerometer, proximity</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging: SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>Browser: HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>Java: No</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;ANT+ support</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Li-Ion 2 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Watch crystal clear videos on the large 11.93 (4.7) super AMOLED display of the Samsung Galaxy smartphone. With 54 x 96 pixels screen resolution, every image is displayed with excellent clarity and details. The super AMOLED display ensures deeper contrast and true-to-life colours for an immersive viewing experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Ultra-Data Saving</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With ultra-data saving feature you can seamless save data while you stream videos, browse your favourite apps or shop online. This advanced feature compresses the data and restricts background apps from consuming data.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Capture Amazing Moments</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy J Series come with powerful camera that captures brilliant shots even in low light conditions. It also comes with an Advanced Mode that gives you an enhanced imaging experience. You can choose from different image Modes to suit different occasions so that you get pictures that look more real.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Seamless Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Powered by a 1.3 GHz&nbsp; Quad Core processor, the GALAXY J2&nbsp; will seamlessly perform a wide range of tasks including gaming, watching movies, and surfing the web. Also with support for HSPA+, you&rsquo;ll experience blazing-fast download and upload speeds. With the enhanced productivity and greater efficiency provided by the GALAXY J2, you can spend less time waiting and more time doing.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1222', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 13249, 12499, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-4g-lte-color-white.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-4g-lte-color-white-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-4g-lte-color-white-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-4g-lte-color-white-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-4g-lte-color-white-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-j2-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-4g-lte-color-white', '2017-09-20 14:36:12', '2017-09-20 14:36:12'),
