em, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: baseline; zoom: 1; color: rgb(17, 17, 17);">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn " style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-text" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Sony Xperia Z5 Dual, as the name suggests is a dual-SIM variant of the flagship phone from Sony. The smartphone comes with two nano SIM slots which are both 4G LTE enabled and comes with a wide range of premium features such as a 23-megapixel rear shooter along with a full HD display.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn " style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-text" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">The&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mysmartprice.com/mobile/pricelist/sony-xperia-mobiles.html" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 102, 192);">Xperia</a>&nbsp;device is available in four colour options, green, god, graphite black and white. It sports a 5.2-inch LCD touchscreen display which has full HD (1920x1080 pixels) screen resolution.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn " style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-text" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">The Sony Xperia Z5 Dual really stands out in the imaging department thanks to the1/2.3 Exmor RS sensor capable of clicking images up to a resolution of 23-megapixels. The sensor is accompanied by a F/2.0 lens. The rear shooter also boasts of improved image stabilization techniques which ensure that videos are flawlessly captured even in low-light condition. The device also boasts of in incredible autofocus time of 0.037 seconds. In addition, the device also comes with a 5-megapixel front shooter capable of capturing beautiful selfies in high definition.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn " style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-text" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Under the hood, the smartphone comes with a Qualcomm Snapdragon 810 chipset having an octa-core 64-bit processor. The SoC also comes with&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mysmartprice.com/mobile/pricelist/3gb-ram-mobiles-in-india.html" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 102, 192);">3GB&nbsp;RAM</a>, all of which ensure that the device never stutters in performance even if you have a multitude of applications running. Storage options on the smartphone come as&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mysmartprice.com/mobile/pricelist/32gb-internal-memory-mobiles-in-india.html" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 102, 192);">32 GB</a>&nbsp;of internal storage space. This translates to about 27 GB of usable storage for apps and media. However, the device does come with a microSD card slot which can be used to bump up to the storage up to 200 GB.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 20px 0px 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-dscrptn " style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="prdct-dscrptn__item-text" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">In terms of connectivity, the smartphone comes with&nbsp;<a href="http://www.mysmartprice.com/mobile/pricelist/4g-mobiles-in-india.html" style="box-sizing: content-box; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; padding: 0px; border: 0px; margin: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 102, 192);">4G LTE</a>&nbsp;connectivity on both the SIM slots and comes with dual active technology which makes sure both the slots are active. In addition, the phone comes with Bluetooth 4.1, Wi-Fi b/g/n and a microUSB 2.0 slot.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1303', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 39374, 37499, 1, 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-white-color.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-white-color-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-white-color-3.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-white-color-4.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-white-color-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-white-color', '2017-09-21 08:51:50', '2017-09-21 08:51:50'),
(493, 1, 21, 61, 2, 26, NULL, 'Sony Xperia Z5 Premium ( 23MP,32GB,3GB RAM, Dual SIM) - Black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">KEY FEATURES</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size + Type : 5.5&quot; IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Camera : 23MP Rear Camera</li>\r\n	<li>Operating System:&nbsp; &nbsp;Android</li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">32GB storage</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">&nbsp;3 GB RAM</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">Up to 200 GB microSDTM card</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">GoogleTM AndroidTM 5.1 (Lollipop)</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">Hi-res audio delivers a fully immersive and spectacularly detailed audio experience</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">Nano SIM; Works with GSM carriers such as AT&amp;T, T-Mobile etc.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">AT&amp;T, T-Mobile &amp; other GSM carriers ; LTE compatibility</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Type: IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Size:&nbsp;5.5 inches&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution: 2160 x 3840 pixels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multitouch:&nbsp;up to 10 fingers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Protection:&nbsp;Scratch-resistant glass, oleophobic coating</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS: Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chipset:&nbsp;Qualcomm MSM8994 Snapdragon 810</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPU:&nbsp;Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2 GHz Cortex-A57</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GPU:&nbsp;Adreno 430</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Card slot: microSD, up to 200GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal: 32GB, 3GB RAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Primary: 23 MP, f/2.0, 24mm, phase detection autofocus, LED flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features: 1/2.3&quot; sensor size, geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, HDR, panorama</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secondary:&nbsp;5.1 MP, f/2.4, 1080p, HDR</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Network</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Technology:&nbsp;GSM / HSPA / LTE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2G bands:&nbsp;GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3G bands:&nbsp;HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1900 / 2100 - E6853</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4G bands:&nbsp;LTE band 1(2100), 2(1900), 3(1800), 4(1700/2100), 5(850), 7(2600), 8(900), 12(700), 17(700), 20(800), 28(700), 38(2600), 40(2300) - E6853</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speed:&nbsp;HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE Cat6 300/50 Mbps</p>\r\n', '<p>The&nbsp;<strong>Sony Xperia Z5 Premium</strong>&nbsp;is powered by a&nbsp;Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2 GHz Cortex-A57 processor. The phone packs 32GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 200GB via a microSD card. The 23&nbsp;megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 5.1-megapixel front camera let you take amazing photos everywhere you go.&nbsp;It runs on Android 5.1.1 and is powered by a Non-removable Li-Ion 3430 mAh battery to give you the ultimate user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/0d222acd466ce67d5d83cc4b53dac9aa.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>4K Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Imagine the best of Sony TV technologies delivered in a smartphone. A super-vivid and sharp display, right in the palm of your hand. Meet Xperia Z5 Premium. With a 4K Ultra HD display, this 5.5&rdquo; smartphone packs in four times the resolution of Full HD for an unrivaled viewing experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/1e7c8025e573190f442843c4d2112e1f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:269px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Capture Important Moments in 4K</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With Xperia Z5 Premium you can capture the world in incredible high-resolution 4K video. This means your videos have four times the detail of Full HD. Add to that a host of Sony&rsquo;s Handycam technologies, including SteadyShot&trade; for stable videos, and you can count on flawless footage.&nbsp;The Xperia Z5 Premium scales up your photos and movies to incredible 4K quality, while retaining every detail. In fact, it makes everything look better than ever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/c1ab4f4eb43eef9e024ee8efe932bdd0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:221px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Beautiful Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia Z5 Premium isn&rsquo;t shy. It loves to be noticed. Available in chrome, black and gold, it is precision-etched with the Xperia&trade; mark and finished with a stunning mirror effect on the back.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/7296d70cd9c91517c14c60a8a4aafce8.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Connect to your TV</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You&rsquo;ve captured a stunning video, now show off every detail on a 4K TV. Connect instantly over Wi-Fi&reg; using DLNA, or use an MHL 3.0 connector. Enjoy your videos on your TV from your&nbsp;Xperia Z5 Premium&nbsp;at the comfort of your couch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/7ebda2ac00128a369c09ee510da07dde.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Long Lasting Battery</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>For this powerhouse of a 4K smartphone, Sony has gathered all its battery know-how to bring you up to two days&nbsp;battery life. Watch more films, listen to more music, carry on chatting and stay out without a care. When you do need topping up, Xperia Z5 Premium can be used together with our Quick Charger for hours of power in just 10 minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/8c9fcceab1bd103a5d4b000e5396a7e1.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:221px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fingerprint Sensor</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia Z5 Premium&rsquo;s power button has our new, integrated fingerprint sensor. Intuitively placed on the side of the phone, you can pick up and securely unlock your phone in a single movement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCUPNAFAMZ/51e688efe5a4eb39f78a02c230f0bd6b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:320px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1304', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 47039, 44799, 1, 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black-color.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-blaxck-color-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-blaxck-color-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-z5-premium-23mp-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black', '2017-09-21 09:19:28', '2017-09-21 09:19:28'),
(494, 1, 21, 61, 1, 1, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy J5 pro - 3GB RAM, 16GB, Dual SIM--color-blue', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">KEY FEATURES</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Size: 5.20-inch&nbsp;<br />\r\nStorage: 16 GB<br />\r\nRAM; 3GB<br />\r\nCamera; 13 MP<br />\r\nOperating System; Android 7<br />\r\nResolution; 720x1280 pixels</p>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>DISPLAY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen size (inches); &nbsp;&nbsp; 5.20</li>\r\n	<li>Touchscreen; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution ;&nbsp;&nbsp; 720x1280 pixels</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>HARDWARE</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Processor; &nbsp;&nbsp; 1.6GHz octa-core</li>\r\n	<li>Processor make; &nbsp;&nbsp; Exynos 7870</li>\r\n	<li>RAM; &nbsp;&nbsp; 3GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal storage; &nbsp;&nbsp; 32GB</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage ;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage type; &nbsp;&nbsp; microSD</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable storage up to (GB) ;&nbsp;&nbsp; 256</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nCAMERA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rear camera; &nbsp;&nbsp; 13-megapixel</li>\r\n	<li>Flash; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Front camera; &nbsp;&nbsp; 13-megapixel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSOFTWARE</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System ;&nbsp;&nbsp; Android 7.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nCONNECTIVITY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi standards supported; &nbsp;&nbsp; 802.11 b/g/n</li>\r\n	<li>GPS; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes, v 4.10</li>\r\n	<li>NFC; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Infrared; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>USB OTG; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>Headphones; &nbsp;&nbsp; 3.5mm</li>\r\n	<li>FM ;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Number of SIMs; &nbsp;&nbsp; 2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>SIM 1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SIM Type; &nbsp;&nbsp; Micro-SIM</li>\r\n	<li>GSM/CDMA; &nbsp;&nbsp; GSM</li>\r\n	<li>3G; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>4G/ LTE; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSIM 2&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GSM/CDMA; &nbsp;&nbsp; GSM</li>\r\n	<li>3G ;&nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>4G/ LTE; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nSENSORS</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Compass/ Magnetometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>Proximity sensor; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Accelerometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Ambient light sensor; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Gyroscope; &nbsp;&nbsp; Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Barometer; &nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n	<li>Temperature sensor ;&nbsp;&nbsp; No</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>BATTERY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-Removable Li-lon&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity:3000 mAh</li>\r\n	<li>Talk Time Up to &nbsp;21h</li>\r\n	<li>Music Play up to 83 h&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:20px">Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro smartphone</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The phone comes with a 5.20-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 720 pixels by 1280 pixels.The Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro is powered by 1.6GHz octa-core Exynos 7870 processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone packs 16GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 256GB via a microSD card. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro packs a 13-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 13-megapixel front shooter for selfies.The Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro runs Android 7.0 and is powered by a 3000mAh non removable battery. It measures 146.30 x 71.30 x 7.90 (height x width x thickness) . The Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro is a dual SIM (GSM and GSM) smartphone that accepts Micro-SIM. Connectivity options include Wi-Fi, GPS, Bluetooth, NFC, FM, 3G and 4G. Sensors on the phone include Proximity sensor, Accelerometer, Ambient light sensor and Gyroscope.<img alt="Elegant by nature" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/ae-feature-elegant-by-nature-68147893?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:394px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:700px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Share life as you see it</strong><br />\r\nIts rear 13 MP F1.7 camera captures clear photos with enhanced detail in low light while its intuitive interface enables one-handed functionality thanks to its moving shutter button so you can still take the shot while adjusting your pose or framing the scene.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="Share life as you see it" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/ae-feature-share-life-as-you-see-it-68147881?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:281px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Look great in every frame</strong><br />\r\nThe Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro lets you take bright and vivid selfies every time with more accurate detail even in low light thanks to its front LED and selfie flashes. You can also control the shutter by simple hand gesture.<br />\r\n<img alt="Look great in every frame" src="http://images.samsung.com/is/image/samsung/ae-feature-look-great-in-every-frame-68147889?$FB_TYPE_A_JPG$" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:394px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:700px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Full speed ahead</strong><br />\r\nKeep usage running at optimal levels. Thanks to 3 GB of RAM, 32 GB of internal storage and up to 256 GB of optional expandable storage capacity with microSD support, the Samsung Galaxy J5 Pro ensures highly responsive and blazingly fast speeds to accelerate your workflow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1224', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 27559, 25999, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-blue.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-blue-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-blue-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-blue-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-blue-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-j5-pro-3gb-ram-16gb-dual-sim-color-blue', '2017-09-21 09:23:53', '2017-09-21 09:23:53');
