tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">4G</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">SIM Configuration</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Dual SIM (Nano-SIM)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">GPS</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">NFC Chipset</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Infrared</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">No</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="background-color:rgb(242, 243, 245); vertical-align:baseline">PROCESSOR</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Variant</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Snapdragon 810</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Architecture</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Cortex-A53</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">No of Cores</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">8 (Octa Core)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Make</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Qualcomm MSM8994</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Frequency</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">1.5 GHz (Quad Core) + 2.0 GHz (Quad Core)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">GPU</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Adreno 430</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="background-color:rgb(242, 243, 245); vertical-align:baseline">SENSORS</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Proximity</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Accelerometer</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Gyroscope</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Ambient Light</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Fingerprint sensor</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="background-color:rgb(242, 243, 245); vertical-align:baseline">SOUND</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Loudspeaker</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:220px">Headphones</td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:middle; width:658px">Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<p>The Sony Xperia Z5 Dual is powered by a&nbsp;Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2 GHz Cortex-A57 processor. The phone packs 32GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 200GB via a microSD card. The 23&nbsp;megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 5.1-megapixel front camera let you take amazing photos everywhere you go.&nbsp;It runs on Android 5.1.1 and is powered by a 2700mAh&nbsp;battery to give you the ultimate user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0OZW54NAFAMZ/0d222acd466ce67d5d83cc4b53dac9aa.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Capture Important Moments</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia Z5 Dual lets you capture life&rsquo;s greatest photo opportunities, before they pass you by. With its Hybrid Autofocus, our best camera phone yet is a master of speed and accuracy. Combined with 23 megapixels and five times more powerful image zoom, Xperia Z5 Dual is able to capture even the most fleeting moments. In sparkling clarity. On the first try.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0OZW54NAFAMZ/2bbed217055b5b42bdcf568c27abb66e.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:340px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Beautiful Design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia Z5 Dual delivers a design difference you can feel. A metal frame with precision engraving. A smooth, simplified form. And a frosted glass back that&rsquo;s both gentle on the eye and cool to the touch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0OZW54NAFAMZ/66c3d96e4535597c63c62bd722725940.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Water Proof</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With a waterproof and dust-tight design, your device doesn&rsquo;t need a rain coat.&nbsp;Rain happens. So do drops in the sink and knocked-over drinks. Xperia Z5 Dual has Sony&rsquo;s leading waterproof&nbsp;design and an IP68 rating. Because a little water should never ruin your day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0OZW54NAFAMZ/3bf452ae736d2d6150cb4606c70cd2e0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:235px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Long Lasting Battery</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia Z5 Dual brings you up to two days&nbsp;of ground-breaking battery power from a single charge. Listen to more music, talk for days and stay out longer without worrying. When you do need topping up, Xperia Z5 Dual has Quick Charge capabilities to give you a full day of power in just 45 minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://www.telstra.com.au/content/tcom/mobile-phones/mobiles-on-a-plan/sony-xperia-z5/_jcr_content/content/switchmodule/item_2/productfeaturesrow.img.jpg/1445575037638.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:300px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fingerprint Sensor</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Xperia Z5 Dual&rsquo;s power button has our new, integrated fingerprint sensor. The button is intuitively placed on the side of the phone, so you&rsquo;re able to pick up and securely unlock in a single movement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521EL0OZW54NAFAMZ/2d618cc0fd29568e88815ed8fd77dc7c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:281px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1305', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 34124, 32499, 1, 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black-color.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black-color-2.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black-color-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-z5-23mp-32gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-black-color', '2017-09-21 10:22:00', '2017-09-21 10:22:00'),
(496, 1, 21, 61, 2, 26, NULL, 'Sony Xperia Z3+ (2GB, 3GB RAM, Dual SIM, 5.2Inch)White Color', '<div class="title">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.2&quot; display</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels</li>\r\n	<li>Android OS, v5.0 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 32GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>20.7 MP camera</li>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 2930 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type:IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.2 inches</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch&nbsp;up to 10 fingers</li>\r\n	<li>Protection:&nbsp;Scratch-resistant glass, oleophobic coating</li>\r\n	<li>X-Reality Engine</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:&nbsp;Android OS, v5.0 (Lollipop), planned upgrade to v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Qualcomm MSM8994 Snapdragon 810</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2 GHz Cortex-A57</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 128 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 32 GB, 3 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sound</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:&nbsp;20.7 MP</li>\r\n	<li>Features: 1/2.3&quot; sensor size, 1.12 &micro;m pixel size, geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, HDR, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5.1 MP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Network</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Technology: GSM / HSPA / LTE</li>\r\n	<li>2G bands: GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900</li>\r\n	<li>3G bands: HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1900 / 2100</li>\r\n	<li>4G bands: LTE band 1(2100), 2(1900), 3(1800), 4(1700/2100), 5(850), 7(2600), 8(900), 12(700), 17(700), 20(800), 28(700), 40(2300)</li>\r\n	<li>Speed: HSPA 42.2/5.76 Mbps, LTE Cat6 300/50 Mbps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>The Sony Xperia Z3+&nbsp;is powered by a&nbsp;Quad-core 1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; Quad-core 2 GHz Cortex-A57 processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone packs 32GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 128GB via a microSD card. The 20.7&nbsp;megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 5.1-megapixel front camera let you take amazing photos everywhere you go.&nbsp;It runs on Android 5.0 and is powered by a 2930mAh&nbsp;battery to give you the ultimate user experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCV5NAFAMZ/0d222acd466ce67d5d83cc4b53dac9aa.jpg" style="width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Clear photos</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Take pixel-perfect photos in any setting with a 20.7 MP camera. Built using Sony&rsquo;s unique camera technologies, Xperia Z3+ enables you to capture moments sharper than ever before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCV5NAFAMZ/ddad9c439ee97e155201fc9372d06936.jpg" style="height:281px; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Great performance</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy top speeds and lag-free performance.&nbsp;Transfer files and stream your favourite media quicker and smoother with the Qualcomm&reg; Snapdragon&trade; 810 processor with integrated LTE and 64-bit Octa-core CPU.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/SO521ELADCV5NAFAMZ/9fd9b48eeafc775dbe493acdc61ba61f.jpg" style="height:266px; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Long Battery life</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Do more of what you love, for longer with the Xperia Z3+. Its incredible two-day* battery means you get more power from a single charge.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1306', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 30974, 29499, 1, 'sony-xperia-z3-2gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-5-2inch-white-color.jpg', 'sony-xperia-z3-2gb-3gb-ram-dual-sim-5-2inch-white-color-2.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'sony-xperia-z3-2