li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>COMMUNICATION</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN:Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetoothv:4.2, A2DP, LE, apt-X</li>\r\n	<li>GPS with A-GPS, GLONASS, BDS</li>\r\n	<li>NFC</li>\r\n	<li>USB:microUSB v2.0, USB Host</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>FEATURES</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SensorsFingerprint, accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass, barometer, heart rate, SpO2</li>\r\n	<li>MessagingSMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>BrowserHTML5</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Fast battery charging: 60% in 30 min (Quick Charge 2.0)</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless charging (Qi/PMA) - market dependent</li>\r\n	<li>ANT+ support</li>\r\n	<li>S-Voice natural language commands and dictation</li>\r\n	<li>OneDrive (115 GB cloud storage)</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/DivX/XviD/WMV/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/WMA/eAAC+/FLAC player</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n	<li>Document editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>BATTERY&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 3000 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Samsung Galaxy S7</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy S7 unlocks a Galaxy of technology that takes your smartphone experience to a new level. The bigger, more stunning screen completes the slimmer design.Why not have a phone that&rsquo;s water resistant, too?&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Incredible Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy S7 proves that less can actually be more. The big screen on an incredibly slim design keeps you fully engaged in movies, games and more. Plus, with the always on display, you get the time or notifications without waking your screen. And when you&rsquo;re finished, just slip Galaxy S7 back into the pocket of your favourite jeans.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Big on screen, slim on profile" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-2?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=ffffff&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Water and Dust&nbsp;Resistant&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Worry less about daily wear and tear of your phone. Galaxy S7 has an IP68 rating&nbsp;meaning not only protection against dust, it also repels splashes, spills and even dunks. Simply wipe it off and move along.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Water-resistant smartphone" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-3?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=f6f6f6&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Take charge of the charge</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Fast, wireless charging++ lets you power Galaxy S7 from 0&ndash;100% in virtually no time. And with Samsung Galaxy&rsquo;s biggest battery* (3000 mAH) in their thinnest device, Galaxy S7 gives you power to keep going even on those extra long days.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Take charge of the charge" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-5?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=ffffff&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Faster Better camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy S7 has a dual&ndash;pixel camera with faster, more precise autofocus&nbsp;and a new low&ndash;light sensor. All combined, it means fewer blurry photos and crisp detail even in soft light. Also, get brighter selfies in low&ndash;light settings, thanks to the device&rsquo;s selfie flash.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Brighter, better, faster photos" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-4?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=e5e3e4&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1225', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 57750, 55000, 1, 'samsung-galaxy-s7-g930d-5-5-inch-32gb-3gb-ram-12mp-camera-single-sim-color-black.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s7-g930d-5-5-inch-32gb-3gb-ram-12mp-camera-single-sim-color-black-2.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s7-g930d-5-5-inch-32gb-3gb-ram-12mp-camera-single-sim-color-black-3.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s7-g930d-5-5-inch-32gb-3gb-ram-12mp-camera-single-sim-color-black-4.jpg', 'samsung-galaxy-s7-g930d-5-5-inch-32gb-3gb-ram-12mp-camera-single-sim-color-black-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-s7-32gb-3gb-ram-12mp-single-sim-white', '2017-09-21 14:51:37', '2017-09-21 14:51:37'),
