p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Big on screen, slim on profile" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-2?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=ffffff&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Water and Dust&nbsp;Resistant&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Worry less about daily wear and tear of your phone. Galaxy S7 has an IP68 rating&nbsp;meaning not only protection against dust, it also repels splashes, spills and even dunks. Simply wipe it off and move along.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Water-resistant smartphone" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-3?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=f6f6f6&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Take charge of the charge</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Fast, wireless charging++ lets you power Galaxy S7 from 0&ndash;100% in virtually no time. And with Samsung Galaxy&rsquo;s biggest battery* (3000 mAH) in their thinnest device, Galaxy S7 gives you power to keep going even on those extra long days.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Take charge of the charge" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-5?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=ffffff&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Faster Better camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Galaxy S7 has a dual&ndash;pixel camera with faster, more precise autofocus&nbsp;and a new low&ndash;light sensor. All combined, it means fewer blurry photos and crisp detail even in soft light. Also, get brighter selfies in low&ndash;light settings, thanks to the device&rsquo;s selfie flash.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Brighter, better, faster photos" src="https://ss7.vzw.com/is/image/VerizonWireless/hero-pdp-image-2112016-4?$defaultscalejpg$&amp;bgc=e5e3e4&amp;scl=2" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1226', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 57750, 55000, 1, 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-gold.jpg', 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-gold-2.jpg', 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-gold-3.jpg', 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-gold-4.jpg', 'galaxy-s7-dual-sim-32gb-12mp-camera-4gb-ram-color-gold-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'samsung-galaxy-s7-32gb-3gb-ram-12mp-single-sim-color-black', '2017-09-21 14:58:18', '2017-09-21 14:58:18'),
(500, 1, 21, 61, 1, 27, NULL, 'OPPO A37FW (8MP Camera, 16GB, 2GB RAM, Dual SIM)- Gold', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Oppo A37fw&nbsp;runs&nbsp;Android 5.1 Lollipop</li>\r\n	<li>It has a&nbsp;5-inch HD&nbsp;(1280x720pixel) display</li>\r\n	<li>The phone is powered by a&nbsp;quad-core Snapdragon 410 processor&nbsp;and&nbsp;2GB of RAM</li>\r\n	<li>The Oppo A37fw has a&nbsp;8MP&nbsp;primary camera and a&nbsp;5 MP&nbsp;front-facing camera</li>\r\n	<li>It comes with&nbsp;16 GB of built-in storage&nbsp;which can further be expanded using a&nbsp;microSD card</li>\r\n	<li>Connectivity includes&nbsp;dual-SIM 4G, Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n, Bluetooth 4.1, GPS, and a microUSB 2.0 port</li>\r\n	<li>The device has a&nbsp;2,630 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>SoC</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: Qualcomm Snapdragon 410 MSM8916</span><br />\r\n<strong>CPU</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: ARM Cortex-A53, 1200 MHz,&nbsp;</span><strong>Cores</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: 4</span><br />\r\n<strong>GPU</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: Qualcomm Adreno 306, 400 MHz</span><br />\r\n<strong>RAM</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: 2 GB, 533 MHz</span><br />\r\n<strong>Storage</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: 16 GB</span><br />\r\n<strong>Memory cards</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: microSD, microSDHC, microSDXC</span><br />\r\n<strong>Display</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: 5 in, IPS, 720 x 1280 pixels, 24 bit</span><br />\r\n<strong>Battery</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: 2630 mAh, Li-Polymer</span><br />\r\n<strong>OS</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: ColorOS 3.0 (Android 5.1.1 Lollipop)</span><br />\r\n<strong>Camera</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: 3264 x 2448 pixels, 1920 x 1080 pixels, 30 fps</span><br />\r\n<strong>SIM card</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: Micro-SIM, Nano-SIM / microSD</span><br />\r\n<strong>Wi-Fi</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: Wi-Fi Hotspot, Wi-Fi Direct</span><br />\r\n<strong>USB</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: 2.0, Micro USB</span><br />\r\n<strong>Bluetooth</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: 4.0</span><br />\r\n<strong>Positioning</strong><span style="color:rgb(137, 137, 137); font-family:lato,sans-serif; font-size:14px">: GPS, A-GPS&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '<p>Get this Oppo A37 and have a smartphone experience that will keep you up to date with the latest that a phone can offer. This is designed to fulfill all your needs which you want to have from your smartphone, it is easy to operate and looks extremely stylish. With cool and latest application and fast performance, this is an ultimate phone to have.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for oppo logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/OP896EL1LPFKSNAFAMZ/69a038c7e86a210f793dc992b8d06583.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:202px; margin:39px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:398px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><br />\r\n<strong>Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Oppo A37 comes to you with an amazing screen size of 12.7 cm (5) which provides you an extreme viewing experience. The screen resolution of this phone is 720x1080 IPS with multi touch facility. It features a gorilla glass 3 with pixel density of 294 ppi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/OP896EL1LPFKSNAFAMZ/f85a702631480bda8a1525cfdd84f600.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:580px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:320px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Performance&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This Oppo phone has an Android v5.1 Lollipop and has some useful pre-installed apps as well. The OS is really smooth and works well. It supports almost all the apps including games, video editors, social media, video players etc. Oppo A37 has a 1.2 GHz Cortex-A53 Qualcomm processor and really easy to operate and process all the applications extremely well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img alt="Image result for android 5.1" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/OP896EL1LPFKSNAFAMZ/55438ae0894b935b1200fac58e40c2fd.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:333px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:589px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This Oppo mobile gives you an amazing camera experience, It has a rear camera of a fabulous 8 MP which is capable of taking extremely well pictures. The USP of camera is that it has it has autofocus with flash. It also has a good front camera of 5 MP which allows you to take selfies the way you like. It allows you to take quick &amp; pretty pictures as well as videos and save it to your phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for oppo a37" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/OP896EL1LPFKSNAFAMZ/231405b381b71e5012fdbd4dc27acfe0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:624px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1227', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 15899, 14999, 1, 'oppo-a37fw-8mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-dual-sim-gold.jpg', 'oppo-a37fw-8mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-dual-sim-gold-2.jpg', 'oppo-a37fw-8mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-dual-sim-gold-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'oppo-a37fw-8mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-dual-sim-gold', '2017-09-21 17:32:38', '2017-09-21 17:32:38');
