;which can further be expanded using a&nbsp;microSD card</li>\r\n	<li>Connectivity includes&nbsp;dual-SIM 4G, Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n, Bluetooth 4.1, GPS, and a microUSB 2.0 port</li>\r\n	<li>The device has a&nbsp;2,630 mAh battery</li>\r\n	<li>2.5D Arc Edge Screen</li>\r\n	<li>Rear Sensor:8-megapixel,Front Senso: 5-megapixel; Aperture -Rear: f/2.2 Front: f/2.4</li>\r\n	<li>Size:5.0 inches;Resolution-HD (1280 by 720 pixels)</li>\r\n	<li>RAM-2GB Storage:16GB (Expandable up to 128GB)</li>\r\n	<li>Operating System - ColorOS 3.0, based on Android 5.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Get this Oppo A37 and have a smartphone experience that will keep you up to date with the latest that a phone can offer. This is designed to fulfill all your needs which you want to have from your smartphone, it is easy to operate and looks extremely stylish. With cool and latest application and fast performance, this is an ultimate phone to have.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for oppo logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/OP896EL0D4YJKNAFAMZ/69a038c7e86a210f793dc992b8d06583.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:202px; margin:39px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:398px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><br />\r\n<strong>Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Oppo A37 comes to you with an amazing screen size of 12.7 cm (5) which provides you an extreme viewing experience. The screen resolution of this phone is 720x1080 IPS with multi touch facility. It features a gorilla glass 3 with pixel density of 294 ppi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/OP896EL0D4YJKNAFAMZ/f85a702631480bda8a1525cfdd84f600.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:580px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:320px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Performance&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This Oppo phone has an Android v5.1 Lollipop and has some useful pre-installed apps as well. The OS is really smooth and works well. It supports almost all the apps including games, video editors, social media, video players etc. Oppo A37 has a 1.2 GHz Cortex-A53 Qualcomm processor and really easy to operate and process all the applications extremely well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img alt="Image result for android 5.1" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/OP896EL0D4YJKNAFAMZ/55438ae0894b935b1200fac58e40c2fd.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:333px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:589px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This Oppo mobile gives you an amazing camera experience, It has a rear camera of a fabulous 8 MP which is capable of taking extremely well pictures. The USP of camera is that it has it has autofocus with flash. It also has a good front camera of 5 MP which allows you to take selfies the way you like. It allows you to take quick &amp; pretty pictures as well as videos and save it to your phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for oppo a37" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/OP896EL0D4YJKNAFAMZ/231405b381b71e5012fdbd4dc27acfe0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:624px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1229', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 16950, 15990, 1, 'oppo-a37-16gb-8mp-camera-dual-sim-gold.jpg', 'oppo-a37-16gb-8mp-camera-dual-sim-gold-2.jpg', 'oppo-a37-16gb-8mp-camera-dual-sim-gold-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'oppo-a37-16gb-8mp-camera-dual-sim-gold', '2017-09-21 18:08:56', '2017-09-21 18:08:56'),
