(508, 1, 21, 61, 2, 28, NULL, 'INFINIX Zero 3 X552  (20.7MP Camera, 16GB, 3GB RAM, 5.5Inch )', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS :&nbsp; &nbsp; Android 5.1 Lollipop</p>\r\n\r\n<div>Screen Size :&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5.5 inches</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Display Resolution :&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1080 x 1920 pixels</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Processor :&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2.2GHz Octa core</div>\r\n\r\n<div>RAM :&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3GB</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Storage Space :&nbsp; &nbsp; 16GB</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Expansion Slot&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp;128GB</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Camera :&nbsp; &nbsp; 20.7 megapixels, LED Flash, Autofocus</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Selfie Camera&nbsp; :&nbsp; &nbsp; 5 megapixels</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Battery&nbsp; &nbsp;; 3030mAh</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Connectivity :&nbsp; &nbsp; 4G LTE</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '<h2>Product Specifications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 5.5-inch IPS Display, 1080 x 1920 pixels (400ppi)</li>\r\n	<li>Display Protection: Corning Gorilla Glass 3</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Platform: Android 5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Processor: 2.2GHz octa-core Processor (Mediatek Helio X10)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rear Camera: 20.7 MP Camera, dual LED Flash, 4k HD Video</li>\r\n	<li>Rear Camera Features: Autofocus, realtime phase detection, Smart Gesture, Geo-tagging, Panorama, Slo Mo</li>\r\n	<li>Front Camera: 5MP Camera, BSI</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="list-style-type:none">\r\n	<li>Built-in Storage: 16GB</li>\r\n	<li>Memory Card Support</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Network Support</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2G GSM: 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900MHz</li>\r\n	<li>3G WCDMA: 850 / 2100MHz</li>\r\n	<li>4G LTE</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Internet &amp; Connectivity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN: Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi Hotspot:&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: Yes, Bluetooth 4.0</li>\r\n	<li>USB Port: Yes, microUSB 2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="list-style-type:none">\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Battery: 3030 mAh Battery</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h4>DESCRIPTION</h4>\r\n\r\n<div id="description-full" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<div class="container columns" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 954px; float: left;">\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns medium-12" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 954px; float: left;">\r\n<p>If an unconventional smartphone is something that you are looking for, then the Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual SIM Smartphone is</p>\r\n\r\n<p>the perfect device for you. The advanced mobile is ideal for those who love photography as it comes embedded with a</p>\r\n\r\n<p>powerful 20.7MP rear camera with Sony Exmor IMX230 CMOS sensor, and a 5MP front facing camera with BSI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>photosensitive components. These cameras enable you to capture ultra high resolution images that will please one</p>\r\n\r\n<p>and all. MediaTek&rsquo;s dynamic Helio X10 Chipset, which incorporates a 2.2GHz Quad Core processor, 3GB RAM, and</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mali 450 MP4 GPU, ensures all the phone features and applications operate smoothly without a glitch. The device&rsquo;s</p>\r\n\r\n<p>802.11 a/b/g/n specification WiFi and 4G LTE support enable you to access the Internet from virtually any location.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A 16GB built in storage easily holds volumes of digital data. This advanced mobile phone is available in a propriety</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Luxurious Gold color.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns medium-6" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: left;">\r\n<h4><strong>PHYSICAL FEATURES</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<div class="text-center" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim Physical Features" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/dimensions-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns medium-6" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<div class="row kf-en" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 15px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns medium-6 small-12" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 223.5px; float: left;">\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OCTA-Core 2.0 GHz</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3GB RAM</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>16GB</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>20.7MP Main Camera ,5MP Front Camera</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns medium-6 small-12" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 223.5px; float: right;">\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3030mAh</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.5 inch</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Android 5.1 Lollipop</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual SIM</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-1-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left mart-30" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 30px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>REDEFINES CLARITY</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim specs boast about its big 5.5inch IPS capacitive touch display, which produces images that have a maximum resolution of 1920 x 1080 pixels. The screen&rsquo;s 16M color output ensures the displayed images are lifelike.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: left;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-2-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right mart-30" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 30px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>STATE OF THE ART DUAL CAMERAS</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim features a 20.7MP rear camera that incorporates an advanced Sony Exmor IMX230 CMOS sensor. This rear Infinix Zero3 camera helps you capture fantastic photos and incredible videos. The Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim even features a 5MP front facing camera with BSI photosensitive components for capturing picture perfect selfies.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-7-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left mart-30" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 30px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>COLORS IN ALL ITS GLORY</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The Infinix Zero3&#39;s 20.7MP camera features dual LED flash that enables you to snap bright images in low lit environments. The Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim&nbsp;combines a 6P Largan Lens, which retains vivid details even when you edit or enlarge the image. Your picture not only lights up brightly, but also achieves natural supplemental lighting for enhanced details.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: left;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-8-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right mart-30" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 30px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>HEAR IT CLEAR</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim is equipped with Hi Fi AAC 1206 audio technology. This enables you to have noise free calls, even when you converse long distance with people. It delivers crisp and clear sound from the other end and sends forth your message without any disturbances.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-9-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left mart-30" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 30px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>XUI</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The smart and efficient XUI is incorporated into the Zero3, enabling you to manage and chart your course with simplicity. This creation, by the Infinix R and D department, provides updates every two weeks, which is more frequently than other brands. It offers 21 percent of improved performance with an ultra smooth operation and zero lag. Additionally, it enhances the battery life up to 20 percent and minimizes system wake up, thus decreasing background app power consumption. It also has a standby mode, in which the XUI auto initiates standby network management, increasing efficiency by 28 percent. For the fun part, XUI offers a ton of chic wallpapers and themes to enhance the look of your device&rsquo;s interface. Moreover, it also provides security enhancements, quick transfer technology, power saving modes, and the option of staying connected everywhere with one account. The success of the XUI has it consolidated with the Infinix X600, X552, and newer models too.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: left;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-3.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right mart-30" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 30px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>ADVANCED HARDWARE AND THE LOLLIPOP OS</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim reviews have lauded its MediaTek Helio X10 chipset, which features 2.2GHz Quad Core processor, 3GB RAM, and Mali 450 MP4 GPU. The dynamic chipset enables the phone to briskly execute all the tasks that are assigned to it. This dual SIM mobile&rsquo;s preloaded Android Lollipop operating system v5.1 makes navigating the mobile&rsquo;s interface appear seamless.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-4-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left mart-60" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 60px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>SLOTS FOR TWO SIM CARDS</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual SIM Smartphone lets you insert two SIM cards into its provided slots. The feature helps you keep your personal and professional numbers separate, letting you enjoy life to the fullest.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: left;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-5-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right mart-50" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 50px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>VERSATILE CONNECTIVITY</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>This dual SIM smartphone&rsquo;s Bluetooth 4.1 can help you transfer files immediately to and from your computers and other compatible devices. The mobile&#39;s built in WiFi adapter instantly connects this device to the Internet. The device even supports 4G LTE connectivity.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;"><img alt="Infinix Zero3 X552 Dual Sim" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Infinix/Infinix-Zero3-X552-Dual-Sim/feature-6-luxurious-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit