(521, 1, 21, 61, 1, 29, NULL, 'Huawei Y5 II, 8GB, 1GB RAM, 8MP Camera, Dual SIM, Color- Black', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Display Size: 5.0 Inches Screen</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Display Type: IPS LCD Capacitive Touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory: 8GB, 1GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Primary Camera: 8 MP, f/2.0, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Battery Capacity:&nbsp; Li-Po 2200 mAh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type:IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size:5.0 inches (~66.6% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution:720 x 1280 pixels (~294 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Emotion UI 3.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v5.1 (Lollipop)l</li>\r\n	<li>Mediatek MT6582 - 3G model</li>\r\n	<li>Mali-400MP2 - 3G model</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory:8GB</li>\r\n	<li>RAM:1GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:8 MP, f/2.0, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:2 MP, LED flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Communications&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN:Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth:v4.0, A2DP, LE</li>\r\n	<li>GPS &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>FM radio</li>\r\n	<li>USB:microUSB v2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Features &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors:Accelerometer, proximity, compass</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging:SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Email, IM</li>\r\n	<li>Browser:HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/eAAC+ player</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Removable Li-Po 2200 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Huawei Y5II</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Upgrade your mobile experience with the super awesome&nbsp;Huawei Y5II! This smartphone is powered by Android Lollipop 5.1 and skinned with Huawei&rsquo;s EMUI 3.1. What&#39;s more, Huawei Y5 II adapts to your life as it has a flexible, modern design that allows relax. Double flash allows several shots in low light conditions and create incredible photos.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for huawei logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL03ZF9SNAFAMZ/67fc36325ec4ca932b90cfa481d41283.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:276px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:293px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Large Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Huawei Y5II sports a beautiful 5-inch HD LCD display, providing crisp, vibrant experience that is truly a feast for the eyes. But it&rsquo;s more than just a piece of eye-candy. The quad 1.3GHz CPU backs up the graphic performance with enough processing power to keep even the most multitasking-oriented user flying along, immersed in a visual wonderland.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Ascend Y5 II" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL03ZF9SNAFAMZ/acb254e4ae8ff52f56b1c8449ec56f74.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:574px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Enjoy the Moments</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s a pity to lose vivid details in photos because of lighting. The dual flashlight of Huawei Y5II performs exceptionally well in low-light conditions. The 8 megapixel camera and the F2.0 aperture creates photos of that look professional. The auto-enhancement feature designed for portraits, along with the 2 mega-pixel front-facing camera delivers the perfect selifes experience, making your portraits stand out and shine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Ascend Y5 II camera" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL03ZF9SNAFAMZ/b08d19e3c167165bb0afdeb12e105c2c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:349px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:525px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Endless App</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tired of endless menus when you are eager to post an exciting moment? The Easy Key function gives you a shorter path to your favorite content. With a simple press, double-press, or press-and-hold you can launch the application or feature you&rsquo;ve assigned to each gesture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Powerful Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Based on Android 5.1, Huawei Y5II runs EMUI3.1 mobile operating system with the look, feel and usability undergoing a complete refresh. Data and applications are neatly organized and easy to find right by using the highly effective Timeline function. The built in phone manager ensures a safer and more fluid user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Ascend Y5 II camera" src="https://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTXkGmkAlO2t1zlwzDN9MxID27VBthH8f6IRW6Md7_cEka8aQw-7Q" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:232px; margin:81px auto 30px; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:820px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1233', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 11659, 10999, 1, 'huawei-y5-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-8mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black.jpg', 'huawei-y5-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-8mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black-2.jpg', 'huawei-y5-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-8mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black-3.jpg', 'huawei-y5-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-8mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'huawei-y5-ii-8gb-1gb-