(522, 1, 21, 61, 2, 28, NULL, 'INFINIX Note 3 Pro ( 13MP Camera, Dual SIM,16GB, 3GB RAM) Grey', '<div class="detail-features" style="box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 230px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">\r\n<div class="list -features -compact -no-float" style="box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; border-top: 1px solid rgb(233, 233, 233); padding: 10px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px;">\r\n<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong>Key Features</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Display Size: &nbsp;6.0 Inch Screen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display Type: Full HD Touchscreen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Primary Camera: 13.0MP AutoFocus, 5.0MP Front Flash &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal Memory:16GB, 3GB RAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS: Android 6.0 Marshmallow</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Number Of SIM : Dual SIM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rear Camera Resolution : 8 MP &amp; Above</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mobile Phone Type : Smartphone</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cellular Network Technology : 4G LTE</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size: 6.0 inches</li>\r\n	<li>Display Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels (~367 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Display Type: IPS capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Back Camera: 13 Megapixel, up to 4160 x 3120-pixel pictures, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Video: Yes, 1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Front Camera: 5 Megapixel, Front Soft Flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Chipset: MediaTek MT6753, 64-bit</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Octa-core 1.3 GHz</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali T720 MP3</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>System Memory: 3 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory: 16 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Card Slot: microSD, up to 128 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Software</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System: Android OS v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>User Interface: XUI 2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sound</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration, MP3 ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm Jack: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2G Network: GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900</li>\r\n	<li>3G Network: HSDPA 850 / 900 / 2100</li>\r\n	<li>4G Network: LTE</li>\r\n	<li>SIM: Dual Micro-SIM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GPRS: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>WLAN: Wi-Fi 802.11</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: Yes, v4.0</li>\r\n	<li>USB: Yes, MicroUSB v2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Features</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors: Fingerprint, G-sensor, Light, Proximity, Compass</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging: SMS, MMS, Email</li>\r\n	<li>Radio: No</li>\r\n	<li>GPS: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n	<li>Photo viewer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Power</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Battery Capacity: 4500mAh Lithium-Ion</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Infinix is back again. Introducing the&nbsp;Infinix X601&nbsp;Note 3 Pro. The new x601 comes with a bigger battery, fingerprint sensor, android M factory shipped and a new sleek premium metal body that will for sure make the gadget lovers happy!&nbsp;This phone with a 6.0&quot; Full HD&nbsp;IPS screen display dazzles with it&#39;s high resolution 367ppi display. All your photos, video &amp; media is sharper, brighter&nbsp;than ever from any angle.&nbsp;It also has an upgraded 13MP fast 0.25ms auto-focus&nbsp;camera that enables superior picture quality and faster focus with LED Flashlight. The 5MP front snapper comes with flash as well for the photo enthusiast.&nbsp;Enjoy life and capture those special moments and take spontaneous selfie whenever, wherever.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/IN213EL09JL4WNAFAMZ/d80bdf08aae6b577889c0092bb0f8464.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertica