(529, 1, 21, 61, 2, 29, NULL, 'Huawei Honor 8 Lite 4GB RAM, 32GB ROM, Color - Sensor-Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(170, 170, 170); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">KEY FEATURES</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>System: EMUI 5.0 ( Android 7.0 )&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Allows you to remain connected and productive</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Hisilicon Kirin 655 Octa Core 2.1GHz ( 4 x 2.1GHz + 4 x 1.7GHz + i5 Co-processor )&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Equipped with better performance, delivering plenty of power for your use</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali-T830 MP2&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Better and faster in playing games and watching videos than the previous generation</li>\r\n	<li>Display: 5.2 inch FHD IPS Screen with 423 PPI&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>16.7M colors, supports multi-touch,&nbsp;offers good experience for watching videos and browsing the Web</li>\r\n	<li>4GB RAM 32GB ROM:&nbsp;provides enough room for your use, can suit all your needs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Huawei Honor 8 Lite</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">The Honor 8 Lite is a cost-effective phone that comes with a&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">5.2 inch FHD IPS display</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;and is equipped with&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">EMUI 5.0 ( based on Android 7.0 )</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">. It comes with most of the features we&#39;ve come to expect from a smartphone, including&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">fingerprint sensor, 4GB RAM, OTG function and decent cameras.</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;You are certainly treated to an excellent user experience.</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Main Features:</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">System: EMUI 5.0 ( Android 7.0 )</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Allows you to remain connected and productive</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">CPU: Hisilicon Kirin 655 Octa Core 2.1GHz ( 4 x 2.1GHz + 4 x 1.7GHz + i5 Co-processor )</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Equipped with better performance, delivering plenty of power for your use</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">GPU: Mali-T830 MP2</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Better and faster in playing games and watching videos than the previous generation</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Display: 5.2 inch FHD IPS Screen with 423 PPI&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">16.7M colors, supports multi-touch,</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;offers good experience for watching videos and browsing the Web</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">4GB RAM 32GB ROM:</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;provides enough room for your use, can suit all your needs</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Dual Cameras:</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">12.0MP rear-facing camera with PDAF and flashlight, supports 1080P video recording,</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;makes images clear and vivid</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">8.0MP front camera,</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;enables you to capture high quality pictures</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">128GB TF Card Expansion:</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;accepts compatible card up to 128GB ( not included ) for easy expansion</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Dual SIM Dual Standby:</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Dual nano SIM cards, SIM 1 is just for nano SIM card, SIM 2 is for nano SIM card / TF card</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">SIM 1 and SIM 2 can be switched as the master card discretionarily</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Navigation:</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;GPS, Glonass, Beidou</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Several Sensors:</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Ambient Light Sensor, Compass, Gravity Sensor, Proximity Sensor, Fingerprint Sensor</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Network:</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">2G: GSM 850/900/1800/1900MHz</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">3G: WCDMA 850/900/2100MHz, TD-SCDMA 1900/2100MHz</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">4G: FDD-LTE 850/1800/2100MHz ( Band 1/3/5 ), TDD-LTE 1900/2300/2500MHz ( Band 39/40/41 )</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Brand:</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;HUAWEI&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Battery Capacity(mAh):</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;3000mAh, Li-ion polymer battery&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Battery Type:</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;Not Detachable&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Camera:</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;12.0MP,8.0MP&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:open sans,sans-serif; font-size:14px">Camera type:</span><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;Front &amp; Back Camera&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span