(533, 1, 21, 61, 2, 28, NULL, 'Infinix Hot 4 Pro X556  (16GB, 2GB RAM, 4G) Champagne Gold', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.5 inch HD display</li>\r\n	<li>4G connectivity</li>\r\n	<li>Dual high-quality stereo speakers</li>\r\n	<li>4000mAh battery</li>\r\n	<li>Dual SIM functionality</li>\r\n	<li>Customized XOS based on&nbsp;Android 6.0 Marshmallow</li>\r\n	<li>1.3GHz Quad-core processor</li>\r\n	<li>2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>13MP rear AF Main camera</li>\r\n	<li>5MP fixed focus front camera</li>\r\n	<li>Quick charge feature</li>\r\n	<li>Smart Voice Technology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h3><strong>Infinix Hot 4 Pro Full Phone Specifications.</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<table style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family:source sans pro,sans-serif; font-size:19px; height:953px; width:640px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>NETWORK</strong></td>\r\n			<td>GSM:&nbsp; GSM 900 / 1800<br />\r\n			3G:&nbsp; HSDPA 850 / 900 / 2100<br />\r\n			4G:&nbsp; &nbsp; FDD-LTE 1(2100) / 3(1800) / 5(850) / 7(2600) / 8(900) / 20(800) / 38(2600) / 40(2300)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>LAUNCH (Availability)</strong></td>\r\n			<td>August 2016</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Dimensions</strong></td>\r\n			<td>152.6 x 76.2 x 8.8 mm</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>SIM Type</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Dual Micro SIM</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>DISPLAY</strong></td>\r\n			<td>IPS display</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Size</strong></td>\r\n			<td>5.5 inches</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Resolution</strong></td>\r\n			<td>720 x 1280 pixels</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Protection</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&ndash;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>0S</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Android 6 Marshmallow</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>CPU(Processor Type)</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Quad-Core 1.3 GHz&nbsp; Mediatek MT6580</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>GPU(Processor Name)</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;Mali-T720 MP2</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>MEMORY</strong></td>\r\n			<td>RAM: 2 GB<br />\r\n			Internal Storage: 16 GB<br />\r\n			External Storage:&nbsp; MicroSD card up to 128 GB (uses 2nd SIM slot)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>CAMERA</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Primary :&nbsp; 13 megapixel autofocus camera with LED flash<br />\r\n			Secondary:&nbsp; 5 megapixel</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Wi-Fi</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Bluetooth</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;v4.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>GPS&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>USB&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;&nbsp; microUSB v2.0; OTG</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>BATTERY</strong></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp; 4000 mAh</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Available colors</strong></td>\r\n			<td>Mysterious Blue. Glossy Silver. Champagne Gold. Anthracite Grey</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="content-area" id="primary" style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 786.406px; float: left; margin-right: 46.25px; margin-bottom: 2.61792em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium;">\r\n<div class="post-6881 page type-page status-publish hentry category-infinix-phones-price-in-kenya category-latest-devices-in-kenya" id="post-6881" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 4.2358em;">\r\n<div class="entry-content" style="box-sizing: border-box;">\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This device comes with 5.5-inch IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen with HD&nbsp;resolution of&nbsp;1280 x 720 pixels. The display&nbsp;comes with 12 ultra bright backlight LEDs providing clear viewing experience during the day and at night.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating System</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This handset runs on customized XOS based on&nbsp;Android 6.0 Marshmallow. The customized XOS operating system is packed with innovative features such as Freezer, custom themes and Smart Cleanup.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CPU</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Smartphone is powered by MediaTek MT6737 quad-core processor clocked at 1.3GHz.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This device comes&nbsp;with 2GB RAM. The internal storage is 16GB expandable via microSD card up to 128GB.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This device comes with&nbsp;13 MP rear camera with autofocus and five internal lens elements. Located at the front is 5MP shooter with soft light flash.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Smart Voice Technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hot 4 Pro has high quality dual stereo speakers providing clear sound quality and great multimedia experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This device also comes with an internal microphone and noise reduction technology which identifies and reduces disturbing background sounds in order to adjust the output volume, creating an enhanced calling experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity Features</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the connectivity features include 2G/3G/4G internet connectivity, MICRO-USB, OTG, Bluetooth and Wi-Fi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This handset comes with 4,000mAh battery with standby time of 660 hours and quick charge feature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dimensions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hot 4 Pro weighs 175 grams and measures 152.6 x 76.2 x 8.8 mm in size.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1334', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 15224, 14499, 1, 'infinix-hot-4-pro-x556-16gb-2gb-ram-4g-champagne-gold.jpg', 'infinix-hot-4-pro-x556-16gb-2gb-ram-4g-champagne-gold-2.jpg', '', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'infinix-hot-4-pro-x556-16gb-2gb-ram-4g-c