(537, 1, 21, 61, 2, 30, NULL, 'TECNO Spark Model K7(13MP Camera, 16GB,1GB RAM) Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family: proxima-nova-n9, proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: 12.6px;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<p class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family: proxima-nova-n9, proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: 12.6px;">&nbsp;Screen: 5.5&quot; display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory: 1GB RAM, 16GB ROM (External Memory, up to 32GB)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor: Quad-Core CORTEX 1.3GHz</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating System: Android 7.0 Nougat With HiOS 2.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera: 13MP Rear Camera, 5MP Front Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery: 3000mAh Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<div class="osh-tabs -center" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;">\r\n<div class="tab-content -active" id="productDescriptionTab" style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 710px; margin: auto;">\r\n<div class="product-description" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 40px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); line-height: 18px;">\r\n<div class="osh-tabs -center" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;">\r\n<div class="tab-content -active" id="productDescriptionTab" style="box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 710px; margin: auto;">\r\n<div class="product-description" style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 40px 0px; text-align: left; color: rgb(96, 96, 96); line-height: 18px;">\r\n<p><strong>DISPLAY</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size: 5.5 inches</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Resolution: 1280 x 720 pixels IPS display</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>HARDWARE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CPU: 32-bit Quad-Core 1.3 GHz</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: MediaTek MT6580</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali&ndash;400</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 2 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory: 16 GB</li>\r\n	<li>External MicroSD: Yes Expandable up to 128 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Sensors: G-Sensors, Proximity Sensors, Fingerprint, Gyroscope, Compass</li