e/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001999538484_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552002000779827_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552002002755297_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552002004902094_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">\r\n<p>The TECNO Spark K7 is a new line of photo-focused smartphones from TECNO, targeted largely at millennial youths, especially students who mostly have to live on a budget. Best known for its bright screen and advanced camera features, the Spark has been termed the brightest smartphones yet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spark K7 has a HD screen that measures 5.5 inches diagonally, display quality is set at 720 by 1280 pixels with 267 PPI.&nbsp;The available screen resolution is not bad for an entry-level device with approachable price tag, the display won&rsquo;t be distorted in any way and will serve well for video streaming and gaming purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Android 7.0 Nougat is pre-installed on the Spark K7 with HiOS 2.0 skin on top, the HiOS interface is said to deliver fluid multi-tasking experience like never seen before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The TECNO Spark K7 stays true to the revolutionary pixel sensor and denoising camera technologies of latest TECNO smartphone cameras. Its 13MP rear and 5MP front camera provides high-sensitivity camera capabilities which help users get better imaging results anytime, anywhere and under any kind of lightening condition.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere is also a single LED flash available for the front and back cameras to help boost image quality in low light conditions, giving you a great imaging experience. In some cases, the front LED flash can also be used as notification light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tecno Spark K7 carries a sufficient 3000 mAh battery in the powerhouse.</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1335', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 10033, 9555, 1, 'tecno-spark-model-k7-13mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-gold.jpg', 'tecno-spark-model-k7-13mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-gold-2.jpg', 'tecno-spark-model-k7-13mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-gold-3.jpg', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'tecno-spark-model-k7-13mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-gold', '2017-09-24 18:54:30', '2017-09-24 18:54:30'),
(538, 1, 21, 61, 2, 30, NULL, 'TECNO Camon CX Air(16GB, 13MP, 2GB RAM,Dual SIM, 5.5")Gold', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong><br />\r\n16M High definition Selfie/slim/2.5D</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage (ROM): 16GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display: 5.5-inch</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Front Camera: 16.0MP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rear Camera: 16.0MP</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery: 3200 mAh</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS: HiOS v2.0.0, based on Android&trade; 7.0<br />\r\nMemory (RAM): 2GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage (ROM): 16GB</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>SPECIFICATIONS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>SIM Type: Dual Micro SIM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3G Network : Yes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4G Network : Band 3/7/20/28A/40</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS: Android 7 Nougat + HiOS 2.0 Custom UI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Display: 5.5-inch HD IPS Display, 1920 x 1080 pixels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Protection : &nbsp;2.5D water drop screen</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor Type: 1.25Ghz Quad-Core processor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>RAM: 2GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Internal Storage: 16GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>External Storage: Yes , up to 128GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Back Camera : 13 megapixels, autofocus with Dual LED Flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Front Camera : 13 megapixels with LED Flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Security : Fingerprint scanner</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery : 3200mAh</p>\r\n', '<p><img alt="Image result for camon cx" src="https://static.jumia.com.ng/cms/external/pet/TE339EL0EZ6DMNAFAMZ/d95eeb4d6f6c5fae52c5b42cebeda2e3.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:block; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Camon CX is designed to take fabulous pictures. Equipped with 16MP front camera and 16MP back camera, devoted to capturing every beautiful second in your life. The Front Camera offers the freedom to choose among a variety of filters for beautification, and is effective in creating polished images and reliving all sweet memories.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Unique 4 in 1 Technology</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The &lsquo;4 in 1&rsquo; technology also pairs effective denoising technology, obtaining a signal-to-noise (SNR) 1.7 times better, with the newest Smart Denoise technology to produce amazingly clear images even in low light. The dual-front flash feature goes further, and allows Camon CX users to take amazing quality selfies in dark environments where previous artificial light would blur and distort images.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Brighter Selfies</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Each pixel sensor detects light, captures individual images and converts the information into signals before forming the final image, resulting in selfies that are 30 per cent brighter, capturing special moments perfectly.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Customized Ring Flash</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The smartphone also includes features such as a customised ring flash, light speed charge and a 5.5 inch FHD (Full High Definition) screen, all allowing for ease of use on the go as well as the best quality images.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="image" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/3ryAtQN5GuICfvuLHc-xoEwDnyLVl9250ZQ-fn-SdZDq3Q8Yf7zkXdTjBbCgUtJKtnR_ygeDKdDXAZyGjM6Mzg9PeuFHdQ0nsFSoM0rYDPaixxICkk9fSPmrve0BB75t0LcjSe-6" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:429px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:763px" /><img alt="image" src="https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/eazjrlt71m-KlFzEg91FDIn_icyP9kek1gFYm-w1-gcAZCqsHT5XnmCP6R-qb7jRgAKUCZBZFrbU2NxDcd6QkMAZZpZdWO0xTBBwPSuHBtm1G8WKTPaTCTB4MsqZSUj_hrmunr_P" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:451px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:800px" /><img alt="image" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/fIQVo7CD75yWG3o0wq0g_fIPczBUdbGNIG-81Yc8bN2nN48YKOHHXYD3P_RJDDqfC1-_ZdHqgyp3o-ND9emZxvnzYuhZuL_u41qMl1jOzQ5nY9sck