(543, 1, 21, 61, 2, 29, NULL, 'Huawei Y6 II 16GB, 2GB RAM, 13MP, Dual SIM-White', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display:&nbsp;5.5inch HD</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 13MP Back + 8MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android 6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 16GB, 2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 3000mAh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display :&nbsp;5.5inch HD</li>\r\n	<li>Emotion UI :&nbsp;EMUI 4.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Front: 8M; Back: 13M</li>\r\n	<li>Camera Flash Yes, LED flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cpu Krin620/MSM8952 (only for CAM-L32)</li>\r\n	<li>OS Android 6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>GPU Mali T450</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>RAM 2GB+ ROM 16GB</li>\r\n	<li>External Up to 128 GB, MicroSD</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WIFI 2.4Ghz 802.11 b/g/n+BT4.1/BT4.0 LE</li>\r\n	<li>USB Yes, microUSB v2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sensors</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>proximity/accelerate/compass/Ambient light sensor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Media Format</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Audio :&nbsp;MP3/AMR-NB/AAC</li>\r\n	<li>Video :&nbsp;H.263/H.264/MPEG-4</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>3000mAh (not removable)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Huawei Y6II&rsquo;s new larger dynamic 1280x720 resolution display is crystal clear and rivals top digital screens, immersing you in the vivid colors and vibrancy of life in a whole new way. The durable GFF transparent lamination protects the display from scratches to ensure long-lasting brightness.&nbsp;<strong>Order for your&nbsp;Huawei Y6II Smartphone from Jumia online and have it delivered straight to your doorstep.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL0QH3VSNAFAMZ/550caece97ac53cd0dd8c157d7a7520b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Rear Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Take the best pictures of your life with the Huawei Y6II&rsquo;s super-powered 13-megapixel camera. The wide-angle, 28mm lens with a 2.0 aperture is made of scratch resistant, state-of-the-art glass. And the customized dynamic range is perfect in any light and any setting, putting a professional-grade camera in the palm of your hand. Never miss a moment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL0QH3VSNAFAMZ/df374d82a4b87c1834be82085a32a400.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Front Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Selfies have never looked so good. The Y6II comes with an enormous 8-megapixel camera&mdash;Huawei&rsquo;s largest front-facing camera to date. The 2.0 aperture offers a huge, 77-degree range letting you take panorama selfies for the first time. Bigger background, bigger story, bigger you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL0QH3VSNAFAMZ/efaad677bf05891d3e6931b867ece380.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Auto Face Enhancement and Make-up Mode</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Always put your best face forward with Huawei&rsquo;s 10-level face enhancement option on the Y6II. The 10-millisecond face recognition creates beautification in real time, and can enhance personal photos as well as group shots. The Y6II also comes equipped with 8 beautification presets and customizable options, offering a range of natural effects and highlights including lip gloss and eye shadow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL0QH3VSNAFAMZ/840b844a29ae00fd9708a1795103c59b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Elegant Design Style</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You can make a big statement with a simple gesture when using the Huawei Y6II. Metallic cross-stripes create 5,176 facets that not only catch and reflect the light, but also catch people&rsquo;s attention. Other textures include: high-gloss black, or more fun options in yellow, pink and blue. The molded mirror polish and 60c-micro texture complete the device&rsquo;s superior design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL0QH3VSNAFAMZ/b2980195ff67942ce6a7026f0b8f1ce4.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Customized Curves</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t let anything slip away. The rounded curves of the 5.5-inch Huawei Y6II were designed for easy one-handed use, offering the greatest display size, best design and greatest comfort. *The product color may vary in different countries and areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL0QH3VSNAFAMZ/0f6df7e01bba450f4e06a79f43a046d8.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Smoother Performance &amp; Ultra-High Efficiency</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Y6II&rsquo;s Kirin 620, 1.2GHz processor let you live without compromises. The lightning fast, 64-bit octa-core allows multiple apps to be open simultaneously without sacrificing speed, power or performance. And the ARM architecture has ultra-high efficiency for longer battery life. The 2GB of RAM, 16GB ROM and 128GB SD card (supported) gives you more capacity, lower power consumption, faster speed and longer use than any smartphone you have ever owned.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL0QH3VSNAFAMZ/d9e61f54128115c636cfd2f30a9b5af0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Android 6.0 + EMUI</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Based on Android 6.0, the Y6II uses the EMUI4.1 operating system, using cutting-edge software to drive a breathtaking user experience. The built-in phone manager monitors power consumption for extended battery life, and cleans and optimizes the devices O.S., while the App Lock and Do Not Disturb functions protect user privacy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL0QH3VSNAFAMZ/4adeeff5e1d72516b7b8bc2fb2b605e3.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1244', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 17850, 17000, 1, 'huawei-y6-ii-5-5-inch-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-4g-lte-dual-sim-color-white.jpg', 'huawei-y6-ii-5-5-inch-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-4g-lte-dual-sim-color-white-2.jpg', 'huawei-y6-ii-5-5-inch-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-4g-lte-dual-sim-color-white-3.jpg', 'huawei-y6-ii-5-5-inch-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-4g-lte-dual-sim-color-white-4.jpg', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'huawei-y6-ii-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-dual-sim-white', '2017-09-24 21:14:24', '2017-09-24 21:14:24'),
(544, 1, 21, 61, 2, 29, NULL, 'Huawei Y6 II, 5.5 inch, 16GB, 2GB RAM, 13MP, Dual SIM Gold', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 5&quot; IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Processor: Quad-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>Internal storage: 16 GB,&nbsp;2 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 13MP rear, 5MP front facing</li>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Po 4000 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>Product Specifications</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.0 inches (~67.1% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 720 x 1280 pixels (~294 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch</li>\r\n	<li>EMUI 3.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Mediatek MT6735P</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali-T720MP2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 128 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 16 GB, 2 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 13 MP, f/2.0, 28mm, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, panorama, HDR</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5 MP, f/2.2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sound</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Comms</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN: Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: v4.0, A2DP, LE</li>\r\n	<li>GPS: Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS</li>\r\n	<li>Radio: FM radio</li>\r\n	<li>USB: microUSB v2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Features</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sensors: Accelerometer, proximity</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging: SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li>\r\n	<li>Browser: HTML5</li>\r\n	<li>Fast battery charging</li>\r\n	<li>Reverse charging</li>\r\n	<li>Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/eAAC+/Flac player</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Po 4000 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Huawei Y6 Pro</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy the ultimate value for your money with the&nbsp;Huawei Y6 Pro. It offers seamless functionality and easy to navigate interface that will blow your mind away. With oozing class and style, the Huawei Y6 Pro&nbsp;is surely your perfect companion whichever the occasion. The Huawei Y6 Pro packs a 13-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 5-megapixel front shooter for selfies. A 4000mAh battery ensures that your charge lasts for a long time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for huawei logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL1IC9DWNAFAMZ/d48d9eab6c688b2b1ea2426ed2b3042c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:276px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:293px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Great Design</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Capture the attention of others with the Huawei Y6 Pro. It features a&nbsp;distinctive texture design, made with 5176 water ripple elements. Ergonomically designed with a&nbsp;modern and elegant solid metal frame you will be the envy of everyone around you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Y6 Pro" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL1IC9DWNAFAMZ/cfa2c6304043ff605e7704017cb493c2.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:365px; margin:14px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:700px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Clear Capture Camera</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Take amazing photos with a lasting clarity through the sophisticated 13-mega-pixel, 2.0 aperture camera. With the 5 mega-pixel 84-degree selfie camera, you will see yourself clearer as well. The reliably efficient quad-core processor will be at your side through every step. Managing multiple tasks with ease, the Y6 Pro will never slow you down, even when the moment of bliss comes unexpectedly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Y6 Pro camera" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL1IC9DWNAFAMZ/ff7a13bf2803192ada993afb7a00b622.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:369px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:633px" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Long lasting charge</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Huawei Y6 Pro uses a 4000mAh battery that ensures long-lasting performance. With the Smart Power Saving technology, the phone can last for 24hrs with only 10% battery charge&nbsp;while idle. This phone can also act as a charger for your other devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Y6 Pro" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL1IC9DWNAFAMZ/6dd3ee185331bccf9816cd2949db0da5.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:471px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1245', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 15215, 14490, 1, 'huawei-y6-ii-5-5-inch-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-4g-lte-dual-sim-color-gold.jpg', 'huawei-y6-ii-5-5-inch-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-4g-lte-dual-sim-color-gold-2.jpg', 'huawei-y6-ii-5-5-inch-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-4g-lte-dual-sim-color-gold-3.jpg', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'huawei-y6-ii-5-5-inch-16gb-2gb-ram-13mp-dual-sim-gold', '2017-09-24 21:22:57', '2017-09-24 21:22:57'),
(545, 1, 21, 61, 2, 30, NULL, 'Tecno L9 Plus (13MP,Fingerprint, 2GB RAM 16 GB)Gold', '<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Android 7.0 (Nougat)</li>\r\n	<li>1.3GHz Quad core</li>\r\n	<li>6.0&quot; IPS Touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>13MP AF Back Camera with flash</li>\r\n	<li>5MP Front Camera with Flash</li>\r\n	<li>16GB ROM + 2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable microSD up to 32GB</li>\r\n	<li>GPS, WiFi,BT, OTG Connectivity</li>\r\n	<li>G-Sensor, Ambient Light Sensor, Proximity Sensor, Fingerprint Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>5000mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>General</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Device type: Smartphone</li>\r\n	<li>Model: Tecno L9&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Design type: Phablet</li>\r\n	<li>Display Type: IPS LCD Capacitive Touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Size:6.0 inches</li>\r\n	<li>Dimensions:162x81.8x7.99mm</li>\r\n	<li>Dual &nbsp;SIM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Camera:13MP</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:5 MP</li>\r\n	<li>Video:1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>16GB + 2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable microSD up to 32GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Software</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>1.3GHz Quad core</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Additional Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GPS, WiFi,BT, OTG Connectivity</li>\r\n	<li>G-Sensor, Ambient Light Sensor, Proximity Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Fingerprint Scanner</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Battery</li>\r\n	<li>Capacity:5000mAh Battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Tecno introduced the &ldquo;L series&rdquo; devices to&nbsp;cater for those that care a lot about battery life. Each device in this series&nbsp;is known for its&nbsp;long-lasting&nbsp;battery ;&nbsp;usually above 24hours. The L9 Plus 