>\r\n	<li>Battery Type: Non-removable 3000mAh Capacity</li>\r\n	<li>Standby Time: Up to 1.5 days</li>\r\n	<li>Talk Time: Up to 1 days</li>\r\n	<li>Fast Charging</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2096/2017/09/2096_05593395589733716_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2096/2017/08/2096_05570182763334886_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001982900689_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001978641080_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001978788913_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552016132661728_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001988114668_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001990489690_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001993090989_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001992263937_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001992567391_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001994723851_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001996556650_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552001999538484_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552002000779827_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552002002755297_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /><img alt="image" src="https://d2lpfujvrf17tu.cloudfront.net/kenya/shop/store/goods/2046/2017/08/2046_05552002004902094_1280.jpg" style="border:medium none; box-sizing:border-box; max-width:100%; outline:none; vertical-align:top" title="TECNO Spark Exclusive @Kilimall.co.ke" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<p>The TECNO Spark K7 is a new line of photo-focused smartphones from TECNO, targeted largely at millennial youths, especially students who mostly have to live on a budget. Best known for its bright screen and advanced camera features, the Spark has been termed the brightest smartphones yet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spark K7 has a HD screen that measures 5.5 inches diagonally, display quality is set at 720 by 1280 pixels with 267 PPI.&nbsp;The available screen resolution is not bad for an entry-level device with approachable price tag, the display won&rsquo;t be distorted in any way and will serve well for video streaming and gaming purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Android 7.0 Nougat is pre-installed on the Spark K7 with HiOS 2.0 skin on top, the HiOS interface is said to deliver fluid multi-tasking experience like never seen before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The TECNO Spark K7 stays true to the revolutionary pixel sensor and denoising camera technologies of latest TECNO smartphone cameras. Its 13MP rear and 5MP front camera provides high-sensitivity camera capabilities which help users get better imaging results anytime, anywhere and under any kind of lightening condition.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere is also a single LED flash available for the front and back cameras to help boost image quality in low light conditions, giving you a great imaging experience. In some cases, the front LED flash can also be used as notification light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tecno Spark K7 carries a sufficient 3000 mAh battery in the powerhouse.</p>\r\n\r\n<div style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1342', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 9450, 9000, 1, 'tecno-spark-model-k7-13mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-blue.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'tecno-spark-model-k7-13mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-blue', '2017-09-24 21:33:04', '2017-09-24 21:33:04'),
(548, 1, 21, 61, 1, 29, NULL, 'Huawei Y3 II, 8GB, 1GB RAM, 5MP Camera, Dual SIM Color- Black', '<h3 class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong>Key Features</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 5&quot;&nbsp;IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 5 MP Primary + 2MP Secondary</li>\r\n	<li>Storage: 8 GB, 1 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: Removable Li-Po 2200 mA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Product Specifications</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>DISPLAY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size 5.0 inches (~66.6% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution 720 x 1280 pixels (~294 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Emotion UI 3.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>CAMERA</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary8 MP, f/2.0, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>FeaturesYes</li>\r\n	<li>VideoYes</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary2 MP, LED flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>PLATFORM</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OSAndroid OS, v5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>ChipsetMediatek MT6735P - 4G model</li>\r\n	<li>CPU Quad-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A53 - 4G model</li>\r\n	<li>GPU &nbsp;Mali-T720MP2 - 4G model</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>NETWORK</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>3G&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>GPRS Yes</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE Yes</li>\r\n	<li>SIM : Dual SIM (Micro-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>MEMORY</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slotmicroSD, up to 32 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal 8 GB, 1 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>SOUND</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert typesVibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>LoudspeakerYes</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jackYes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>COMMS</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLANWi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetoothv4.0, A2DP, LE</li>\r\n	<li>GPSYes, with A-GPS</li>\r\n	<li>RadioFM radio</li>\r\n	<li>USBmicroUSB v2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>FEATURES</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SensorsAccelerometer, proximity, compass</li>\r\n	<li>MessagingSMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Email, IM</li>\r\n	<li>BrowserHTML5</li>\r\n	<li>MP3/WAV/eAAC+ player</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/H.264 player</li>\r\n	<li>Document viewer</li>\r\n	<li>Photo/video editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Removable Li-Po 2200 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Huawei Y3 II&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Huawei Y3 II lights up when you get a call, communicating alerts and notifications in vibrant color. Immerse yourself in bright hues that dance to the rhythm of your ringtone. Let your phone send a rainbow into your world.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL18YM7SNAFAMZ/66e31a9d939af7bdbc8a842744f7ed62.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Music to Your Ears</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Music is the irresistible drive of the night. Delivering an awesome acoustic performance, Huawei Y3II places the immersive experience of a concert in your own pocket.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL18YM7SNAFAMZ/8848050e797911219252994f995f601f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The Easy Key to a Smarter Experience</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Easy Key function offers an easy, intuitive way to operate the device. Simply pre-set the button function, and let the Easy Key to perform it. So if you set the action to camera, a single press will take a quick snapshot. Create multiple function shortcuts by using the double press and press-and-hold gestures to make the device easily accessible by touch alone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL18YM7SNAFAMZ/2587760ccc439f662ee905039082c935.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>More Choice in Colors</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Never settle for the simplicity of black and white. Live in a world of vibrant color. Rose Pink, Sky Blue, Arctic White, Obsidian Black, and Sand Gold are the five colors that will inspire love at first sight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HU687EL18YM7SNAFAMZ/bcc39b71b787f3bc297db95f82384dcc.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1247', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 8373, 7899, 1, 'huawei-y3-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black.jpg', 'huawei-y3-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black-2.jpg', 'huawei-y3-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black-3.jpg', 'huawei-y3-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black-4.jpg', 'huawei-y3-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'huawei-y3-ii-8gb-1gb-ram-5mp-camera-dual-sim-color-black', '2017-09-24 21:42:50', '2017-09-24 21:42:50');
