(560, 1, 21, 61, 2, 29, NULL, 'Huawei GR5 - 5.5 inch, 16GB, Dual SIM, 2GB RAM, 13MP- Silver', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size: 5.5&quot; Screen</li>\r\n	<li>Display Type:&nbsp;Full HD touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android&trade; 5.1 (Lollipop)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Primary Camera: 13MP AF ,Secondary: 5MP FF&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory:16GB, 2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Battery Capacity: 3000mAh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen Size: 5.5&quot; display</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Type:&nbsp;FHD touchscreen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CPU: Qualcomm&reg; MSM8939</li>\r\n	<li>Octa-core(4&times;1.5GHz+4&times;1.2GHz)</li>\r\n	<li>Operation System: Android&trade; 5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Storage</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>16GB ROM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 13MP AF&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5MP FF&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Network</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>4G: HUAWEI KII-L21:FDD B1/B3/B7/B8/B20, HUAWEI KII-L22:TDD B40, FDD B1/B3/B5/B7/B8/B28, HUAWEI KII-L23/HUAWEI KII-L03:FDD B2/B4/B5/B7/B28</li>\r\n	<li>3G: HUAWEI KII-L21:UMTS B1/B2/B8, HUAWEI KII-L22:UMTS B1/B5/B8, HUAWEI KII-L23/HUAWEI KII-L03:UMTS B1/B2/B5/B4(AWS)</li>\r\n	<li>2G: 850/900/1800/1900MHz</li>\r\n	<li>GPS: GPS/AGPS/Glonass</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth 4.1,WI-FI 402.11b/g/n, 2.4G</li>\r\n	<li>Sensors: Fingerprint sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Accelerometer, Proximity sensor, light sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Digital compass, Magnetometer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>MP3, MIDI, AMR-NB, AAC, AAC+, eAAC+, PCM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Video</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>H.263, H.264, MPEG-4</li>\r\n	<li>EMUI: Emotion UI 3.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Capacity: 3000mAh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Huawei GR5</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Get this Huawei GR5 Smartphone that is designed to enhance your mobile experience in every way. Enjoy improved connectivity (WiFi, 4G and 4G LTE and clearer calls), enhanced power and efficiency. You&#39;ll enjoy enhanced multimedia features thanks to the advanced camera features of a Snapdragon processor and realistic 3D graphics for gaming.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The Power of Touch</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 5.5-inch screen puts a clearly superior cinematic eInnovative fingerprint technology makes every touch of your device an interactive experience. Fast, smart, and convenient, a single tap can unlock the phone, take a photo, or answer a phone call in an instant.xperience in the palm of your hands.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Designed to Impress</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>An elegant and strong aluminum magnesium alloy body molded into a classic frame presents the device not only in a beautiful light but displays the exacting, state-of-the art craftsmanship it took to construct the device. A Huawei GR5 in your hand will always be the iconic fashion statement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capture Your Life&#39;s Moments</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t miss a second of your life. A 13-megapixel f/2.0 camera makes the Huawei GR5 an essential tool for keeping track of all the colorful moments in life. What makes the photography experience so incredibly special are the different filters you can use to enhance the minute details and colors of each photograph. The Good Food photo filter brings out the natural appeal of delicious courses and makes your food look as good as it tastes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Better Vision</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Huawei GR5 is not just a pretty 5.5-inch FHD screen. The smart light sensor can keenly detect changes in light while the Apical Assertive Display automatically begets dynamic adjustment. See the world in its full detail with Huawei GR5.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Performance and Efficiency</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The octa-core Qualcomm Snapdragon CPU delivers balanced performance with efficient task management and high speed processing power while keeping the energy consumption low.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Takes You All the Way</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The powerful 3000mAh battery perfectly affords long time entertainment and task. Even the charge period has been shortened. You will spend less time waiting and much more time on fun, with Huawei GR5 a perfect companion.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'GLN1255', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 25200, 24000, 1, 'huawei-gr5-5-5-inch-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-color-silver.jpg', 'huawei-gr5-5-5-inch-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-color-silver-2.jpg', 'huawei-gr5-5-5-inch-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-color-silver-3.jpg', 'huawei-gr5-5-5-inch-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-color-silver-4.jpg', 'huawei-gr5-5-5-inch-16gb-4g-lte-dual-sim-2gb-ram-13mp-camera-color-silver-5.jpg', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'huawei-gr5-5-5-inch-16gb-dual-sim-2gb-ram-13mp-silver', '2017-09-25 15:00:30', '2017-09-25 15:00:30'),
