(562, 1, 21, 61, 2, 29, NULL, 'Huawei GR3, 5.2 inch, 12MP,16GB, 3GB RAM, Dual SIM - Gold', '<h3><strong>Key Features</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display: 5.2-inch FHD display</li>\r\n	<li>Operation System : Android&trade; 7.0+EMUI 5.0</li>\r\n	<li>Memory : 3GB RAM+ 16GB ROM</li>\r\n	<li>Camera :&nbsp;12MP + 8MP Front</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Product Specifications</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.2&quot; HD touchscreen</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CPU: MTK MTK6753T, Octa core, 1.5 GHz, Cortex-A53 64bit</li>\r\n	<li>Operation System: Android&trade; 5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal: 16GB, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>12&nbsp;MP AF camera+5 MP FF camera</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Network</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>4G: L01/L21:FDD B1/B3/B7/B8/B20,&nbsp;L13:FDD?B2/B4/B5/B7/B12/B17,&nbsp;L22:TDD B38/B40, FDD B1/B3/B5/B7/B8/B28,&nbsp;L03/L23:FDD B2/B4/B5/B7/B28</li>\r\n	<li>3G: L01/L21:UMTS B1/B8,&nbsp;L22:UMTS B1/B5/B8,&nbsp;L03/L13/L23:UMTS B1/B2/B5/B4</li>\r\n	<li>2G: 850/900/1800/1900MHz</li>\r\n	<li>GPS: GPS/AGPS/Glonass</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth 4.1, A2DP, EDR, LE support Wi-Fi hotspot, Wi-Fi direct</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Video</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>H.263, H.264, MPEG-4</li>\r\n	<li>EMUI: Emotion UI 3.1 Lite</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>3000mAh non-removable&nbsp;Lithium polymer battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align:center"><strong>Huawei GR3(2017)</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Be the envy of your friends with the new Huawei GR3(2017) which gives you an amazing experience whether you want to connect to the internet, play games or take amazing photos? The Huawei GR3(2017) gives you all of this and more.&nbsp;With a&nbsp;Octa core&nbsp;1.5 GHz&nbsp;Cortex-A53 64bit processor, 12MP camera and 4G LTE plus a long lasting battery, experience the excellen