(564, 1, 21, 61, 2, 30, NULL, 'TECNO L8 Lite (8MP Camera, 16GB, 1GB RAM )Champagne Gold', '<div class="detail-features" style="box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 230px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">\r\n<div class="list -features -compact -no-float" style="box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; border-top: 1px solid rgb(233, 233, 233); padding: 10px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px;">\r\n<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display:&nbsp;5.0 Inch Screen IPS&nbsp; Capacitive Touchscreen&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory: 16GB, 1GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: 1.3GHz Quad-Core</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 8MP Primary Camera, up to 3264 x 2448-pixel pictures, HDR, autofocus; 2MP Front Camera</li>\r\n	<li>Operating System: Android v 6.0</li>\r\n	<li>Battery Capacity: 4000mAh Li-Ion</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<div class="product-long-description-detailed" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family: proxima-nova-n9, proxima-nova, sans-serif; font-size: 12.6px;">\r\n<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Screen Type: IPS capacitive touchscreen with 16,000,000 colors<br />\r\nScreen Size: 5.0 inches<br />\r\nResolution:&nbsp;720 x 1280 pixels</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform</p>\r\n\r\n<p>OS: Android 6.0 Lollipop<br />\r\nProcessors: Quad-core 1.3 GHZ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Primary: 8MP, up to 3264 x 2448-pixel pictures<br />\r\nHDR, autofocus, Geo-tagging, panorama camera with LED flash<br />\r\nVideo<br />\r\nSecondary: 2MP up to 1600 x 1200-pixel pictures</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Card slot: MicroSD card, up to 128GB<br />\r\nInternal: 16GB<br />\r\nRAM: 1GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Audio</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Alert types: Vibration, MP3 ringtones<br />\r\nLoudspeaker<br />\r\nAudio port: 3.5mm jack<br />\r\nConnectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p>The Tecno L8 Lite&nbsp;is unbelievably smart, perfect for work, gaming, watching movies in HD, listening to music, taking pictures and a whole lot more. It isis packed with features designed to give you a chance to relax, connect with family and friends and keep you entertained. A 5.0 inch&nbsp;IPS capacitive touchscreen, 16GB internal storage and a long life battery of 4000mAh capacity, the Tecno L8 Lite&nbsp;offers more ways to live a convenient life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Tecno L8 Lite best price in Nigeria" src="https://static.jumia.com.ng/cms/external/pet/TE339EL13DOUENAFAMZ/208565547fe8b22260af3b5daaceef02.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:293px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:337px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Ample Storage</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The TECNO L8 Lite&nbsp;comes with 1GB of RAM and 16GB of internal storage space. The 16GB of space can be expanded to 128GBusing a microSD card. Smoothly move through apps thanks to 1GB of RAM, that allow you to handle&nbsp;most Android tasks without any glitches.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>?<img alt="Tecno L8 Lite Memory" src="https://static.jumia.com.ng/cms/external/pet/TE339EL13DOUENAFAMZ/d3061a96bea53730b583b82c42a366ea.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:393px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fast Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We are sure you like quick performance from your smartphone. The awesome TECNO L8 Lite is powered by a Quad-core 1.3 GHZ&nbsp;MediaTek processor which is quite reliable for an entry level device. As for the OS, it comes with Android 6.0.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Affordable Android Marshmallow Phones in Nigeria" src="https://static.jumia.com.ng/cms/external/pet/TE339EL13DOUENAFAMZ/c726a799f0a3557bd9bc19ffa1e0cfa4.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:250px; margin:72px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Long Life Battery</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Long gone are the days when you had to carry your charger everywhere you go. Enjoy an unplugged life with TECNO L8 Lite 4000mAh Li-Ion battery that gets you through the day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for battery capacity" src="https://static.jumia.com.ng/cms/external/pet/TE339EL13DOUENAFAMZ/5c4d0ecba534d4433920dc7671215fe9.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:300px; margin:47px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:400px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1347', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 9450, 9000, 1, 'tecno-l8-lite-8mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-champagne-gold.jpg', 'tecno-l8-lite-8mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-champagne-gold-2.jpg', 'tecno-l8-lite-8mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-champagne-gold-3.jpg', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'tecno-l8-lite-8mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-champagne-gold', '2017-09-25 15:39:35', '2017-09-25 15:39:35'),
