ttery</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Long gone are the days when you had to carry your charger everywhere you go. Enjoy an unplugged life with TECNO L8 Lite 4000mAh Li-Ion battery that gets you through the day.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1348', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 8925, 8500, 1, 'tecno-l8-lite-8mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-silver.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'tecno-l8-lite-8mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-silver', '2017-09-25 15:44:22', '2017-09-25 15:44:22'),
