Audio</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration, MP3 ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Capacity: 4000mAh Li-Ion battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>The Tecno L8 Lite&nbsp;is unbelievably smart, perfect for work, gaming, watching movies in HD, listening to music, taking pictures and a whole lot more. It isis packed with features designed to give you a chance to relax, connect with family and friends and keep you entertained. A 5.0 inch&nbsp;IPS capacitive touchscreen, 16GB internal storage and a long life battery of 4000mAh capacity, the Tecno L8 Lite&nbsp;offers more ways to live a convenient life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Tecno L8 Lite best price in Nigeria" src="https://static.jumia.com.ng/cms/external/pet/TE339EL13DOUENAFAMZ/208565547fe8b22260af3b5daaceef02.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:293px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:337px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Ample Storage</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The TECNO L8 Lite&nbsp;comes with 1GB of RAM and 16GB of internal storage space. The 16GB of space can be expanded to 128GBusing a microSD card. Smoothly move through apps thanks to 1GB of RAM, that allow you to handle&nbsp;most Android tasks without any glitches.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>?<img alt="Tecno L8 Lite Memory" src="https://static.jumia.com.ng/cms/external/pet/TE339EL13DOUENAFAMZ/d3061a96bea53730b583b82c42a366ea.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:393px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fast Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We are sure you like quick performance from your smartphone. The awesome TECNO L8 Lite is powered by a Quad-core 1.3 GHZ&nbsp;MediaTek processor which is quite reliable for an entry level device. As for the OS, it comes with Android 6.0.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Affordable Android Marshmallow Phones in Nigeria" src="https://static.jumia.com.ng/cms/external/pet/TE339EL13DOUENAFAMZ/c726a799f0a3557bd9bc19ffa1e0cfa4.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:250px; margin:72px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Long Life Battery</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Long gone are the days when you had to carry your charger everywhere you go. Enjoy an unplugged life with TECNO L8 Lite 4000mAh Li-Ion battery that gets you through the day.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1349', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 12600, 12000, 1, 'tecno-l8-lite-8mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-grey.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'tecno-l8-lite-8mp-camera-16gb-1gb-ram-grey', '2017-09-25 15:48:45', '2017-09-25 15:48:45');
