nt camera and flash, while the 8GB memory provides more than enough space for your memories. Buy the Tecno W1 online on Jumia at the best price in Nigeria.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Entry-level Android phone Tecno W1 best price" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/TE685EL0FQG4ONAFAMZ/31f83ebd9c7cc2b7b9b0a976c02099a4.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:434px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:710px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The front camera of Tecno W1 comes with a flash. So no matter what time of the day, your pictures still come out as clear as day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/TE685EL0FQG4ONAFAMZ/0cf23f791aec0823564a8058616da4b2.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/TE685EL0FQG4ONAFAMZ/8a5556ef2f4e2f6f5e17beb6c776b7b4.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t let the size and price fool you. The W1 packs the power of a 1.3GHz Quad-Core processor, and with the 1GB RAM, you can enjoy easy multitasking, effortlessly switching between apps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Tecno W1 with front camera flash" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/TE685EL0FQG4ONAFAMZ/4dea818c6fd447605671c8622dad44a6.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:428px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:710px" /><img alt="tecno w1 affordable Android Nougat phone." src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/TE685EL0FQG4ONAFAMZ/790b3eccf4b1ed17186b53c9dd0da287.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:709px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1350', 