(573, 1, 21, 61, 2, 30, NULL, ' TECNO Model WX3P (5MP Camera, 8GB, 1GB RAM) Champagne Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.0Inch display</li>\r\n	<li>Android 7.0,Nougat</li>\r\n	<li>5.0MP back camera with flash</li>\r\n	<li>5.0MP front camera with flash</li>\r\n	<li>8GB ROM + 1GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Expandable Micro SD,up to 32GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Display: 5-inch, 480 x 854 pixels (197 PPI), IPS LCD Capacitive touchscreen<br />\r\nSensors: Accelerometer, Proximity and Compass<br />\r\nHardware</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Type: Quad-core 1.3 GHz&nbsp;<br />\r\nProcessor Name: Mediatek<br />\r\nGraphics Processor:<br />\r\nRAM: 1 GB<br />\r\nInternal Storage: 8 GB<br />\r\nExternal Storage: microSD, up to 32 GB</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rear: 5 MP, 2592 x 1944 pixels, autofocus, LED flash&nbsp;<br />\r\nVideo recording: Yes<br />\r\nFront-facing: 5 MP with LED flash and screen flash</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery: 2500 mA</p>\r\n', '<p>The Tecno Wx3P is a 5.0-inch smartphone having a resolution of 854*480 pixels. The device boots Android 7.0 Nougat out of the box and HiOS interphase.The major highlight of the new WX3P is the battery. The phone&nbsp;is powered by a huge 5000mAh battery.</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>3 Days of Unstopped Entertainment</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>In the heart of your powerful device sits a 5000mAh large battery, which delivers continuous energy for an uninterrupted experience. Coupled with smart power-saving technology, you can have more than 3 days of battery life at a single charge. Just like a dynamic partner, it stays alive along your journey, passing your voice to someone on the other end of the call, talking into your ears and surprising you with stunning graphics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/exter