ical-align:bottom; width:263px"><strong>Extras:</strong></td>\r\n			<td style="vertical-align:bottom; width:487px">Dual SIM</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '', '', '', 'JCG1369', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 15750, 15000, 1, 'tecno-l7-16gb-2gb-ram-5-0-inches.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'tecno-l7-16gb-2gb-ram-5-0-inches', '2017-09-26 17:58:33', '2017-09-26 17:58:33'),
(587, 1, 21, 61, 2, NULL, NULL, 'HTC One X9 Dual ( 13MP Camera, 3GB RAM 32GB ROM) Black Grey', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen Size: 5.5&nbsp;inches</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Type: Super LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>OS: &nbsp;Android OS, v5. (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 13MP Back, 5MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 32GB Internal, 3GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: Non-removable Li-Po 3000 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen&nbsp;Size:&nbsp;5.5 inches (~71.4% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Screen&nbsp;Type:&nbsp;Super LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels (~401 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch</li>\r\n	<li>Protection:&nbsp;Corning Gorilla Glass (unspecified version)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Mediatek MT6795 Helio X10</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Octa-core Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: PowerVR G6200</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 200 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 32 GB</li>\r\n	<li>RAM: 3GB&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 13 MP, f/2.0, 28mm, autofocus, OIS, dual-LED (dual tone) flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, panorama, HDR</li>\r\n	<li>Video: 2160p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5 MP, f/2.8, 34mm, 1080p@30fps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sound</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alert types: Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker: with stereo speakers</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Communication</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>WLAN: Wi-Fi 802.11 dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, DLNA, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth: v4.2, A2DP, aptX</li>\r\n	<li>GPS: with A-GPS, GLONASS, BDS</li>\r\n	<li>USB: microUSB v2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p>Introducing the HTC One X9: packed with city smarts</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience an eye-popping 5.5&rdquo; full HD display, blur-free photos, superior smartphone audio and an elegant design that stands out while fitting your hand with ease, a long-lasting battery life and your best selfies ever. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Made with city swagger, the HTC One X9 packs style and high-tech performance into a silky-smooth design. Featuring full frontal glass display and an over 70% screen-to-body ratio. Available in Opal Silver and Carbon Grey.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>big screen, slim body</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Big screens don&rsquo;t have to be bulky. Fitting a 5.5&rdquo; FHD screen into a slender body, the HTC One X9 boasts a 401 PPI display for remarkable details.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt="" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/sellerhq_merchant_images.konga.com/55168_1460581705.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>shoot like a pro</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The main camera of the HTC One X9 features OIS for sharp, bright photos in an instant. Our most advanced OIS uses an anti-shake lens to reduce blur. Capture all your big city moments, day or night. Simply point, click and smile.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<img alt="" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/sellerhq_merchant_images.konga.com/55168_1460581722.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>cinematic surround sound</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Great looks, incredible sound. Push play and you&rsquo;ll immediately hear how HTC BoomSound&trade; and Dolby Audio Surround&trade; combine to take your music, films and games to the next level with clear vocals, deep bass and fine audio detail. You&rsquo;ll enjoy rich audio from both external speakers as well as headphones.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>amp it up</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The HTC One X9&rsquo;s built-in amp provides the raw power needed to bring out the best in your music collection, for a superior audio experience you&rsquo;ll crave.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1370', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 22469, 21399, 1, 'htc-one-x9-dual-13mp-camera-3gb-ram-32gb-rom-black-grey.jpg', 'htc-one-x9-dual-13mp-camera-3gb-ram-32gb-rom-black-grey-2.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'htc-one-x9-dual-13mp-camera-3gb-ram-32gb-rom-black-grey', '2017-09-28 07:08:04', '2017-09-28 07:08:04'),
(588, 1, 21, 61, 2, NULL, NULL, 'HTC One M10   (12MP Camera ,32GB, 4GB RAM)White', '<p><strong>Key features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset:Qualcomm MSM8996 Snapdragon 820</li>\r\n	<li>CPU:Dual-core 2.15 GHz Kryo &amp; dual-core 1.6 GHz Kryo</li>\r\n	<li>GPU:Adreno 530</li>\r\n	<li>Card slot:microSD, up to 200 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal:32 GB, 4 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Primary:12 MP, f/1.8, 26mm, OIS, laser autofocus, dual-LED (dual tone) flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Qualcomm MSM8996 Snapdragon 820</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Dual-core 2.15 GHz Kryo &amp; dual-core 1.6 GHz Kryo</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Adreno 530</li>\r\n	<li>Features:1/2.3&#39;&#39; sensor size, 1.55&micro;m pixel size, geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, HDR, panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Video:2160p@30fps, 1080p@60fps, 720p@120fps, HDR, stereo sound rec.</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:5 MP, f/1.8, 23mm, OIS, autofocus, 1.34 &micro;m pixel size, 1080p, HDR</li>\r\n	<li>Alert types:Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker:Yes, dual speakers</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm jack:Yes, 24-bit/192kHz audio</li>\r\n	<li>WLAN:Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, DLNA, hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth:v4.2</li>\r\n	<li>USB:v3.1, Type-C 1.0 reversible connector</li>\r\n	<li>Sensors:Fingerprint, accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass</li>\r\n	<li>Messaging:SMS (threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Email</li>\r\n	<li>Browser:HTML5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>HTC M10</strong>, it&rsquo;s more of what you&rsquo;re looking for in a flagship phone. Unparalleled performance. Superb 24-bit Hi-Res sound. The world&rsquo;s first Optical Image Stabilization in both front and back cameras. And one of the highest smartphone camera rankings ever from DxOMark. All in a beautifully crafted metal unibody.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/279ee90d9e587c5418c481f0242302f7.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/279ee90d9e587c5418c481f0242302f7.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:938px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Inspiration Realized in Metal</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s the beauty of light, crafted into a brand new all-metal unibody. Every element of HTC M10 has been designed, refined and perfected. From the bold new chamfered contour to its stunning dual-textured finish and quality construction. All the way down to getting the perfect click from the power button.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/0e5b1648c8e1cc7930f56aab396729b6.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/0e5b1648c8e1cc7930f56aab396729b6.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:388px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:917px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Next Generation Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>HTC M10 delivers what may well be the best smartphone camera available today. With innovations like the world&rsquo;s first OIS front and back, 12 million UltraPixels, faster laser autofocus and more. A DxOMark score of 88*, one of the highest camera quality scores of any smartphone so far, shows we&rsquo;re definitely on the right track.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/287d5c781b29f3553a9de2c30abcc080.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/287d5c781b29f3553a9de2c30abcc080.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:399px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:943px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Brilliant Hi-Res Audio</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>HTC M10 sets a new gold standard in sound quality with its brand new BoomSound Hi-Fi edition speakers, Personal Audio Profile and Hi-Res audio earphones. All of which works beautifully with HTC 10&rsquo;s certified 24-bit Hi-Res audio. Music has never sounded this good on a smartphone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/60a8209f239c5c2e6568f31f27505399.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/60a8209f239c5c2e6568f31f27505399.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:406px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:960px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Off the Chart Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With HTC M10, apps launch faster and run smoother, the screen reacts instantly to your every touch, and things just work brilliantly. It&rsquo;s what you expect from best in class hardware and software tuned to near perfection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/f6693c6763b0d6735667130f4ec89080.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/f6693c6763b0d6735667130f4ec89080.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:501px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:459px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Unprecedented Control</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the greatest things about Android is how it empowers you. HTC M10 magnifies the level of control you have and lets you easily personalize your phone in ways you&rsquo;ve never thought possible. All while offering you fine-grained control over apps like never before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/48d46022938633661746e1ec29d3be16.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/48d46022938633661746e1ec29d3be16.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:447px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:1059px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Made to Last and Last</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Every part of HTC M10 has been optimized from the ground up to run more efficiently. Giving you up to 2 days of use. It also stays cooler while charging faster than ever &ndash; up to 50% in just 30 minutes &ndash; enough for a day on the go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/521eec7b1d8792a4ffc3800d9a65c0ca.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0MV0JSNAFAMZ/521eec7b1d8792a4ffc3800d9a65c0ca.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:929px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1371', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 41999, 39999, 1, 'htc-one-m10-12mp-camera-32gb-4gb-ram-white.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'htc-one-m10-12mp-camera-32gb-4gb-ram-white', '2017-09-28 07:18:06', '2017-09-28 07:18:06'),
