(596, 1, 21, 61, 2, 31, NULL, ' HTC Desire 10 Pro ( 20MP Camera , 64GB, 4GB RAM)Black', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Size: &nbsp;5.5 inches (~70.5% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 64 GB, 4 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Primary: 20 MP</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Secondary: 13 MP</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SIM:Single SIM (Nano-SIM)</li>\r\n	<li>Type:Super LCD5 capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size:5.2 inches (~71.1% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution:1440 x 2560 pixels (~565 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch:Yes</li>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset:Qualcomm MSM8996 Snapdragon 820</li>\r\n	<li>CPU:Dual-core 2.15 GHz Kryo &amp; dual-core 1.6 GHz Kryo</li>\r\n	<li>GPU:Adreno 530</li>\r\n	<li>Card slot:microSD, up to 200 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal:32 GB, 4 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Primary:12 MP, f/1.8, 26mm, OIS, laser autofocus, dual-LED (dual tone) flash</li>\r\n	<li>Video:2160p@30fps, 1080p@60fps, 720p@120fps, HDR, stereo sound rec.</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:5 MP, f/1.8, 23mm, OIS, autofocus, 1.34 &micro;m pixel size, 1080p, HDR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>HTC Desire 10 Pro smartphone comes with a 5.50-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 1080 pixels by 1920 pixels at a PPI of 400 pixels per inch.&nbsp;The HTC Desire 10 Pro is powered by 1.8GHz octa-core MediaTek Helio P10 processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone packs 32GB of internal storage. HTC Desire 10 Pro packs a 20-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 13-megapixel front shooter for selfies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0TPMBSNAFAMZ/e13489bffc72dbf98f7f0255c0a5d2d5.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:210px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:300px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Capture Clear Photos</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Take stunning photos using a 20MP camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0TPMBSNAFAMZ/d1b50dfa700b5e78302285613b629dbf.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>13MP Selfie Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Smile for the selfie camera that has the same sensor pixel count as the main camera in many other phones. If you&rsquo;re serious about great-looking selfies then you&rsquo;ll appreciate the HTC Desire 10 pro&rsquo;s 13MP selfie camera. It promises you higher resolution selfies that capture more scenery and good time with friends. This selfie camera also features a built-in screen flash, which helps you take brighter selfies in low light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0TPMBSNAFAMZ/9f01bf13f3a6de9b9c344f2d2d823987.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fingerprint Security</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Protect your valuable data. HTC Desire 10 pro&rsquo;s fingerprint security keeps your data safe, but quickly unlocks at just the touch of your finger. The sensor recognizes your fingerprint from almost every angle and position. And, with the App Lock function in Boost+, your fingerprint can also be used to help prevent your apps from being opened by others.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0TPMBSNAFAMZ/bf3dcfa0a3be364b7ec26fabf0a81f3a.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>More Storage Space</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>HTC Desire 10 pro gives you more space for the things that are important with a massive 4GB of RAM and 64GB storage space. So you can load up on photos, videos, movies, games and more. And if that&rsquo;s not enough room, HTC Desire 10 pro has SD card support for up to 2TB expandable memory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fully Customizable</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Make your phone as unique as you are. HTC Freestyle Layout frees you from an onscreen grid and lets you get creative. Drag icons, stickers and widgets anywhere. Layer them, overlap them, group them and more. You can even link stickers to apps, and get rid of onscreen icons entirely. The home screen is yours, use it your way.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1381', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 27142, 25849, 1, 'htc-desire-10-pro-20mp-camera-64gb-4gb-ram-black.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'htc-desire-10-pro-20mp-camera-64gb-4gb-ram-black', '2017-09-28 10:30:46', '2017-09-28 10:30:46'),
(597, 1, 21, 61, 2, 31, NULL, 'HTC Desire Model  630(13MP Camera, 16GB, 2GB RAM) White', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Display Size:5.0 inches&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory:16GB, 2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Primary Camera:13 MP</li>\r\n	<li>Battery:Li-Ion 2200 mAh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Size:5.0 inches&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution:720 x 1280 pixels&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Type:Super LCD capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>CPU:Quad-core 1.6 GHz&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>GPU:Adreno 305</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory:16 GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:13 MP, f/2.4, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Video:1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:5 MP, f/2.8</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery &nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Removable Li-Ion 2200 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Meet the&nbsp;<strong>HTC Desire 630 Dual SIM</strong>. The smartphone that lets you stand out with unique micro splash styling, impressive audio and great cameras front and back. Go ahead &ndash; make an impact. What&#39;s more, stand out with the playfully retro, uniquely designed HTC Android smartphone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/a0fb9430282cbd06f5d57ab57a15f2a3.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/a0fb9430282cbd06f5d57ab57a15f2a3.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:300px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:995px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Unique Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Crafted with a micro splash finish applied over the handset, HTC Desire 630 dual sim has a unique style all its own. Featuring a soft-touch polycarbonate body and complementary lanyard strap to complete a personalised look.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/fb4175fc1d74627fc7a4034595047251.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/fb4175fc1d74627fc7a4034595047251.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:312px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:1035px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Awesome Images</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Talks of awesome photos front and back. Graduation walks, game-winning goals, roller coaster screams and more: when it comes to capturing magic moments, the HTC Desire 630 dual sim has you covered front and back. 13MP main camera takes great-looking photos and videos, and features a built-in Photo Editor function that lets you easily add effects such as Double Exposure to your photos.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/80be4d7185a0f35c1baeac4d7c322fd5.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/80be4d7185a0f35c1baeac4d7c322fd5.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:319px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:1061px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Amplified Audio</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There&rsquo;s no missing the distinctive sound quality of the HTC Desire 630 dual sim. Push play and you&rsquo;ll hear HTC BoomSound&trade; with Dolby Audio&trade; Profile take your music, film and games to the next level with clear vocal, deep bass and fine audio detail. Plus, with the included HTC Extreme Fidelity earphones, a superior audio experience comes standard.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/1440596b91deeafe90102ba00a03e58f.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/1440596b91deeafe90102ba00a03e58f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:369px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:796px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Personalise your Style</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Stand out from the crowd in more ways than ever. Each HTC Desire 630 dual sim comes with coordinated button highlights and a unique micro splash texture. Create your own custom phone theme based on your favourite photos with HTC Themes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/0240fb0a41dc24ae8dfb5b5968105d5f.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/0240fb0a41dc24ae8dfb5b5968105d5f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:342px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:1097px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1382', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 18533, 17650, 1, 'htc-desire-model-630-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-white.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'htc-desire-model-630-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-white', '2017-09-28 10:46:28', '2017-09-28 10:46:28');
