next level with clear vocal, deep bass and fine audio detail. Plus, with the included HTC Extreme Fidelity earphones, a superior audio experience comes standard.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/1440596b91deeafe90102ba00a03e58f.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/1440596b91deeafe90102ba00a03e58f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:369px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:796px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Personalise your Style</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Stand out from the crowd in more ways than ever. Each HTC Desire 630 dual sim comes with coordinated button highlights and a unique micro splash texture. Create your own custom phone theme based on your favourite photos with HTC Themes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/0240fb0a41dc24ae8dfb5b5968105d5f.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL0F88NGNAFAMZ/0240fb0a41dc24ae8dfb5b5968105d5f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:342px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:1097px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1383', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 19793, 18850, 1, 'htc-desire-model-630-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-grey.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'htc-desire-model-630-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-grey', '2017-09-28 15:58:22', '2017-09-28 15:58:22'),
(599, 1, 21, 61, 2, 31, NULL, 'HTC Desire Model 825 (13MP Camera, 16GB, 2GB RAM) White', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating System: OS: Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Size:&nbsp;5.5&rdquo;</li>\r\n	<li>Storage + Memory Card Support:&nbsp;16GB Storage</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 13 MP, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Screen&nbsp;Type: capacitive touchscreen</li>\r\n	<li>Processor : Quad-core 1.5&nbsp;GHz Cortex-A53 CPU</li>\r\n	<li>RAM : 2gb</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 720 x 1280 pixels (~267 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Type: Super LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.5 inches (~69.1% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Qualcomm Snapdragon 400</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-core 1.6 GHz Cortex-A7</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Adreno 305</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal: 16 GB, 2 GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 256 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 13 MP, f/2.2, 28mm, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5 MP, f/2.8, 1080p</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Ion 2700 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Enjoy the best features offered by this HTC phone that comes with a massive 5.5&rdquo; HD display driven by a warp-speed Octa-core processor. 13MP main camera paired with an UltraPixel front-facing camera for incredible pics from both sides, and easy editing tools to make your photos and videos completely personal.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://famouslogos.net/images/htc-logo.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:267px; margin:22px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:382px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Large Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>View it large with this phone&#39;s&nbsp;5.5&rdquo; Full HD screen displays that gives an incredibly detailed graphics and images. You are now able to watch your movies, music&nbsp;videos,&nbsp;play&nbsp;games&nbsp;and more in a large display. With an&nbsp;immersive HTC BoomSound&nbsp;that gives you a Dolby Audio&nbsp;Surround for epic audio you have to hear to believe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1JFFF0NAFAMZ/57a4d2d39c0bfbfa9894ec66fd2e35c1.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:370px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:556px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Clear Sound</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This Phone has an amazing design with a&nbsp;volume leveler and dynamic equalizer optimizes tone, provides clear movie dialogue and maintains a consistent volume so you won&rsquo;t have to manually adjust for clarity. You&rsquo;ll get jaw-dropping audio from both external speakers and headphones: the HTC Desire 825 dual sim brings everything to life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1IOU5WNAFAMZ/3fb91af8ad1203a33ec469bb3172858a_09bf08024df44586e384445c0de5535db9a5665d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:313px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Powerful Processor</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy stunning speed and power with the HTC Desire 825. Seamless multitasking, smooth video streaming and silky gaming are&nbsp;superfast powered by Android OS, v6.0 (Marshmallow) . Taking and sharing photos has never been easier with the all-new Android&nbsp;operating system.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" class="i0M7dzS7wXqw-HwpH6ZlgJaI irc_mut" src="https://encrypted-tbn2.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQymd0OklaiAlZ_oYp_143J0SLQSYk_J2V_jVe41XNeCseu1_Oo" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:699px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Clear Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Capture every special moment with HTC&nbsp;with its incredible photos from both sides of the HTC Desire 825 dual sim. Its 13MP main camera is loaded with our most advanced Optical Image Stabilization and a full range of easy-to-use editing tools.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1IOU5WNAFAMZ/00de10ab40b832be02d4592f34259414_79fab99ba5bcf263de9b448bdfe94a04beb3ba8c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:295px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1384', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 17576, 16739, 1, 'htc-desire-model-825-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-white.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'htc-desire-model-825-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-white', '2017-09-28 16:13:28', '2017-09-28 16:13:28'),
(600, 1, 21, 61, 1, 31, NULL, 'HTC Desire 828 (13MP Camera, 16GB, 2GB RAM) White', '<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">Dual SIM (nano SIM)&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">ROM: 32 GB </span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">&nbsp;RAM: 3 GB; microSDXCTM card slot, up to 2 TB</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">Bluetooth 4.1 Wi-Fi: 802.11 b/g/n (2.4 GHz) 3.5 mm stereo audio jack micro-USB 2.0 (5-pin) port, HTC BoomSoundTM with Dolby AudioTM</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">Main camera: 13 MP, auto-focus , BSI sensor, Optical Image Stabilisation (OIS), 1080p video recording Front camera: HTC UltraPixelTM, BSI sensor, f/2.0, 26.8 mm lens, 1080p video recording</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">5.5 inch, Full HD 1080p, </span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">Battery Capacity: 2800 mAh, </span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">CPU Speed: Octa-Core (8 x 1.5 GHz)</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(17, 17, 17)">, AndroidTM with HTC SenseTM</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.5 inches (~67.9% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 720 x 1280 pixels (~267 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Type: Super LCD2 capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Mediatek MT6753</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Octa-core 1.3 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal: 16 GB, 2 GB RAM - Desire 728</li>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 256 GB (dedicated slot)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 13 MP</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5 MP, f/2.8, 34mm,&nbsp;1080p@30fps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Po 2800 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>HTC Desire 728 Dual SIM</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The HTC Desire 728 Dual SIM is powered by 1.3GHz octa-core MediaTek MT6753 processor and it comes with 2GB of RAM. The phone packs 16GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 2000GB via a microSD card. As far as the cameras are concerned, the HTC Desire 728 Dual SIM packs a 13-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 8-megapixel front shooter for selfies. The HTC Desire 728 Dual SIM runs Android 5.1.1 and is powered by a 2800mAh non removable battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for htc logo" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1MVS1CNAFAMZ/e13489bffc72dbf98f7f0255c0a5d2d5.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:302px; margin:22px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:432px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Display and Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The HTC Desire 728 Dual flaunts a 5.5-inch HD multi touch display which is bound to provide you with rich graphics. It has a pixel density of 267ppi. It has a weight of 153g and is quite slim at just 7.8mm. The device appears in matte skin-bud body.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for htc 728" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1MVS1CNAFAMZ/a3f8ee8b779f82de39a6fa9ed82f1d54.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:715px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Powerful Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Under the hood, the HTC Desire 728 Dual sports a 1.3GHz octa-core processor sitting on MediaTek MT6753M chipset. It is paired with a 2GB RAM and Mali-T760 MP2 graphics unit to deliver a gliding performance. It sails on Google&#39;s latest Android v5.1.1 (Lollipop).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for Android v5.1.1" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1MVS1CNAFAMZ/f57937ef127f12e95ce73645a9887ee6.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:333px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:589px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Excellent Entertainment and Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The HTC Desire 728 Dual comes with a 13MP autofocus camera at the back with BSI sensor and an LED flash. It has features like panorama, HDR, face detection, geo-tagging and can record full HD videos at 30fps. It is accompanied by an 8MP snapper at the front to produce beautiful selfies. It houses an internal memory of 16GB which is further expandable up to a spectacular 2TB with the help of a microSD card. So the users can use this device as their external hard drives as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1MVS1CNAFAMZ/b0d09f6eb8e0434de38f05e25bbbb4a2.jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1MVS1CNAFAMZ/b0d09f6eb8e0434de38f05e25bbbb4a2.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:410px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:730px" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Connectivity</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The HTC Desire 728 Dual is fuelled by a 2,800mAh li-po battery. Connectivity features include 4G, 3G, Wi-Fi, GPS/A-GPS, Bluetooth v4.1, USB port, microUSB and GLONASS. As the name suggests, the phone has dual SIM support as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Related image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HT791EL1MVS1CNAFAMZ/03bf74284c9bba1da292de3f9c05a98d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:300px; margin:47px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:534px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1385', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 18019, 16999, 1, 'htc-desire-828-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-white.jpg', 'htc-desire-828-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-white-2.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'htc-desire-828-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-white', '2017-09-28 16:33:34', '2017-09-28 16:33:34'),
