width:450px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Efficiency</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With new features, a visual overhaul, and numerous under-the-hood improvements, Android&trade; 5.0 is more responsive and efficient, plus lighter on smartphone batteries, than previous releases. As a result, the Lenovo A1000 gives you a fast, smooth, and powerful Android experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1ABJ3GNAFAMZ/f62d779592adbdc88d9e011dc35c9aed.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Connectivity&nbsp;Speed</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As well as keeping you in the loop, the 3G-enabled A1000 lets you snap and share great moments - instantly. With HSPA+ connectivity and download speeds of 21 Mbps, your online social networks, videos, and music are just a click away.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Seamless Processing</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The A1000&#39;s 1.3GHz quad-core processor helps to make multitasking faster, enables the Android OS to run smoother, and delivers a more fluid gaming &amp; video experience.&nbsp;Finding your way around has never been easier than with the A1000. It includes satellite-controlled GPS to guide you accurately even when you don&rsquo;t have an Internet connection.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1ABJ3GNAFAMZ/ff66a4c61cec467d89392346c6e470c6.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Integrated&nbsp;Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The A1000&#39;s 5MP rear camera with LED flash captures sharp, clear photos and video. What&rsquo;s more, the front camera makes video chatting easy and fun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1ABJ3GNAFAMZ/e8d1c3f4682df75e192fe8864acabd80.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:253px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:450px" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Preloaded Apps</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Do more with preloaded apps like SHAREit with CLONEit, which lets you rapidly share files wirelessly across smartphone and other devices without network charges or a WiFi connection; and SYNCit, which lets you back up and restore contacts, SMS messages, and call logs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/kpjMgcnsFmWKcM7emHwNKLloxOxF4Yh3-MwgcOWXsTiooxyqF7RDLFiKVF4KPN2iig=w300" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1388', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 5249, 4999, 1, 'lenovo-model-a1000-5mp-camera-8gb1gb-ram-black.jpg', 'lenovo-model-a1000-5mp-camera-8gb1gb-ram-black-2.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-model-a1000-5mp-camera-8gb1gb-ram-black', '2017-09-30 06:38:15', '2017-09-30 06:38:15'),
