td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>- MP4/H.264 player<br />\r\n			- MP3/WAV/eAAC+/FLAC player<br />\r\n			- Photo/video editor<br />\r\n			- Document viewer</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="7" scope="row" style="text-align:left">BATTERY</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Non-removable Li-Po 3500 mAh battery</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Up to 543 h (3G)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Up to 34 h (2G) / Up to 27 h 30 min (3G)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<p>Lenovo K5 Note (K52e78) smartphone is powered by 1.8GHz octa-core MediaTek Helio P10 processor &nbsp;processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone has 32GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 128GB via a microSD card. Lenovo K5 Note packs a 13-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 8-megapixel front shooter for selfies. This Lenovo phone comes with a 5.50-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 1080 pixels by 1920 pixels.<img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1D5574NAFAMZ/8257142bc1d95c97711340e4d1159400.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:128px; margin:48px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:300px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Sleek and Stunning Design</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Lenovo K5 Note smartphone is designed to comfortably fit your hand,your routines and your taste. The user interface is refined to make it more intuitive than ever, and continued with a form that makes a statement with its simplicity. It measures 152.00 x 75.70 x 8.49 (height x width x thickness) and weighs 152.00 grams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1D5574NAFAMZ/29d2248d8c71c46d5fc54a8be1556e3a.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:491px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:873px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fast Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Lenovo K5 Note is powered by 1.8GHz octa-core MediaTek Helio P10 processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone packs 32GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 128GB via a microSD card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1D5574NAFAMZ/dfd9920144f03756c56ae9ea31447adb.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:420px; margin:36px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:630px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Clear Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The most shareable moments tend to be the hardest to capture. To help you get the shots you want, the Lenovo K5 Note packs a 13-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 8-megapixel front shooter for selfies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL1D5574NAFAMZ/215026dff66a10ab3c73c53f568c85d1.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:394px; margin:49px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:728px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fingerprint Sensor</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Adding a simple-yet-essential layer of protection, the built-in fingerprint reader helps to prevent unwanted access to your Vibe K5 Note and personal data.The fingerprint sensor is very fast and unlocks in 0.3 seconds. Moreover you can invoke different actions like taking an image, back button etc. using the built in fingerprint gestures.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Secure Fingerprint Sensor" src="http://www.lenovo.com/images/subseries/lenovo-smartphone-vibe-k5-note-finger-print-sensor-2.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:block; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" title="Secure Fingerprint Sensor" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Front and Rear Cameras</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A 13 MP auto-focus rear camera with LED flash lets you capture great photos and videos; while an 8 MP camera at the front can help make your selfies stand out from the crowd.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Cameras: 13 MP Rear, 8 MP Front" src="http://www.lenovo.com/images/ap/in/en/590x471/lenovo-smartphone-vibe-k5-note-front-rear-cameras-3.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:block; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" title="Cameras: 13 MP Rear, 8 MP Front" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1389', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 18899, 17999, 1, 'lenovo-k5-note-32gb-3gb-android-6-0-13mp-camera-silver.jpg', 'lenovo-k5-note-32gb-3gb-android-6-0-13mp-camera-silver-2.jpg', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-k5-note-32gb-3gb-android-6-0-13mp-camera-silver', '2017-09-30 06:48:18', '2017-09-30 06:48:18'),
