tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Adreno 505</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="5" scope="row" style="text-align:left">MEMORY</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>microSD, up to 128GB&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="4" scope="row" style="text-align:left">&nbsp;</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>utofocus, LED flash</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, HDR, panorama</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>1080p@30fps</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>8 MP</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="4" scope="row" style="text-align:left">SOUND</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Vibration; MP3, WAV ringtones</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Yes, with stereo speakers</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>- Dolby Atmos audio enhancement<br />\r\n			- Active noise cancellation with dedicated mic</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="9" scope="row" style="text-align:left">COMMS</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, hotspot</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>v4.2, A2DP, LE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Yes, with A-GPS</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>FM radio</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>microUSB v2.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="12" scope="row" style="text-align:left">FEATURES</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Fingerprint (rear-mounted), accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>HTML5</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>No</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>- MP4/H.264 player<br />\r\n			- MP3/WAV/eAAC+/FLAC player<br />\r\n			- Photo/video editor<br />\r\n			- Document viewer</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="7" scope="row" style="text-align:left">BATTERY</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Non-removable Li-Po 4000 mAh battery</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Up to 649 h (3G)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Up to 50 h (2G) / Up to 33 h (3G)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<p>Lenovo K6 Note is one of the best smartphones that has been produced in the market to ensure you get the best outstanding performance. Bursting with the latest features that bespoke to you, K6 Note is more than just a phone as it opens the world of endless possibility. It is super-fast, stylish and these are just but a few privileges that you will be indulging into when you own one of these gadget.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="Image result for lenovo" src="http://www.lenovo.com/defense/LenovoLockup-POS-Color.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Vibrant Full HD Screen</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Lenovo&nbsp;K6 Note brings your photos, videos, and online world to life. Delivering everything in stunning, crystal clear detail, the 13.97cm (5.5) Full HD display has in-plane switching technology, enabling you to enjoy a richer range of colors and wider viewing angles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Lenovo Smartphone Vibe K6 Note Camera Feature" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL125UVGNAFAMZ/d27afe0dd061fb740e13fd8c1e0d1108.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:408px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:507px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Exceptional Cameras</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Incredible shots come as standard with the Lenovo K6 Note smartphone. Its 16 MP fast-focusing rear camera boasts dual CCT (Colour Correlated Temperature) flash technology, which helps avoid over-exposed or washed-out photos. And if you&#39;re looking for sharp, picture-perfect selfies, you&#39;ll simply love the 8 MP camera in the front.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="Image result for Lenovo K6 Note camera" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL125UVGNAFAMZ/cd442bfec03d021975c1bfad0fca6ffa.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:590px" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fingerprint Security</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Why struggle to remember a password, when you can just log in with a swipe of your finger? As well as saving you time, the Lenovo&nbsp;K6 Note&#39;s advanced fingerprint reader ensures that only you can access your smartphone. The full-metal unibody design of the Lenovo&nbsp;K Note looks great, feels great. What&#39;s more, with Dolby Atmos&reg; audio enhancement, it also elevates your music and movies to another level.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Lenovo Smartphone Vibe K6 Note Color Options Feature" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL125UVGNAFAMZ/bee8bfb9cc37d101d723edb04d646625.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:417px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:540px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>High Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Powerful octa-core processing and the latest Android&trade; operating system (6.0, Marshmallow) combine perfectly to give you smooth, fast performance. In addition, the Lenovo&nbsp;K6 Note boasts a large 4,000 mAh battery,&nbsp;with enough juice to keep you going through every challenge of the day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for 6.0, Marshmallow" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL125UVGNAFAMZ/ae2b26a53d9861e1698f6c8b8ca90d81.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:250px; margin:72px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1390', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 21587, 20559, 1, 'lenovo-k6-note-16mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-5-5-inches-black.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-k6-note-16mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-5-5-inches-black', '2017-09-30 07:00:20', '2017-09-30 07:00:20');
