(605, 1, 21, 61, 2, 19, NULL, ' Lenovo Vibe P1  (13MP Camera 2GB RAM 32GB , 5.5 Inches) Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen size :<strong>&nbsp;</strong>5.5 Inches</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 13MP Rear, 5MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 32GB ROM, 2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>SIM: Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>DISPLAY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>IPS capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors<br />\r\n5.5 inches (~72.1% screen-to-body ratio)<br />\r\n1080 x 1920 pixels (~401 ppi pixel density)<br />\r\nYes, up to 10 fingers<br />\r\nCorning Gorilla Glass 3</p>\r\n\r\n<p>BODY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>152.9 x 75.6 x 9.9 mm (6.02 x 2.98 x 0.39 in)<br />\r\n189 g (6.67 oz)<br />\r\nDual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PLATFORM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Android OS, v5.1 (Lollipop)<br />\r\nQualcomm MSM8939 Snapdragon 615<br />\r\nOcta-core (4x1.5 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; 4x1.1 GHz Cortex-A53)<br />\r\nAdreno 405</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MEMORY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>microSD, up to 128 GB (dedicated slot)<br />\r\n32 GB, 2 GB RAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>CAMERA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13 MP, f/2.2, phase detection autofocus, dual-LED (dual tone) flash<br />\r\nGeo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, HDR, panorama<br />\r\n1080p@30fps<br />\r\n5 MP<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBATTERY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Non-removable Li-Po 5000 mAh battery<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>The Lenovo Vibe P1</strong><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;Dual SIM smartphone is meticulously built to give you both luxury and smooth functionality. Available in a pretty silver color and with a thickness of merely 9.9mm, this phone is quite the eye catcher. These dimensions ensure that your phone is not only a pretty face but is also comfortable to use and easy to port. This phone also gives you amazing connectivity. It supports the 4G LTE network that gives you blistering Internet speeds. It powers your tasks efficiently and also enables smooth multitasking with the help of the 2GB RAM. The processor draws power efficiently from the potent&nbsp;</span>5000mAh Lithium Polymer<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">, which enables the smartphone to offer a whopping 44 hours of talk time while on the 3G network. Carry this smartphone with you wherever you go, without the fear of running out of charge halfway through the day.</span><br />\r\n<img alt="aeProduct.getSubject()" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0DX51SNAFAMZ/f00bc5225ad1397cedbc883f8664e33f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:block; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; height:625px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:900px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="aeProduct.getSubject()" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0DX51SNAFAMZ/d9e90f8340ca4e8e1aed952730b4f239.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:block; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; height:799px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:900px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="aeProduct.getSubject()" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0DX51SNAFAMZ/44b25ad539e087ab0c96de364e586c6f.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:block; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; height:655px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:900px" /><br />\r\n<img alt="aeProduct.getSubject()" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0DX51SNAFAMZ/92a506a0ccdfdec41c500d1027af5acd.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display