e cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; outline:none; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="9" scope="row" style="text-align:left">COMMS</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, hotspot</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>v4.2, A2DP, LE</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Yes, with A-GPS</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>FM radio</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>microUSB v2.0</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; outline:none; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="12" scope="row" style="text-align:left">FEATURES</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Fingerprint (rear-mounted), accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>SMS(threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>HTML5</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>No</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>- MP4/H.264 player<br />\r\n			- MP3/WAV/eAAC+/FLAC player<br />\r\n			- Photo/video editor<br />\r\n			- Document viewer</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<table cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(37, 39, 42); font-family:proxima-nova-n9,proxima-nova,sans-serif; font-size:12.6px; outline:none; width:484.444px">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="7" scope="row" style="text-align:left">BATTERY</th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Non-removable Li-Po 4000 mAh battery</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Up to 649 h (3G)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Up to 50 h (2G) / Up to 33 h (3G)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '<p>Lenovo K6 Note is one of the best smartphones that has been produced in the market to ensure you get the best outstanding performance. Bursting with the latest features that bespoke to you, K6 Note is more than just a phone as it opens the world of endless possibility. It is super-fast, stylish and these are just but a few privileges that you will be indulging into when you own one of these gadget.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="Image result for lenovo" src="http://www.lenovo.com/defense/LenovoLockup-POS-Color.png" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Vibrant Full HD Screen</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Lenovo&nbsp;K6 Note brings your photos, videos, and online world to life. Delivering everything in stunning, crystal clear detail, the 13.97cm (5.5) Full HD display has in-plane switching technology, enabling you to enjoy a richer range of colors and wider viewing angles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Lenovo Smartphone Vibe K6 Note Camera Feature" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL125UVGNAFAMZ/d27afe0dd061fb740e13fd8c1e0d1108.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:408px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:507px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Exceptional Cameras</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Incredible shots come as standard with the Lenovo K6 Note smartphone. Its 16 MP fast-focusing rear camera boasts dual CCT (Colour Correlated Temperature) flash technology, which helps avoid over-exposed or washed-out photos. And if you&#39;re looking for sharp, picture-perfect selfies, you&#39;ll simply love the 8 MP camera in the front.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="Image result for Lenovo K6 Note camera" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL125UVGNAFAMZ/cd442bfec03d021975c1bfad0fca6ffa.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:393px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:590px" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fingerprint Security</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Why struggle to remember a password, when you can just log in with a swipe of your finger? As well as saving you time, the Lenovo&nbsp;K6 Note&#39;s advanced fingerprint reader ensures that only you can access your smartphone. The full-metal unibody design of the Lenovo&nbsp;K Note looks great, feels great. What&#39;s more, with Dolby Atmos&reg; audio enhancement, it also elevates your music and movies to another level.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Lenovo Smartphone Vibe K6 Note Color Options Feature" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL125UVGNAFAMZ/bee8bfb9cc37d101d723edb04d646625.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:417px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:540px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>High Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Powerful octa-core processing and the latest Android&trade; operating system (6.0, Marshmallow) combine perfectly to give you smooth, fast performance. In addition, the Lenovo&nbsp;K6 Note boasts a large 4,000 mAh battery,&nbsp;with enough juice to keep you going through every challenge of the day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for 6.0, Marshmallow" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL125UVGNAFAMZ/ae2b26a53d9861e1698f6c8b8ca90d81.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:250px; margin:72px auto 30px; max-width:710px; outline:none; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1392', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 16631, 15839, 1, 'lenovo-k6-note-16mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-5-5-inches-white.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-k6-note-16mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-5-5-inches-white', '2017-09-30 07:12:16', '2017-09-30 07:12:16'),
(607, 1, 21, 61, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo Vibe S1  (13MP Camera,  32GB, 3GB RAM) Black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5-inch IPS LCD display</li>\r\n	<li>Android OS, v5.0 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal&nbsp;Storege :32 GB</li>\r\n	<li>RAM : 3 GB&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>13MP Rear, 8MP Front Camera</li>\r\n	<li>Dual SIM</li>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Po 2420 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.0 inches (~67.9% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels (~441 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch: Yes, up to 5 fingers</li>\r\n	<li>Protection: Corning Gorilla Glass 3</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.0 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: Mediatek MT6752</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Octa-core 1.7 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>GPU: Mali-T760MP2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 128 GB (uses SIM 2 slot)</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 32 GB, 3 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 13 MP</li>\r\n	<li>Video: Yes</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 8 MP + 2 MP (DOF)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Po 2420 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>VIBE S1 is designed for the today millennial who want the best of design and performance in everything that they need. VIBE S1 brings the perfect amalgamation between Beauty and Performance in a Smartphone. It features the World&rsquo;s first Dual Front camera to unleash the creativity within you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL05XP20NAFAMZ/217f4eee73b8475010d7676504eda6c2.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:289px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:510px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Details Get Attention</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The VIBE S1 is the ultimate showstopper. That&rsquo;s because, the front Gorilla Glass 3 disperses reflections in such a manner that the images will always appear softer and richer. While an 8 -step engineering process has gone into creating the VIBE S1&rsquo;s impeccable curved-glass, rear-panel and premium rounded metal frame. At just 131 grams, this sleek smartphone also feels as light as a feather.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL05XP20NAFAMZ/36f55bf60409c19def8d93e64db5af9c.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:234px; margin:89px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:462px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Powerhouse Of Performance</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The VIBE S1 has a 64-Bit 1.7 Ghz Octa-Core processor, 400Mhz Mali GPU, 3GB RAM, that makes it ideal even for high-end games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL05XP20NAFAMZ/825aac520dfcbd05bf64c235aca016f0.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:305px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:444px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>First-Of-Its-Kind With Twice The Fun</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Lenovo VIBE S1 smartphone makes you the center of attention. It&rsquo;s the world&rsquo;s first Dual selfie camera with not 1, but 2 selfie cameras to focus on you. An 8MP F2.2 camera with BSI sensor to give you superb, crisp image quality and a 2MP camera to analyze depth of field. This gives you unprecedented creative options, including One-touch Refocus and Background Swap. What&#39;s more, its multiple shooting modes give you maximum flexibility, gesture &amp; voice controls let you steady your hand, and anti-distortion components balance selfies perfectly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also capture sensational images in low light with the 13 megapixel F2.2 rear camera that has a low-light BSI sensor and phase detection autofocus (PDAF), which dramatically increases focusing speeds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL05XP20NAFAMZ/263a455a9b189fa5b211d55b28f49160.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:257px; margin:40px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:462px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Android&trade; 5.0 Lollipop</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Android&trade; Lollipop operating system with VIBE UI includes a host of new features, a visual overhaul and numerous under-the-hood improvements to make it faster, more efficient and lighter on your battery. It also works perfectly with all your favorite Google apps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL05XP20NAFAMZ/9ac55e173fd7dad4b60c874770404959.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:288px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:474px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1393', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 18899, 17999, 1, 'lenovo-vibe-s1-13mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-blue.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-vibe-s1-13mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-black', '2017-09-30 12:02:05', '2017-09-30 12:02:05'),
(608, 1, 21, 61, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo Moto (16MP Camera 4GB RAM 32GB ) Silver', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android Marshmallow 6</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: MediaTek Helio P15 64-bit</li>\r\n	<li>4 GB RAM - 32 GB ROM - Expandable Upto 128 GB</li>\r\n	<li>5.5 inch Full HD Display</li>\r\n	<li>16MP Rear Camera - 8MP Front Camera</li>\r\n	<li>3050 mAh Li-Polymer Battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.5 inches</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: Full HD 1080 x 1920 pixels</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android Marshmallow 6</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset: MediaTek Helio P15 64-bit</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Octa-core 2.2 GHz&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 128 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 32GB, 4GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 16 MP</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 8 MP</li>\r\n	<li>Flash: LED\r\n	<p><strong>Battery&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Po 3050 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Meet the all-new Moto M. Crafted in all-metal, this stylish smartphone will keep you up-to-date in fashion and technology. Powered by MTK Helio P15 64-bit Processor and 3050 battery, the Moto M keeps you going all day long.&nbsp;Stylishly designed in all metal, the Moto M is all you need to stay in vogue. Equipped with a blazing-fast processor and 3 GB RAM, this smartphone enhances your performance and ensures faster app loading and responsiveness.</span><br />\r\n<strong>Power Meets Style</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with a 7.85 mm thin full-metal unibody design and featuring a 13.97 cm Full HD display, the Moto M looks fresh and elegant.&nbsp;The Moto M&rsquo;s sharp, unusual design makes it one of the best-looking smartphones around.&nbsp;Watch movies while traveling, listen to music, play games, and do much more without worrying about running out of charge as this Moto M is powered by a 3050 mAh battery. This phone also comes with a 10W rapid charger which charges your phone faster than you think.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL022ZM4NAFAMZ/dd73baef245c4a783bb15efda376868d.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; color:rgb(96, 96, 96); display:block; font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /><strong>Blazing-fast Performance</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Powered by 2.2 GHz octa-core CPU and 3 GB RAM, this Moto M allows you to play games, stream videos and multitask at lightning speed. Store all that you want, from movies to music, videos to documents, on this phone&#39;s 32 GB storage. If you want to store an entire season of your favourite TV show, you can do so by inserting a microSD card of up to 128 GB.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL022ZM4NAFAMZ/0ad7a7b9c0760c147b11bc231cf88d40.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Advanced Cameras</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Click pictures of eye-pleasing and mouth-watering food you eat, places you visit and the scenic beauty of the hill station you&#39;re holidaying in using the Moto M&#39;s 16 MP PDAF rear camera. With a dynamic Correlated Color Temperature (CCT) dual LED flash, you can also capture beautiful pictures in low lighting as well. With its 8 MP front camera, you can click selfies and also beautify them using the Beautification mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL022ZM4NAFAMZ/dc8aa417d00f3ae4f9b2ff631be7499b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Advanced audio that makes your music come alive</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The rear speaker on the Moto M features patented Dolby Atmos technology, which allows sound to move in three-dimensional space, not just in channels. Your music and movies will come to life with amazing clarity, richness, power, and depth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL022ZM4NAFAMZ/f1852a15abc90dbcebcc290bd537858b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fingerprint Sensor</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let go of complicated pins and passwords as this Moto M comes with a ultra-fast fingerprint sensor. Unlock your phone while on the go with just a touch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="denied:data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP//yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /><img alt="Image result for one-touch, totally secure, Moto M" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL022ZM4NAFAMZ/e626d2c3c404d6ffa1962634b96eda20.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; letter-spacing:-0.2px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Water Protection</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t panic if there are accidental splashes or spills of water as this smartphone offers protection from water, thanks to its water-repellent nano-coating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for one-touch, totally secure, Moto M" src="http://www.motorola.in/sites/default/files/styles/tiles_template_1_-_desktop_1x/public/library/in/products/moto-m/moto-m-featex-splashproof-d-row.jpg?itok=jn3hytHC&amp;timestamp=1481745498" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1394', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 24149, 22999, 1, 'lenovo-moto-16mp-camera-4gb-ram-32gb-silver.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-moto-16mp-camera-4gb-ram-32gb-silver', '2017-09-30 13:47:25', '2017-09-30 13:47:25'),
