ortion components balance selfies perfectly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can also capture sensational images in low light with the 13 megapixel F2.2 rear camera that has a low-light BSI sensor and phase detection autofocus (PDAF), which dramatically increases focusing speeds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL05XP20NAFAMZ/263a455a9b189fa5b211d55b28f49160.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:257px; margin:40px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:462px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Android&trade; 5.0 Lollipop</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Android&trade; Lollipop operating system with VIBE UI includes a host of new features, a visual overhaul and numerous under-the-hood improvements to make it faster, more efficient and lighter on your battery. It also works perfectly with all your favorite Google apps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL05XP20NAFAMZ/9ac55e173fd7dad4b60c874770404959.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:288px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:474px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1396', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 18899, 17999, 1, 'lenovo-vibe-s1-13mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-white.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-vibe-s1-13mp-camera-32gb-3gb-ram-white', '2017-09-30 14:04:11', '2017-09-30 14:04:11'),
