(612, 1, 21, 61, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo Model A6010 (8GB, 1GB RAM, 8MP Camera, Dual SIM)Black', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5-inch IPS LCD display</li>\r\n	<li>Android OS, v5.0 (Lollipop), Octa-core 1.7 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n	<li>Internal:&nbsp; 8GB, 1&nbsp;GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li><span style="color:rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">Primary Camera: 8MP, autofocus, LED flash</span></li>\r\n	<li>Dual SIM, 4G</li>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Po 2300&nbsp;mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type:IPS capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size:5.0 inches (~69.8% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution:720 x 1280 pixels (~294 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS:Android OS, v5.0 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset:Qualcomm MSM8916 Snapdragon 410</li>\r\n	<li>CPU:Quad-core 1.2 GHz Cortex-A53</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internal Memory:8 GB</li>\r\n	<li>1 GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary:8 MP, f/2.5, autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features: Geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;720p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:2 MP, f/2.3</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Removable Li-Po 2300 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Enjoy the high quality of the<strong>&nbsp;Lenovo A6010</strong>&nbsp;Smartphone! For smooth, responsive system performance that won&#39;t break the bank, the A6010 &nbsp;is superb. Boasting Qualcomm MSM8916 Snapdragon 410 processor, it has the power to play music &amp; video, run apps &amp; games, and more - all without skipping a beat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL074MQGNAFAMZ/55871ff6b8a607d7e7b64dc87177bb57.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:412px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:412px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Brilliant 12.7cm (5) HD Display</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Rich in color and sharp in resolution, the Lenovo A6010 smartphone&#39;s 12.7cm (5) HD screen is made for multimedia. It ensures that your video, games, and images all appear clearer and more vivid. Plus, with in-plane switching (IPS) offering nearly 180&deg; of wide-angle viewing, the A6010&#39;s big, bright display is perfect for sharing with a crowd of friends.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL074MQGNAFAMZ/9522d948c49ad44013b712bc90cbe9d5.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:326px; margin:10px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:581px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Fast &amp; Speedy Performance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The Qualcomm Snapdragon Processors not only manages your mobile device&#39;s features, they improve them! Snapdragon is designed to enhance your mobile experience in every way. Enjoy improved connectivity (WiFi, 4G and 4G LTE and clearer calls), enhanced power and efficiency. You&#39;ll enjoy enhanced multimedia features thanks to the advanced camera features of a Snapdragon processor and realistic 3D graphics for gaming.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL074MQGNAFAMZ/dd984b093967ceb7bed196c584b77748.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:335px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:596px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Integrated Cameras</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The A6010&#39;s 8MP auto-focus camera with LED flash captures sharp, clear photos and video. What&rsquo;s more, the front camera makes video chatting easy and fun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL074MQGNAFAMZ/06890d9c39875d1ad8dcc0802c6cd0e2.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:412px; margin:0px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:427px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Enhanced Audio</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether it&#39;s music, movies, or games, the A6010 delivers an exceptional audio experience through its twin speakers or your headphones. In addition, with Dolby Digital Plus&trade; and enhanced volume levels, everything sounds richer, deeper, and more realistic - even in loud and busy environments. Perfect for headphone junkies and music lovers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL074MQGNAFAMZ/8210c77171753e7dd945456ca902f887.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:360px; margin:26px auto 30px; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:480px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Dual SIM</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Two phone numbers in one smartphone can help keep business and pleasure separate. This dual-SIM feature also enables you to choose different data plans to save money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Lenovo A6000 Smartphone" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/LE842EL0TC784NAFAMZ/375a71a6d3821a45f9aca4b9474a568b_945ff4b9f7fb30ee74888126acce987fed943750.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:530px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:271px" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1398', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 9449, 8999, 1, 'lenovo-model-a6010-8gb-1gb-ram-8mp-camera-dual-sim-black.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'lenovo-model-a6010-8gb-1gb-ram-8mp-camera-dual-sim-black', '2017-09-30 15:16:43', '2017-09-30 15:16:43'),
