(614, 1, 21, 61, 2, 19, NULL, 'Lenovo Vibe P1 (13MP Camera, 2GB RAM,16GB, Dual SIM)Gold', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.5 inches (~72.5% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels (~401 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset:&nbsp; Qualcomm Octa Core 1.5GHz</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 13MP Rear, 5MP Front</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 16GB ROM, 2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>SIM: Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Type: LTPS IPS LCD capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Size: 5.5 inches (~72.5% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution: 1080 x 1920 pixels (~401 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li>Multitouch</li>\r\n	<li>Screen Protection: Gorilla Glass 3</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Platform</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS: Android OS, v5.1 (Lollipop)</li>\r\n	<li>Chipset:&nbsp; Qualcomm Octa Core 1.5GHz</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Card slot: microSD, up to 128 GB</li>\r\n	<li>Internal: 16GB, 2GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary: 13 MP, f/2.2, phase detection autofocus.</li>\r\n	<li>Video:&nbsp;1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary: 5 MP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Non-removable Li-Po 5000mAh Battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>The Lenovo Vibe P1</strong><span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">&nbsp;Dual SIM smartphone is meticulously built to give you both luxury and smooth functionality. Available in a pretty silver color and with a thickness of merely 9.9mm, this phone is quite the eye catcher. These dimensions ensure that your phone 