s like; touch focus, face/smile detection, geo-tagging, and HDR panorama for photos. The secondary camera has 5&nbsp;MP.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Sound Alert</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vibration, Proprietaryringtone and lound speaker can be helps in sound alert with this smartphone. A jack pin 3.5 is also available for earphones active noise cancellation with mic.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Communication features</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>WLAN, Bluetooth GPS, NFC and USB are both available with this Apple Iphone 6 Plus to make your data transfer offer different platforms much easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Other great features</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Sonsors ; Fingersprint sensor to control access for your phone&rsquo;s data and keep it secure as possible. Accelerometer, gyro, proximity, compass and barometer are both found on this iphone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Message; iMessage, Threated SMS, MMS Email and Push Email</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Uses Safari browser as the default but has an option of using other&nbsp; browser as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Siri natural language commands and dictation features for better searches. Icloud services also provided with this phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Battery</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>A Non-removable Li-Po 2915 mAh battery is available with Apple iPhone 6 Plus.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Colors</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Apple iPhone 6 Plus is available in Silver, Gold and Space Gray.</p>\r\n', '<p><strong>IPhone 6S - 4.7 inch 4G Refurbished Smartphone iOS 9 2GB/128GB Touch Focus EU - Rose Gold</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note:<br />\r\n1.The stated ROM amount shows the maximum available ROM with nothing installed. However, the Android OS and pre-installed software from the manufacturer will occupy some of this ROM. The available ROM on the device will therefore be slightly less than the ROM listed.<br />\r\n2.During the six months warranty,for the damages caused by customers, return freight charges,second-send freight charges and parts charges are paid by customers while repaire charges is free for customers<br />\r\nFor other damages caused by the quality itself,return freight ,second-send freight and parts are charged by the sellers.<br />\r\n3.STK(SIM Tool Kit): No</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="" src="http://pdm.gw-ec.com/uploads/ebay/2016/201611/20161130/heditor/201611301513598282.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://pdm.gw-ec.com/uploads/ebay/2016/201611/20161130/heditor/201611301513596521.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /><img alt="" src="http://pdm.gw-ec.com/uploads/ebay/2016/201611/20161130/heditor/201611301514279261.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://pdm.gw-ec.com/uploads/ebay/2016/201611/20161130/heditor/201611301514278684.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /><br />\r\n<img alt="" src="http://pdm.gw-ec.com/uploads/ebay/2016/201611/20161130/heditor/201611301514279589.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /><img alt="" src="http://pdm.gw-ec.com/uploads/ebay/2016/201611/20161130/heditor/201611301515117990.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1407', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 75600, 72000, 1, 'apple-iphone-6s-128gb-1gb-ram-8mp-camera.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'apple-iphone-6s-128gb-1gb-ram-8mp-camera', '2017-09-30 22:25:35', '2017-09-30 22:25:35'),
