(635, 6, NULL, NULL, 2, 15, NULL, 'HP Envy x360  (1TB ,16GB RAM)Intel Core i7 7th Gen', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display Size: 15.6 Inches</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 16GB RAM,1TB</li>\r\n	<li>Processor:&nbsp;Intel Core i7 Gen</li>\r\n	<li>Graphics Card: Intel&reg; HD Graphics 620&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>OS: Windows 10</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 3-cell, 57.8 Wh Li-ion</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>15.6 Inches&nbsp;<span style="color:rgb(96, 96, 96); font-family:roboto,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size:12px">FHD UWVA BrightView</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>16GB LPDDR3-1600 SDRAM (onboard)</li>\r\n	<li>Hard drive:&nbsp;1TB GB PCIe&reg; NVMe&trade; &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>System</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Operating system:&nbsp;Windows 10&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Processor:&nbsp;Intel&reg; Core&trade; i7-7500U (2.7 GHz, up to 3.5 GHz, 4 MB cache, 2 cores)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Graphics: Intel&reg; HD Graphics 620 (up to 4.07 GB)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wireless technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>802.11ac (2x2) and Bluetooth&reg; 4.2 combo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>External I/O Ports</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2 USB 3.1 Gen 2 (Type-C&trade;, HP USB Boost, Thunderbolt); 1 USB 3.1 Gen 1 (HP Sleep and Charge); 1 headphone/microphone combo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Other Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Webcam:&nbsp;HP TrueVision FHD IR Camera with dual array digital microphone [8]</li>\r\n	<li>Audio:&nbsp;Bang &amp; Olufsen; Quad speakers</li>\r\n	<li>Special features:&nbsp;Supports active stylus compliant with Microsoft Ink</li>\r\n	<li>Sensors:&nbsp;Accelerometer; Gyroscope; eCompass</li>\r\n	<li>Pointing device:&nbsp;HP Imagepad with multi-touch gesture support</li>\r\n	<li>Keyboard:&nbsp;Full-size island-style backlit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery &amp; Power</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Power supply:&nbsp;45 W AC power adapter</li>\r\n	<li>Battery:&nbsp;3-cell, 57.8 Wh Li-ion</li>\r\n	<li>Battery life:&nbsp;Up to 16 hours and 15 minutes&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Video Playback Battery Life:&nbsp;Up to 10 hours and 45 minutes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Meticulously crafted from the inside out, the Envy x360 redefines what you expect from technology. With four unique modes, and over 8 million pixels on the thinnest convertible PC we&rsquo;ve ever made, it&rsquo;s a new perspective on what you and your laptop can do.&nbsp;Enjoy a seamless transition from notebook to tablet and everything in between, with an elegantly designed 360&deg; hinge that lets this convertible PC look great in every position.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for HP logo jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0WXV4KNAFAMZ/ba47aea67550ffd9d839002589e0492b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Four Modes Engineered to Amaze</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Our thinnest x360 yet is irresistibly sleek At 2.89 lbs. and 13.9mm thin, and impressively versatile with a 360&deg; hinge and four unique modes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for HP Spectre 13t-x360" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0WXV4KNAFAMZ/fcd8fd539a118a4ba06a936b288eb38a.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Astounding Power. Exceptional Endurance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Prepare to accomplish more than you ever thought possible with up to 16 hours of battery life and HP Fast Charge. Get unrivaled all-day performance with a lightning-fast Intel&reg; Core&trade; processor.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="Image result for HP Spectre x360 jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0WXV4KNAFAMZ/9a891c979a2f4229a963b15f61dae084.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Exhilarate Your Creative Side</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>View and edit high resolution photos on a 4K display with 8 million pixels of detail, or sketch and draw with your active pen and Windows Ink.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for HP Spectre x360 jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0WXV4KNAFAMZ/ced08f91b3b06acc5ebd1c10ecf8fc64.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:367px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Enticing Audio</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With quad HP Speakers, HP Audio Boost, and custom tuning by the experts at Bang &amp; Olufsen, entertainment comes to life with sound you can feel. Awaken your senses with PC audio perfection.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1429', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 83999, 79999, 1, 'hp-envy-x360-1tb-16gb-ram-intel-core-i7-7th-gen.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'hp-envy-x360-1tb-16gb-ram-intel-core-i7-7th-gen', '2017-10-03 16:36:15', '2017-10-03 16:36:15'),
