 Get unrivaled all-day performance with a lightning-fast Intel&reg; Core&trade; processor.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="Image result for HP Spectre x360 jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0HECDONAFAMZ/47695674bf4c7a5ba08f1a35788ed18a.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Exhilarate Your Creative Side</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>View and edit high resolution photos on a 4K display with 8 million pixels of detail, or sketch and draw with your active pen and Windows Ink.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for HP Spectre x360 jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0HECDONAFAMZ/ced08f91b3b06acc5ebd1c10ecf8fc64.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; height:367px; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle; width:500px" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Enticing Audio</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>With quad HP Speakers, HP Audio Boost, and custom tuning by the experts at Bang &amp; Olufsen, entertainment comes to life with sound you can feel. Awaken your senses with PC audio perfection.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><img alt="Image result for HP Spectre x360 jpg" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL0HECDONAFAMZ/a09c46c012ce95591258eb51ba3df57b.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></h2>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1430', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 212099, 201999, 1, 'hp-spectre-13t-x360-512gb-16gb-ram-touch-screen-intel-core-i7-gen.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'hp-spectre-13t-x360-512gb-16gb-ram-touch-screen-intel-core-i7-gen', '2017-10-03 16:42:35', '2017-10-03 16:42:35'),
(637, 6, NULL, NULL, 2, 15, NULL, 'HP Envy 24  (Core i5 , 8gb RAM, 1TB HDD, 23.8 Inches, Touchscreen', '<p>Key Features</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>10-point touch-enabled 23.8&rdquo; IPS Full HD LED backlit edge-to-edge display (1920x1080)</li>\r\n	<li>8GB PC3-12800 DDR3L-1600 SDRAM memory</li>\r\n	<li>1TB 5400RPM Serial ATA hard drive</li>\r\n	<li>6th generation Intel Core i5-6400T Quad-Core processor (2.20GHz)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Technicolor Color Certified Display</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Specifications</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Intel HD Graphics 530 with Up to 4043MB Total Available Graphics Memory</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless chiclet-style keyboard and optical mouse&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Gigabit (10/100/1000) Ethernet Network&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Bang &amp; Olufsen State-of-the-art Quad-speaker sound&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless LAN 802.11a/b/g/n/ac and Bluetooth 4.0&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>HP 3-in-1 Media Card Reader&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>HDMI Out, HDMI In</li>\r\n	<li>Rear I/O: 2 USB 3.0, 2 USB 2.0, Bottom: 2 USB 3.0</li>\r\n	<li>720p HD low-light fixed-focus front-facing webcam with dual microphone array</li>\r\n	<li>Headphone/Microphone Combo jack</li>\r\n	<li>Tilt/Stand Design: Tilt Angle: -5 to 35 degrees</li>\r\n	<li>Windows 10 Home&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>ENERGY STAR certified&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Mercury-free display backlights&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>No DVD Drive Included on this model&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>A work of art&nbsp;<br />\r\nat any angle.</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>We crafted the HP ENVY All-in-One to make a statement. It&#39;s not just a computer &ndash; it&#39;s a work of art. From the artfully inspired stand to the dazzling 4K screen, it&#39;ll be your new conversation piece.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>A design icon</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Head-turning design inspired by the lines and curves of the modern movement. Sleek and slim, featuring beautifully refined edges.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a id="Gallery_Image_1" name="Gallery_Image_1"><img alt="gallery image 1" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL07LBCONAFAMZ/5b0702d66f2a4a0803d859d4f3e069f9.jpg" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a id="Gallery_Image_2" name="Gallery_Image_2"><img alt="gallery image 2" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL07LBCONAFAMZ/b79ebc1397cc9f4205f95761ae65f5f0.jpg" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a id="Gallery_Image_3" name="Gallery_Image_3"><img alt="gallery image 3" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL07LBCONAFAMZ/4eb27d3222a7dd3132a0731c3c02f5a6.jpg" style="border-style:initial; border-width:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><a id="Gallery_Image_3" name="Gallery_Image_3"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Art imitates life</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The first All-in-One PC to be Technicolor Color Certified, for true-to-life color.&nbsp;And with up to 4K resolution, your content will come alive like never before.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for hp envy 23.8 all in one" src="http://www.computer3g.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/HP-ENVY-27-p021-All-in-One-Computer.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Masterful performance</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With a 6th generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; processor, up to 16GB of RAM, and AMD R7 or R9 graphics, you&#39;ll have more than enough power for everything you do.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="Image result for hp envy 23.8 all in one" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/HP246EL07LBCONAFAMZ/2b04b1a333aa87420d0248563711b252.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>An exceptionally rich audio experience</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>State-of-the-art Audio by Bang &amp; Olufsen transforms your display into a soundstage where entertainment comes alive with sound you can feel. Designed for true audio perfection on a display.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Finely tuned audio</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Advanced audio processing enhances your sound. The result is a totally refined, completely immersive audio experience. With sound this lifelike and nuanced, you might just forget you&rsquo;re listening to a recording.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>High fidelity design</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We&rsquo;ve cherry-picked only the best components to make the ENVY All-in-One a musical masterpiece. With quad speakers, including two tweeters, this machine was carefully designed for dynamic, vivid sound.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>The Bang &amp; Olufsen experience</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>As a leader in the field of high-quality audio equipment, Bang &amp; Olufsen knows what it takes to make every note of your music ring true. So after extensive testing by our own engineers, we ship product samples to Denmark, where Bang &amp; Olufsen&rsquo;s Tonmeister ensures our work complies with their sound philosophy and standards.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1431', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 89249, 84999, 1, 'hp-envy-24-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-23-8-inches-touchscreen.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'hp-envy-24-core-i5-8gb-ram-1tb-hdd-23-8-inches-touchscreen', '2017-10-03 16:51:32', '2017-10-03 16:51:32');
