(643, 1, 21, 61, 2, 15, NULL, 'X-TIGI A1 Plus (4GB, 64GB  16MP, Dual SIM - Black)', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;5.5 Inches&nbsp;HD TFT IPS&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Android 7.0 Nougat</li>\r\n	<li>4G LTE</li>\r\n	<li>MT6753V/WA Octa core 1.3GHz</li>\r\n	<li>4GB RAM + 64GB ROM memory</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 16MP Front + 13MP Rear Camera</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 4010mAh Li-polymer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Display</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Size : 5.5 Inches</li>\r\n	<li>Type:&nbsp;AMOLED capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li>\r\n	<li>Resolution:&nbsp;1080 x 1920 pixels (~401 ppi pixel density)</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.gsmarena.com/glossary.php3?term=multitouch">Multitouch</a>:Yes</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.gsmarena.com/glossary.php3?term=screen-protection">Protection</a>:Corning Gorilla Glass (unspecified version)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Platform</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS :&nbsp;Android 7.0 (Nougat)</li>\r\n	<li>CPU Speed:&nbsp;Octa-core (4x2.0 GHz Cortex-A53 &amp; 4x1.0 GHz Cortex-A53)</li>\r\n	<li>Processor:&nbsp;Mediatek MT6755 Helio P10</li>\r\n	<li>GPU:Mali-T860MP2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.gsmarena.com/glossary.php3?term=memory-card-slot">Card slot</a>:&nbsp;microSD, up to 256 GB (uses SIM 2 slot)</li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.gsmarena.com/glossary.php3?term=dynamic-memory">Internal</a>:64 GB ROM,4GB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Primary Camera:&nbsp;13 MP, f/2.0, phase detection autofocus, LED flash</li>\r\n	<li>Features:1/3&quot; sensor size, 1.12 &micro;m pixel size, geo-tagging, touch focus, face detection, HDR</li>\r\n	<li>video:1080p@30fps</li>\r\n	<li>Secondary:&nbsp;16 MP, f/2.0, 1/3&quot; sensor size</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="http://ww