(650, 1, 21, 61, 2, 32, NULL, ' X-TIGI  Model S1450 (256MB RAM,  512MB  5MP)Blue', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>4.5 Inches&nbsp;WVGA</li>\r\n	<li>512gb Storage</li>\r\n	<li>256mb RAM</li>\r\n	<li>5MP Primary</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>OS : Android 4.4 OS (kit kat)</li>\r\n	<li>CPU :1.3 GHz processor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>512MB ROM</li>\r\n	<li>256MB RAM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>5.0 MP Back Camera</li>\r\n	<li>2.0 MP Front Camera</li>\r\n	<li>LED Flash</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sim</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Dual Sim</li>\r\n	<li>Dual standby</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Communication</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth</li>\r\n	<li>FM Radio</li>\r\n	<li>MPS/WAV/eAAC+ Flac Player</li>\r\n	<li>MP4/H264 Player</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Other Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Light Sensor, 3D G-Sensor, proximity sensors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Li-Ion 1750 mAh battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Good Camera</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>In this age of selfies, the X-TIGI One 1450 will come in handy. With the 5 MP Back camera with a LED Flash, you are ensured of clear selfies both during the day and during the night. The phone also features a 2 Megapixels front camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Powerful OS</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The android 4.4 kitkat OS installed on this phone ensures that you enjoy improved performance. Android 4.4 takes system performance to an all-time high by optimizing memory and improving your touchscreen so that it responds faster and more accurately than ever before. This means that you can listen to music while browsing the web, or race down the highway with the latest hit game, all without a hitch.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Multi-Task Processor&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The XTIGI 1450 phone has been specially designed to take your multitasking experience to a whole new level. Its Dual Core 1.3 Ghz processor makes sure that you are able to toggle between various applications effortlessly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Dual SIM</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The XTIGI 1450 comes with the Dual SIM, Dual standby feature that opens up a whole new world of possibilities for you. Now you can manage your personal and professional life more efficiently and seamlessly.</p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1448', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 3516, 3348, 1, 'x-tigi-model-s1450-256mb-ram-512mb-5mp-blue.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'x-tigi-model-s1450-256mb-ram-512mb-5mp-blue', '2017-10-07 14:05:52', '2017-10-07 14:05:52'),
