(667, 1, 21, 61, 2, 34, NULL, ' InnJoo Max 3  (13MP Camera, 16GB 2GB RAM)  Gold ', '<div class="title" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 17px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">Key Features</div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Screen: 6.0 Inch 720p HD IPS Display</li>\r\n	<li>Memory: 2GB RAM, 16GB ROM (expandable via MicroSD to 128GB</li>\r\n	<li>CPU: Quad-Core Mediatek Processor</li>\r\n	<li>Operating System: Android 5.1 Lollipop</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 13MP Rear Camera, 5MP Front Camera</li>\r\n	<li>Battery: 4000mAh Capacity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Display</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display:&nbsp;6.0-inch IPS Display, 720 x 1280 pixels (244ppi)</li>\r\n	<li>Display Protection:&nbsp;2.5D diamond cut Glass, Full Lamination</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Camera</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rear Camera:&nbsp;13 MP Camera, 1080p HD Video</li>\r\n	<li>Rear Camera Features:&nbsp;Autofocus, Dual-LED Flash, Geo-tagging, Panorama</li>\r\n	<li>Front Camera:&nbsp;8 MP Camera, Autofocus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>System</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>OS&nbsp;<strong>:&nbsp;</strong>Android 5.1 Lollipop system &nbsp;upgradable to&nbsp;6.0&nbsp;Marshmallow.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Storage</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Built-in Storage:&nbsp;16GB, 2GB RAM</li>\r\n	<li>Memory Card Support:&nbsp;Yes, up to 128GB</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Network Support</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>2G GSM:&nbsp;850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900MHz</li>\r\n	<li>3G WCDMA:&nbsp;900 / 2100MHz</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Internet &amp; Connectivity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GPRS:&nbsp;Yes, up to 48kbps</li>\r\n	<li>EDGE</li>\r\n	<li>3G/WCDMA/HSPA:&nbsp;Yes, up to 21Mbps</li>\r\n	<li>WLAN:&nbsp;Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi Hotspot</li>\r\n	<li>Bluetooth:&nbsp; Bluetooth 4.0</li>\r\n	<li>USB Port:&nbsp;microUSB 2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Messaging</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SMS/MMS</li>\r\n	<li>Instant Messaging</li>\r\n	<li>Push Emails</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Entertainment</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Music Player:&nbsp;Yes, mp3, WAV, FLAC, eACC+</li>\r\n	<li>Video Player:&nbsp;Yes, MPEG4, H.263, H.264, XviD</li>\r\n	<li>FM Radio</li>\r\n	<li>Loudspeaker</li>\r\n	<li>3.5mm Jack</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Navigation</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Navigation:&nbsp;Yes, GPS with A-GPS</li>\r\n	<li>Maps:&nbsp;Yes, Google Maps</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sensors &amp; Control</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Accelerometer</li>\r\n	<li>Proximity Sensor</li>\r\n	<li>Gyroscope</li>\r\n	<li>Fingerprint Scanner</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Other Features</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Video Streaming</li>\r\n	<li>Image Editor</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Battery:&nbsp;4000 mAh Li-Po Battery (Non-Removable)</li>\r\n	<li>Talktime:&nbsp;up to 19 hours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>The Innjoo Max 3 comes with lovely design and metallic body and screen protector which makes the phone strong and rugged. A wide screen of an epic 6-inch display and the screen is not just large but also has a matching 720p High Definition resolution. The device further highlights a massive 4000mAh long-life battery and Fast Charge function which means you spend short time charging but enjoy a really long Talk time. A super-fast fingerprint sensor and Injoo also for sake of the camera conscious users made sure there are two powerful cameras with auto-focus, anti-shake, multiple modes and some other amazing features. The front camera is 8MP while the back camera is 13MP, this is amazing and sure to make a professional photographer out of you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="image" src="https://static.jumia.co.ke/cms/external/pet/IN594EL019POGNAFAMZ/f694846ef7717f04d8440cc1f6b2a0a8.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; display:block; margin:30px auto; max-width:710px; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n', '', '', 'JCG1466', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 10364, 9870, 1, 'innjoo-max-3-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-gold.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'innjoo-max-3-13mp-camera-16gb-2gb-ram-gold', '2017-10-11 16:13:32', '2017-10-11 16:13:32'),
