right: 1.07143rem; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>SERIOUS PERFORMANCE</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The Quad Core 1.3GHz CPU, 2GB RAM, and Mali T720 GPU of this 4G LTE mobile ensure snappy, lag free processing. Onboard 16GB storage offers you plenty of space to save all your movies, songs, games, apps, photos, and more. Support for 4G LTE connectivity and a built in WiFi adapter enable fast and effortless Web browsing from virtually anywhere. This phone features slots for, not one, but two SIM cards.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem; font-family: opensans, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 10px !important;">\r\n<div class="large-6 medium-12 small-centered medium-centered left columns" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: left; clear: both;"><img alt="Innjoo Fire2 Plus" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2016/Innjoo/Fire2-Plus-Dual-Sim-16GB-4G-LTE/feature-2-gray.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="large-6 medium-12 right columns mart-60" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 60px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>HIGH RESOLUTION CAMERAS</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The 13MP rear camera of this 4G smartphone comes enhanced with a 4P lens size and f 2.0 aperture. The camera can capture stunning 3264 x 2448 pixels resolution pictures and dazzling videos. Make sure all your fond moments turn into crisp and clear, chronicled memories. The 5MP front facing camera not only shoots stunning selfies but also ena