>Capacity: 2000 mAh</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h4>DESCRIPTION</h4>\r\n\r\n<div id="description-full" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n<div class="container columns" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 954px; float: left;">\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns medium-12" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 954px; float: left;">\r\n<p>Innjoo Halo2 mobile features a 1.2GHz Octa Core processor, 1GB RAM, and 8GB onboard storage. This Innjoo Halo mobile looks bright and stylish in a gold finish. The Innjoo Halo2 3G mobile is all about making your life hassle free. How can a phone simplify your life? By giving you smooth usability and quick solutions to meet the ever growing demands of smartphone computing needs. So with this mobile, you have a responsive system, giving you instant end results the moment your finger touches the screen. This fast, glitch free performance lets you get done with your tasks quickly with ample amount of time left in your hands for other activities. It works on a 1.2GHz SC7731C Quad Core processor and 1GB RAM. It runs on Android 6.0 Marshmallow OS that gives it a neat screen design and intuitive interface. With its 8GB onboard storage capacity, you have plenty of space for a multitude of apps, games, movies, etc. You can also extend the capacity by up to 32GB to get more space for all the content you cannot do without. With its fast 3G connection, you can load, download, and share online content from anywhere. Its dual SIM slots come in handy for easy search and management of your work and personal contacts. This slim and stylish mobile is available in a beautiful gold finish.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns medium-6" style="b