ing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5 Inch</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2000 mAh</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Android</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="row mart-10" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 10px !important; margin-right: -1.07143rem; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: -1.07143rem; padding: 0px; max-width: 71.4286rem;">\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 right" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;"><img alt="Innjoo Halo 2" class="lazy-loaded" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2017/innjoo/Halo2-3G-Dual-Sim/1-innjoo-halo2-3g-dual-sim-gold.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:inherit; display:inline-block; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div class="columns large-6 medium-12 left mart-60" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 60px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 1.07143rem; width: 477px; float: right;">\r\n<h4>PACKED WITH POWER INSIDE</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>This Innjoo Halo 2 is a delightful to use because of its fluid operations. It is incorporated with an SC7731C Quad Core processor with a clock speed of 1.2GHz. This CPU is supported by a 1GB RAM for maintaining its smooth performance. You can increase the 8GB onboard storage capacity by 32GB via a microSD card slot to improve the system&#39;s performance and gain additional space for all your multimedia content. A fast and smooth system is not enough, it should be interactive, easy to understand, and have a customi