(811, 8, 28, 82, 2, NULL, NULL, 'Kenwood CM200 4 Cup Coffee Maker - White', '<p>Kenwood&nbsp;CM200</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="short_description" style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Compact design</li>\r\n	<li>500ml 4 cup</li>\r\n	<li>650W</li>\r\n	<li>Anti drip vavle</li>\r\n	<li>Hotplate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n', '<p>.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', 'JCG1627', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 6085, 5795, 1, 'kenwood-cm200-4-cup-coffee-maker-white.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'kenwood-cm200-4-cup-coffee-maker-white', '2017-11-02 09:35:17', '2017-11-02 09:35:17'),
(812, 8, 28, 82, 2, NULL, NULL, 'Delonghi BCO320 Combi Coffee Maker', '<p>Key&nbsp; Features:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Complete frontal loading</li>\r\n	<li>Cappuccino system</li>\r\n	<li>Pratical cup storage</li>\r\n	<li>Drip side water filtration</li>\r\n	<li>Manual cappuccino device&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Easy Serving Espresso</li>\r\n	<li>Stainless steel espresso boiler</li>\r\n	<li>15 bar professional pressure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>More information</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>DeLonghi combination coffee and espresso machine has a stylish design. This DeLonghi coffee machine makes delicious cappuccinos and lattes. The DeLonghi BCO320 Combination Coffee Machine is a must have in any coffee lover&rsquo;s kitchen. Be it filter coffee, espresso, or cappuccino, this coffee machine makes you the best brewed coffee whenever you want it. This coffee machine has a compact design, and it can be accommodated easily in your kitchen without occupying much space. It has a stream spout that quickly heats and foams cappuccinos and lattes. You can keep your coffee cups on the practically designed cup holder on the top. The complete front loading system ensures frontal refilling of coffee and water, without moving it around. The DeLonghi BCO320 Combination Coffee Machine sports a beautiful black finish that looks elegant and will match well with your kitchen interiors.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>REMARKABLE PERFORMANCE</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The cappuccino system in this DeLonghi combination coffee and espresso machine mixes air, steam, and milk to give you a creamy, rich froth for perfect cappuccinos. It can produce up to four refreshingly hot cups of espresso coffee in one go. An advanced charcoal filter keeps the water clean, giving you fresh coffee every time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="DeLonghi coffee machine" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2017/Delonghi/combination-coffee-machine-bco320/1-combination-coffee-machine-bco320.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>EASY USE</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>The V shaped paper filter prevents lime scaling and can be easily cleaned. The heat resistant glass jug with a water level marking helps you fill the water accurately for a perfect taste. The safety cap in the DeLonghi coffee machine prevents accidental openings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt="DeLonghi coffee machine" src="https://souqcms.s3.amazonaws.com/spring/images/2017/Delonghi/combination-coffee-machine-bco320/2-combination-coffee-machine-bco320.jpg" style="border:0px; box-sizing:border-box; height:auto; max-width:100%; vertical-align:middle" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\r\n', '', '', '', 'JCG1630', NULL, '', NULL, 'visible', 24145, 22995, 1, 'delonghi-bco320-combi-coffee-maker.jpg', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'delonghi-bco320-combi-coffee-maker', '2017-11-02 09:43:39', '2017-11-02 09:43:39'),
